\id LUK - Saveeŋ (Tuam dialect) NT -Papua New Guinea 2011 (web 2014) 
\h Lukas 
\toc1 Vaaru Poia tau Lukas Iboode 
\toc2 Lukas 
\toc3 Lu 
\mt1 Vaaru Poia tau Lukas Iboode  
\mt2 Luk—Luke  
\c 1  
\s1 Paesiiŋ to Lukas  
\p
\v 1-2 O tiina tsiau Teopilus, Maaron igham uraat tiina ivot ila iit sosoon itaghon saveeŋ mbuaaŋ tooni. Saawe tau uraat tawe ivot imin maata ve ilam na, zeran siriv tilepleep, ve tighita pa matazi. Tauta tipariaaŋ uraat tana saveeŋa ve tigham uratoini. Zeran tawe tisinai poi payei pa uraat tana. Leso niwataghi paam. Ve tamtamon katini titoova to tibood duduŋai sinaiŋ tana ila rau. \x * \xo 1:1-2 \xt Mbaŋ 1:1+; Hib 2:3; 1Yo 1:1\x*   
\m
\v 3-4 Yau tauvene paam. Saawe malau rig, nazuari ghau leso nawatagh katin uraat naol tana ila ta puughu ve ilam. Ve nabood sinaiŋ tana ila rau itaghon duduŋai gabua tau ivot na. Tauta aazne nayambaara ilat payo. Leso yo uwatagh ughe saveeŋ tau tipaduduuŋ ghom pani na, ene onoon mon. \x * \xo 1:3-4 \xt 2Tim 3:14; 2Pe 1:16\x*   
\s1 Aŋela ivot to Sakaria  
\p
\v 5 Saawe tau kinik Erod iŋgin taan sirivu to Yudea, ŋeer ee to watooŋrau ilepleep, eeza Sakaria. I ileep ila ŋgun to Abia pa uraat to watooŋrau. Azaawa eeza Elisabet. I paam siŋ to Aron.  
\v 6 Yesuru tamtamon duduŋazi. Lezi sosor eta ila Maaron maata mako. Saawe isov, matazi kisin tutuuŋ to Ŋeer Tiina tomania tutuuŋ ŋgara, ve titaghon duduŋaini.  
\v 7 Eemon yesuru lezi natuzi eta mako. Pasaa, Elisabet, i uupa. Ve yesuru timin zolmana wa.   
\p
\v 8-9 Saawe ee, Sakaria tomania zeetŋa siriv tau tileep ila ŋgun to Abia na, anazi tila tigham uraat ila Maaron naagho ila Rumei Tiina loolo. Zeran to watooŋrau, gabuazi tauvene: Saawe toozi to uraat ighe ivot, mako tipayooz mbuur. Leso itotoi sei tau pale ila itun naunauŋ tau vaazi poia na ila Maaron naagho. Saawe tana, tipayooz mbuur le Sakaria eeza ivot.  
\v 10 Tauvene saawe to tunuuŋ naunauŋ, i ileep ila Rumei Tiina loolo, ve igham uraat tana, ve eval tiina tileep muuri ve tisuŋsuŋ.   
\p
\v 11 Sakaria ighamgham uraat, ve malau mako ve aŋela ee to Ŋeer Tiina ivot tooni, ve iyooz ila artaal ziige tau ila pa niima tapir.  
\v 12 Sakaria ighita aŋela tawe le irur ve roiŋ tiina ighamu.   
\p
\v 13 Eemon aŋela isaav pani ighe: “Sakaria, uroi sov. Suŋuuŋ tsio, Maaron ilooŋa wa. Azuwam Elisabet pale aapo ve ipoop tamoot. Ve yo aat uwaat eeza Yoan.  
\v 14 I pale igham ghom tintinim ve lolom poia kat. Ve yo mon mako. Saawe tau tiina ipoopa, eval tiina pale tintinizi ve lolozi poia pani paam.  
\v 15 Pasaa, i pale eeza tiina ila Maaron maata. I irau ighun vaen ma yaa ariaaŋa mako. Ve saawe tau i ilepleep ila tiina aapo loolo ve ila, Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ pale izeeva. \x * \xo 1:15 \xt Nam 6:1+\x*   
\m
\v 16 I pale igham tamtamon katini to Israel titoor ŋgar toozi imuul ila pa Tiina toozi Maaron.  
\v 17 Ŋgar tooni ve tapiri pale imin propet Ilia. Ve i pale imuuŋ pa Ŋeer Tiina, ve igharaat eez pani. Pale itoor zolmana ŋgar toozi imuul ila pa natuzŋa, leso tilup lolozi imin eemon. Ve igham yes zeran to taliiŋzizi titoor ŋgar toozi, ve titaghon ŋgar poia imin tamtamon duduŋazi. Leso igham tamtamon tigharaat tauzi ve tisaŋan saawe tau Ŋeer Tiina igham mulin zi.” \x * \xo 1:17 \xt Mal 3:1, 4:5+; Mt 3:3; Mk 9:12\x*   
\p
\v 18 Sakaria ilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve ighason aŋela ighe: “Saa gabua pale imin ilaal payau leso nawatagh naghe saveeŋ tsio pale ighur anooŋa? Ughita, yau namin kooŋ ve azuwag imin olman tinazi wa.” \x * \xo 1:18 \xt Gnp 18:11\x*   
\p
\v 19 Aŋela iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Yau Gabriel. Monmon nayozyooz ila Maaron naagho. I tauu imbaaŋ ghau nalam to nasavia gabua poia tane vaaru payo. \x * \xo 1:19 \xt Dan 8:16, 9:21; Hib 1:14\x*   
\m
\v 20 Ve ulooŋ. Saveeŋ tsiau tane pale ighur anooŋa ivot itaghon saawe tau Maaron ighuru na. Eemon yo ughur ila mako. Tauvene avom pale ivool, ve irau usaav mako, lee saveeŋ tane ighur anooŋa.”   
\p
\v 21 Sakaria ileep malau ila Rumei Tiina loolo. Tauvene eval tiina tau tileep muuri na tisaŋani le mako, ve tigham ŋgar naol pani.  
\v 22 Saawe tau ivot ilam toozi, i irau isavia saveeŋ eta pazi mako. Itotoi pa niima mon. Pasaa, aavo ivool. Tauta tighilaal tighe gabua eta aat ivot pani ila rumei loolo.   
\p
\v 23 Sakaria ilepleep le saawe tooni to uraat isov, ve imuul ila pa nugh tooni.  
\v 24 Murei ra, azaawa Elisabet aapo. I ileep ila ruum loolo irau kaiyo liim imin ŋgozaaŋ tauu.  
\v 25 Ve maata iŋgal ighe: “Ŋeer Tiina ighita pataŋani tsiau, tauta loolo isaghatin ghau ve iuul ghau le aazne igham mayag ipit ila tamtamon matazi.” \x * \xo 1:25 \xt Gnp 30:23\x*   
\s1 Aŋela ivot to Maria ve ipaes pani ighe i pale ipoop Yesu  
\p
\v 26 Elisabet kaiyo tooni irau liim ve ee, ragha Maaron imbaaŋ aŋela Gabriel ila nugh Nasaret tau igheen taan sirivu to Galilaia.  
\v 27 Gabriel ila ivot to livaa mbiu ee, eeza Maria. I, tisiigho pa ŋeer ee wa, eeza Yosep. Yosep puughu tooni ivot ila to kinik David. \x * \xo 1:27 \xt Mt 1:6+; Lu 2:5\x*   
\m
\v 28 Gabriel ila ivot to Maria, ve isaav pani ighe: “Maria, aaz poia! Ŋeer Tiina loolo payo, ve ipakur ghom, ve ileep tomani ghom.”   
\p
\v 29 Maria ilooŋ saveeŋ tane le irur ve igham ŋgar naol ighe saveeŋ poia tau aŋela isavia pani na, puughu mindai?   
\p
\v 30 Tauvene aŋela isaav pani muul ighe: “Maria, uroi sov. Pa Maaron loolo payo ve igham poghani ghom.  
\v 31 Ulooŋ. Yo pale apom, ve upoop tamoot. Natum tana, yo aat uwaat eeza Yesu. \x * \xo 1:31 \xt Is 7:14; Mt 1:21; Lu 2:21\x*   
\m
\v 32 I pale eeza tiina kat, ve tiwaato tighe Maaron Tiina Tau Iliiv Zimaronŋa Tisov na Naatu. Tiina toit Maaron pale ighuru to igham pooz imin tiimbu David. \x * \xo 1:32 \xt Mbo 2:6, 132:11; Is 9:6+\x*   
\m
\v 33 Ve pooz tooni irau isov ne mako. I pale iŋgin Yakop paaghu tooni taghon taghon gha ila.” \x * \xo 1:33 \xt Dan 2:44, 7:14; Hib 1:8\x*   
\p
\v 34 Aŋela isavsaav le isov, ra Maria ighasoni ighe: “Saveeŋ tsio tane pale anooŋa ivot mindai? Pasaa, yau livaa mbiu. Yeiru ŋeer eta nilup ghei soone.”   
\p
\v 35 Aŋela iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ tomania Maaron Tiina Tau Iliiv Zimaronŋa Tisov na tapiri pale izaa tsio. Tauvene marani tau yo upoopa na, i pale patabuyaaŋ, ve tiwaato tighe ‘Maaron Naatu.’ \x * \xo 1:35 \xt Mt 1:18+; Mk 15:39\x*   
\m
\v 36 Ve ulooŋ. Waghamliva Elisabet tau imin olman tinazi ve muuŋ tiwatwaato tighe uupa na, i paam aapo, ve kaiyo tooni liim ve ee wa.  
\v 37 Pasaa, Maaron, gabua eta irau ikeeka mako.” \x * \xo 1:37 \xt Gnp 18:14; Mt 19:26; Ro 4:21\x*   
\p
\v 38 Tauvene Maria isaav pani muul ighe: “Poia. Yau besooŋa livaa to Ŋeer Tiina. I irau igham gabua ivot payau itaghon aliŋam.” Maria isavia saveeŋ tane le isov, ra aŋela ipuli, ve ila.   
\s1 Maria ila ighita Elisabet  
\p
\v 39 Saawe tana, Maria iburig ve ilaagh rekia mon ila ivot Sakaria gha Elisabet nugh toozi. Nugh tawe igheen ila taan sirivu to Yudea izala loloz.  
\v 40 Ila peria, ve malmali iloŋ ila ruum to Sakaria, ve igham ‘aaz poia’ pa Elisabet.   
\p
\v 41-42 Elisabet ilooŋ Maria aliiŋa, ve naatu ipuul ve iyaat ila aapo loolo. Ra Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ ipavon Elisabet, ve ipaburigini gha isaav aliiŋa tiina ighe: “Maria, Maaron ipakur ghom ve ighur poia tooni tiina izaa tsio le uliiv zilivaa tisov. Ve natum tau apom pani na, Maaron pale ipakuru ve ighur poia tooni izaa tooni. \x * \xo 1:41-42 \xt Lu 1:15\x*   
\m
\v 43 Yau sei, ta Maaron tsiau tiina ilam igig ghau?  
\v 44 Saawe duduuŋ tau nalooŋ ugham ‘aaz poia’ payau, natug tau ileep ila apog loolo ne, ipuul toman tintini.  
\v 45 Poia to Ŋeer Tiina aat izaa tsio. Pasaa, yo ughur ila ughe saveeŋ tau i isavia payo na, ene pale anooŋa ivot.”   
\s1 Mbouŋ to Maria  
\r (1Sam 2:1-10)  
\p
\v 46-47 Ra Maria ipait Maaron eeza tauvene:  
\q2 “Yau napait Ŋeer Tiina toman lolog. Pasaa, i eeza tiina kat.  
\q2 Maaron i Uleeŋa tsiau tau igham mulin ghau. Tauvene lolog poia kat pani. \x * \xo 1:46-47 \xt Mbo 34:2+; 1Tim 4:10\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 48 Yau besooŋa livaa tooni sorok. Leg ezag mako.  
\q2 Eemon i maata iŋgalŋgal ghau ve igham poghani ghau.  
\q2 Tauvene aazne ve ila, tamtamon pale tisavia poia to Maaron tau izaa tsiau ne. \x * \xo 1:48 \xt Mbo 138:6; Lu 11:27\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 49 Pasaa, Maaron saksaki igham uraat tintiina payau.  
\q2 I eeza patabuyaaŋ. \x * \xo 1:49 \xt Mbo 71:19, 111:9, 126:2+\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 50 Tamtamon tau tiroi pani ve titaghon ŋgar tooni na, i loolo isaghatin zi, ve iuluul zi. Ighamgham tauvene pa tamtamon to aazne, ve taghon taghon gha ila. \x * \xo 1:50 \xt Igham 20:6; Mbo 103:13-18\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 51 Maaron niima ighamgham uraat tintiina, leso itotoi tapiri ivot ighazooŋ.  
\q2 Tamtamon tau tipapait tauzi ezazi tighe yes tirao na, i ireu zi tighawaar. \x * \xo 1:51 \xt Lu 18:9+; 1Pe 5:5\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 52 Ve yes daaba tau tapirizi tiina na, i izirziir zi pa niazi to ghamuuŋ pooz, ve itatan zi tizi timin kaut sorok.  
\q2 Eemon tamtamon tau lezi ezazi mako na, i ipakur zi. \x * \xo 1:52 \xt Mbo 113:7; Mt 23:12; Kol 2:15\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 53 Ve yes tau pitool zi na, i igham gabua popoia pazi, ve tighan le isooŋ zi.  
\q2 Eemon kuaz tauŋa, i iziir zi tighau tila toman nimazi ŋginaaŋa mon. \x * \xo 1:53 \xt Mbo 34:10, 107:9; Lu 6:21\x*   
\q1
\v 54-55 Muuŋ, i imbu saveeŋ tomania timbuunŋa tauvene: I pale loolo isaghatin Abaram ve paaghu tooni, ve iuul zi taghon taghon gha ila.  
\q2 Tauta aazne, maata iŋgal besooŋa tooni Israel, ve iuul zi.” \x * \xo 1:54-55 \xt Gnp 17:7; Mbo 98:3; Mika 7:20; Ro 11:28\x*   
\p
\v 56 Maria ileep tomania Elisabet irau kaiyo tol ma vene, ra iburig imuul ila pa nugh tooni.   
\s1 Elisabet ipoop Yoan  
\p
\v 57 Elisabet saawe tooni to popaaŋ ivot, ve ipoop tamoot.  
\v 58 Ziiri waaro tooni tomania zeetŋa siriv tau ruum toozi igharau na, tilooŋ Elisabet vaaru tighe Ŋeer Tiina loolo isaghatini ve igham uleeŋ tiina pani. Tauta yesŋa Elisabet lolozi poia.   
\p
\v 59 Tileep le mboŋ imin liim ve tol, ra zetazŋa tilam pa uraat to ravuuŋ marani tana waaro. Ve tighe tiwaat taama Sakaria eeza pani. \x * \xo 1:59 \xt Gnp 17:12\x*   
\m
\v 60 Eemon tiina isaav pazi ighe: “Mako! Tawaat eeza Yoan.”   
\p
\v 61 Yes tiyol aliiŋa tighe: “Ene poia. Eemon ziiri waaro tsio eta eeza tauvene mako.”  
\v 62 Tauta titotoi pa taama tighe tighita pale iwaat eeza sei?   
\p
\v 63 Sakaria itotoi pazi gha tigham taper ilam, ve ibood saveeŋ tauvene: “I eeza Yoan.” Yes tau tileep tomani zi na, tighita gabua tana le tisov tirur.  
\v 64 Rekia mon Sakaria aavo pakia, yaama ibees, ve ipait Maaron eeza pa poia tooni.   
\p
\v 65 Tauvene roiŋ tiina igham tamtamon tisov tau tileep tigharau zi na. Ve tisavia gabua isov tana vaaru irau taan sirivu to Yudea loloza.  
\v 66 Tamtamon tisov tau tilooŋ gabua tana vaaru, tigham ŋgar naol, ve tivasavo zi tighe: “Wai, marani tawe, murei pale igham saa?” Pasaa, tighilaal tighe i ileep ila Ŋeer Tiina niima wa.   
\s1 Mbouŋ to Sakaria  
\p
\v 67 Ra Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ izeev Yoan taama Sakaria, ve i ivotia Maaron aliiŋa imin propet ighe:   
\q1
\v 68 “Iit tapait Maaron pa poia tooni! I Tiina to iit Israela.  
\q2 Pasaa, i ilam to iuul tamtamon tooni, leso igham mulin zi pa pataŋani toozi. \x * \xo 1:68 \xt Mbo 72:18, 111:9; Lu 7:16\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 69-70 I ighur leen Uleeŋa ariaaŋa ee. Leso igham mulin ghiit pa pataŋani toit, itaghon saveeŋ tau muuŋ i ivotia ila yes propet tooni patabuyaaŋa avozi.  
\q2 Uleeŋa tawe ivot ila siŋ to besooŋa tooni David. \x * \xo 1:69-70 \xt Mt 1:1; Ro 1:1-3\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 71 I pale igham mulin ghiit ila koiaanŋa nimazi.  
\q2 Leso taleep ila yes tau tighur koi pait na sambazi muul sov.   
\b  
\q1
\v 72-73 Muuŋ, Maaron imbu saveeŋ tomania timbuun Abaram, ve ipariaaŋa le iyaryaaŋ kat. Ighe:  
\q2 Yesuru pale tivalupu zi timin eemon. Ve i pale loolo isaghatin Abaram tomania paaghu tooni, ve iuul zi pa pataŋani toozi taghon taghon gha ila.  
\q2 Tauta maata iŋgal saveeŋ mbuaaŋ tooni patabuyaaŋ tawe, \x * \xo 1:72-73 \xt Gnp 17:1, 22:16+\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 74 ve igham mulin ghiit ila koiaanŋa nimazi.  
\q2 Leso taroi muul sov, ve tabees pani toman loloon poia, \x * \xo 1:74 \xt Ro 6:22; 1Yo 4:17+; Hib 9:14\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 75 ve tataghon ŋgar tau patabuyaaŋ ve iduduuŋ mon ila i maata, le irau saawe toit to taan isov.” \x * \xo 1:75 \xt Ep 4:24; Tit 2:12; 1Pe 1:15\x*   
\p
\v 76 Ra Sakaria isaav pa naatu ighe:  
\q2 “Natug, yo pale tiwaat ghom tighe propet to Maaron Tiina Tau Iliiv Zimaronŋa Tisov.  
\q2 Pasaa, yo pale umuuŋ pa Ŋeer Tiina, ve ugharaat eez pani. \x * \xo 1:76 \xt Is 40:3; Mal 3:1; Mt 3:3, 11:9\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 77 Yo pale upaghazoŋai Maaron tamtamon tooni, leso tiwatagh eez tau i pale igham mulin zi ve ireu sosor toozi. \x * \xo 1:77 \xt Yer 31:34; Mt 1:21; Lu 3:3\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 78 Pasaa, Maaron toit, i loolo igheen toit ve loolo isaghatin ghiit kat.  
\q2 Tauvene ghazooŋa to sambam pale izilam pait imin aaz isinaar izaa pa mboŋoozo.   
\b  
\q1
\v 79 Yes tau ndoroom ikau zi ve tileep ila mateegh yavyaava na, ghazooŋa tawe pale isul zi ve ipaghazoŋai zi.  
\q2 Leso tataghon duduŋai eez to Maaron, ve taleep poia ila tooni.” \x * \xo 1:79 \xt Is 9:1+; Mt 4:16; Yo 8:12; Mbaŋ 26:18\x*   
\p
\v 80 Yoan itum imin olman, ve Maaron Avuvu tapiri igheen tooni ve ipaloti. I ila ileep izi nugh ŋginaaŋa le irau saawe tau ipaburigin uraat tooni ila yes Israela matazi. \x * \xo 1:80 \xt Lu 2:40, 52\x*   
\c 2  
\s1 Yesu tiina ipoopa  
\r (Mt 1:18-25)  
\p
\v 1 Elisabet ipoop Yoan ve saawe siriv ilam ila, ra Augustus tau kinik tiina to Rom na ighur saveeŋ pa nugh naol isov tau tileep ila i saamba na, ighe tila tighur ezazi.  
\v 2 Saawe tana, tipaburigin uraat to ghamuuŋ tamtamon ezazi ivot imin maata. Uraat tawe ivot indeeŋ Kirinius igham pooz pa taan sirivu to Siria.  
\v 3 Tauvene tamtamon tisov timuul tila pa nugh toz toz puughu, leso tighur ezazi.   
\p
\v 4-5 Yosep puughu tooni ivot ila to kinik David. Tauvene igham Maria, livaa tau tisiigho pani na, ve yesuru tipul nugh Nasaret tau igheen ila taan sirivu to Galilaia na, ve tilaagh tila peria taan sirivu to Yudea. Ra malmalizi tila tivot nugh to kinik David, eeza Betelem. Leso tighur ezazi. Saawe tana, Maria i aapo.  
\v 6 Tilepleep ta sewe, ve Maria saawe tooni to popaaŋ ivot. \x * \xo 2:6 \xt Yo 7:42\x*   
\m
\v 7 Tauvene ipoop naatu aidaaba, ve ikaukauu pa uuli, ve ipagheena igheen ila ŋgai niazi to ghanghaniiŋ. Yes tileep ta sewe pasaa, ruum to loomba tisov tivoniir.   
\s1 Aŋela tivot to yes ŋginiiŋa to sipsip  
\p
\v 8 Mboŋ tana, ŋginiiŋa siriv to sipsip tileep izi nugh Betelem ziige, ve tiŋginŋgin sipsip toozi.  
\v 9 Malau mako, aŋela to Ŋeer Tiina izilam gha iyooz ila naghozi, ve Ŋeer Tiina mbonari isul livutin zi. Tauvene roiŋ tiina kat igham zi.  
\v 10 Eemon aŋela tawe isaav pazi ighe: “Yam aroi sov. Alooŋ. Yau nalam to napaesia vaaru poia payam. Vaaru poia tane pale igham tamtamon tisov lolozi poia le poia kat. \x * \xo 2:10 \xt Mbaŋ 13:52; Ro 15:13\x*   
\m
\v 11 Pasaa, mboŋ aazne, Uleeŋa tsiam, tiina ipoopa izi nugh to David wa. I Mesia, ve Tiina tsiam. \x * \xo 2:11 \xt Is 9:6; Mbaŋ 2:36; 1Yo 4:14\x*   
\m
\v 12 Gabua tane pale itotoia payam: Ala, pale aghita marani ee tau tikaukauu pa uuli, ve tipagheena igheen ila ŋgai niazi to ghanghaniiŋ.”   
\p
\v 13 Malau mako aŋela ndiŋndiŋ ndiŋndiŋ to nugh sambam timeke tizilam, gha tilup zi tomania aŋela tana, ve tipait Maaron eeza tighe:   
\q1
\v 14 “Tapait Maaron tau ileep saaŋa le saaŋa kat na eeza pa tapiri ve poia tooni.  
\q2 Mboŋ aazne, luuma to Maaron izilam taan. Tauvene yes tau Maaron loolo poia pazi, ene pale luuma tooni izaa toozi ve tileep poi.” \x * \xo 2:14 \xt Lu 19:38; Ro 5:1; Ep 2:14; Kol 1:20\x*   
\p
\v 15 Yes aŋela tipul zi, ve timuul tizala pa sambam, ra yes ŋginiiŋa to sipsip tana tivasavo zi tighe: “Aiyo, taburig, ve tala pa Betelem. Leso taghita gabua tau Ŋeer Tiina ipaesia pait ne.”   
\p
\v 16 Tauvene tilaan rekia tila, ve tindeeŋ Maria yesuru Yosep, ve marani tana. I ighengheen ila ŋgai niazi to ghanghaniiŋ.  
\v 17 Tighita le isov, ra tipaesia saveeŋ tau aŋela isavia pazi pa marani tana.  
\v 18 Tamtamon tisov tau tilooŋ saveeŋ toozi na, tirur ve tigham ŋgar naol.  
\v 19 Ve Maria ikis saveeŋ tana isov igheen ila loolo ve ighamgham ŋgar pani. \x * \xo 2:19 \xt Lu 2:51\x*   
\m
\v 20 Ra yes ŋginiiŋa to sipsip timuul tila. Tilaghlaagh, ve tipapait Maaron eeza pa gabua naol isov tau tilooŋa ve tighita. Pasaa, gabua tana ivot itaghon duduŋai saveeŋ tau aŋela isavia pazi na.   
\s1 Maria yesuru Yosep tigham Yesu ila Rumei Tiina  
\p
\v 21 Tilepleep ve mboŋ liim ve tol ilam ila, ra uraat to ravuuŋ natuzi waaro ivot, ve tiwaat eeza Yesu. Eeza tane, Maria aapo soone, ve aŋela iwaato pataghaaŋ wa. \x * \xo 2:21 \xt Gnp 17:10; Mt 1:21, 25\x*   
\m
\v 22-23 Maria gha Yosep tileep le saawe toozi ivot to tigharaat tauzi le tiŋgalaaŋ muul ila Maaron maata itaghon tutuuŋ to Mose. Ra tigham ŋeer marani tana, ve tizala Yerusalem. Leso tighuru imin Ŋeer Tiina le, itaghon saveeŋ tau tiboode ila Ŋeer Tiina tutuuŋ tooni. Isaav tauvene ighe:  
\q2 “Natmimŋa aidabazŋa, aghur zi tisov timin Maaron le.” \x * \xo 2:22-23 \xt Igham 13:2, 12; Wkp 12:2+\x*   
\m
\v 24 Tauvene yesuru tila tighur marani tana imin Ŋeer Tiina le, ve tirav mbuun ru imin watooŋrau itaghon tutuuŋ to Ŋeer Tiina tau ighe: “Arav mbuun ru, ma mbunumoor paghpaaghu ru imin watooŋrau.” \x * \xo 2:24 \xt Wkp 12:8\x*   
\s1 Simeon ivotia ŋgar tau pale ivot pa Yesu  
\p
\v 25 Ŋeer ee ileep izi Yerusalem, eeza Simeon. I ŋeer duduuŋa ila Maaron maata. Saawe isov, i maata iŋgalŋgal Maaron ve itaghon ŋgar tooni. I ighurghur maata pa saawe to Maaron igham mulin yes Israela ve tileep poia muul. Ve Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ ileep tomania. \x * \xo 2:25 \xt Is 40:1\x*   
\m
\v 26 Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ ipaghazoŋaini wa, ighe: I pale ighita Mesia to Maaron le isov, o imaat.  
\v 27 Tauvene Yesu taama gha tiina tighamu tiloŋ tila sirsiir to Rumei Tiina loolo tighe tigham ŋgar tau tutuuŋ isavia na pani. Ve saawe duduuŋ tana, Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ ipaburigin Simeon paam gha iloŋ ila sirsiir to Rumei Tiina loolo.  
\v 28 I ighita ŋeer marani, ve ila iiti izaa imbaraara, ve ipait Maaron eeza ighe:   
\q1
\v 29 “O Tiina, yau besooŋa tsio. Ŋgarig gha ateg izi. Aazne, ighe yo ugham ghau napul taan ve nalat, yau aat nalat toman lolog poia.  
\q2 Pasaa, saveeŋ tau yo umbua payau na, ighur anooŋa ivot wa. \x * \xo 2:29 \xt Gnp 46:30; Pil 1:23\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 30-31 Eez tau yo pale ugham mulin tamtamon pani na, yo utotoia payau gha naghita pa matag wa. Eez tane, yo taum ugharaata ila nughmariŋ matazi. \x * \xo 2:30-31 \xt Is 40:5, 52:10; Lu 3:6\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 32 I pale imin ghazooŋa pa yes tau Yuda mako na, ve ipaghazoŋai zi payo.  
\q2 Ve igham tamtamon tsio Israel ezazi ivot imin tiina paam.” \x * \xo 2:32 \xt Is 42:6, 49:6; Mbaŋ 13:47, 26:23\x*   
\p
\v 33 Yesu taama gha tiina tilooŋ saveeŋ tau Simeon isavia pa Yesu na, le tigham ŋgar naol.  
\v 34-35 Ra Simeon ighur poia to Maaron izaa toozi, ve isaav pa Yesu tiina Maria ighe: “Ulooŋ. Ŋeer marani tane, Maaron ighuru pa valaghiiŋ tamtamon katini to Israel. Siriv pale tizori ve titap gha tilalez. Ve siriv, i pale igham zi tiburig tiyooz. Pasaa, i pale igham ŋgar tau igheen ila tamtamon lolozi na ivot ighazooŋ. Eemon tamtamon katini pale tizori. Ve ŋgar tau pale ivot pani na, yo pale uyamaana imin mbuzaagh maata iŋgal atem.” \x * \xo 2:34-35 \xt Is 8:14; Mt 21:42+; Yo 19:25; Ro 9:32+\x*   
\s1 Propet livaa Anna ighita Yesu  
\p
\v 36 Propet livaa ee ileep ila sirsiir to Rumei Tiina loolo paam, eeza Anna. Taama eeza Panuel, ve puughu tooni ivot ila to Aser. I imin kooŋ wa. Muuŋ, i ivai. Eemon yesuru azaawa tileep irau ndaman liim ve ru mon, ra azaawa imaat, ve i izi imin naar.  
\v 37 I ilepleep le ndaman tooni irau tamoot paaŋ geege paaŋ (84). I ipulpul Rumei Tiina mako. Saawe isov, mboŋ ve mataaz, ibesbees pa Maaron ta sewe. Ve iŋgunŋgun tauu pa ghaniiŋ aniiŋ ve isuŋsuŋ. \x * \xo 2:37 \xt 1Tim 5:5\x*   
\m
\v 38 Yosep yesuru Maria ve natuzi tilepleep ila sirsiir to Rumei Tiina loolo soone, ve Anna aana ilam ivot toozi, ve ipait Maaron eeza, ve ipaesia ŋeer marani pa yes eval tau tighurghur matazi pa saawe to Maaron igham mulin tamtamon to Yerusalem pa pataŋani toozi. \x * \xo 2:38 \xt Is 52:9; Lu 1:68\x*   
\p
\v 39 Yosep gha Maria tigham uratoi gabua naol tau tutuuŋ to Ŋeer Tiina isavia na le isov, ra timuul tila pa nugh toozi Nasaret tau igheen ila taan sirivu to Galilaia. \x * \xo 2:39 \xt Mt 2:23\x*   
\m
\v 40 Natuzi itum imin olman rig ve tapiri ivot. Ve ŋgar tooni paam, ivot imin tiina ve ŋgar popoia katini igheen tooni. Ve poia to Maaron igheen tomania. \x * \xo 2:40 \xt Lu 1:80, 2:52\x*   
\s1 Yesu ndaman tooni saŋavul ve ru ve ila Rumei Tiina  
\p
\v 41 Ndaman isov, Yesu taama gha tiina tilala Yerusalem pa lupuuŋ tiina to Pasova. \f + \fr 2:41 \ft Pasova, ene lupuuŋ tiina to yes Yuda tau matazi iŋgal saawe tau Maaron igham mulin timbuzŋa izi Isip.\f* \x * \xo 2:41 \xt Igham 23:14+\x*   
\m
\v 42 Saawe tau Yesu ndaman tooni imin saŋavul ve ru, tighamu gha yesŋa tizala Yerusalem titaghon ŋgar tau monmon tighamghamu na.  
\v 43-44 Lupuuŋ tawe isov, ra Yosep yesuru Maria tipaburigin laghooŋ toozi tighe timuul tila pa nugh toozi. Eemon Yesu izi ileep Yerusalem. Ve taama gha tiina tiwataghi mako. Matazi iŋgal sorok tighe i yesŋa tamtamon siriv timuuŋ tila wa. Tilaagh tila le ravrav izi, ra tiilo. Tauvene tilaagh irau zetazŋa, ve tighason zi pani.  
\v 45 Eemon tindeeŋa mako. Tauvene timuul tila pa Yerusalem, leso tiilo ta sewe.  
\v 46 Tiilo le irau mboŋ tol ila, ra tindeeŋa ileep ila sirsiir to Rumei Tiina loolo. I yesŋa zeran ŋgara siriv to tutuuŋ tilepleep, ve i iloŋlooŋ zi, ve ighaghason zi pa saveeŋ siriv.  
\v 47 Tamtamon tisov tau tilooŋ saveeŋ tooni na, tirur pa ŋgar tooni ve saveeŋ tau i iyoli pa zeran ŋgara tawe. \x * \xo 2:47 \xt Mt 7:28\x*   
\m
\v 48 Taama gha tiina tighita le tirur. Ve tiina ila isaav pani ighe: “Wai natug, mindai ta yo ugham ŋgar tauvene payei? Yeiru tamam atemai iparav payo kat, ve nikaria ilooŋ ghom.”   
\p
\v 49 Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Ne? Yamru ail ghau pasaa? Awatagh mako? Yau aat naleep ila Tamaŋ ruum tooni.”  
\v 50 Eemon yesuru tighilaal saveeŋ tau i isavia pazi na puughu mako. \x * \xo 2:50 \xt Lu 9:45, 18:34\x*   
\p
\v 51 Ra yesŋa tiburig, ve timuul tila pa Nasaret. I monmon maata loŋloŋai pazi. Ve tiina ighur saveeŋ tomania gabua isov tau ivot pa naatu na ila loolo, ve ighamgham ŋgar pani. \x * \xo 2:51 \xt Igham 20:12; Lu 2:19\x*   
\p
\v 52 Yesu itum imin olman, ve ŋgar tooni imatuugh pa ŋgar popoia to Maaron. Tauvene Maaron loolo poia pani. Ve tamtamon paam, lolozi poia pani.   
\c 3  
\s1 Ŋeer rughuzaaŋa Yoan igharaat eez pa Yesu Krisi  
\r (Mt 3:1-12; Mk 1:1-8; Yo 1:19-28)  
\p
\v 1 Tiberius imin kinik to Rom, ve igham pooz irau ndaman saŋavul ve paaŋ, ve ite imin liim pani, ene Pontius Piladus iŋgin taan sirivu to Yudea, ve Erod iŋgin taan sirivu to Galilaia, ve toogha Pilip iŋgin taan sirivu to Iturea ve Trakonitis, ve Lisanius iŋgin taan sirivu to Abilene.  
\v 2 Ve Anas yesuru Kaiapas timin daaba pa yes zeran to watooŋrau. \x * \xo 3:2 \xt Mt 26:3; Yo 18:13; Mbaŋ 4:6\x*  
\m Saawe tana, Yoan tau Sakaria naatu na, ilepleep izi nugh ŋginaaŋa, ve Maaron aliiŋa ilam pani.  
\v 3 Tauvene iburig ilaagh irau nugh naol tau tigheen tigharau yaa Yordan ziige na, ve ivovotia Maaron aliiŋa pa tamtamon ighe tipul ŋgar toozi sasaghati ileple, ve titoor ŋgar toozi imuul ila pa Maaron ve tigham yaa. Leso Maaron ireu sosor toozi. \x * \xo 3:3 \xt 1Pe 3:21\x*   
\m
\v 4 Ŋgar tau Yoan ighamu, ene itaghon saveeŋ tau igheen ila rau to propet Isaia na. Isaav tauvene:  
\q2 Ŋeer ee iboboob izi nugh ŋginaaŋa ighe:  
\q2 “Agharaat eez pa Ŋeer Tiina.  
\q2 Apaduduŋai eez ta naol ne pani le tiduduuŋ.   
\q2
\v 5 Nugh naol isov tau ŋgolopa ŋgolopa na, apavon zi le tizaa raraate.  
\q2 Ve loloz tomania nugh mbua tisov, aghel zi le tizi raraate.  
\q2 Eez tau kookakooka na, agharaat zi le tiduduuŋ.  
\q2 Ve eez naol tau tisaghat na, agharaat zi le popoia. \x * \xo 3:5 \xt Is 2:11, 12, 17\x*   
\q2
\v 6 Leso tamtamon tisov to taan tighit katin uraat tau Maaron pale ighamu leso igham mulin zi.” \x * \xo 3:6 \xt Mbo 98:2; Is 40:3-5, 52:10\x*   
\s1 Saveeŋ tau Yoan ivovotia pa tamtamon  
\p
\v 7 Eval tiina tilala to Yoan tighe i igham yaa pazi. Eemon Yoan isaav pazi ighe: “Yam tane, moot sasaghati natŋa! Sei imbaaŋ payam, ta alam sene? Mindai, yam aghe aŋguaaz taumim pa aatyavyav to Maaron tau ighe ivot ne? \x * \xo 3:7 \xt Mt 12:34, 23:33\x*   
\m
\v 8 Isaav ighe onoon yam apul ŋgar tsiam sasaghati ileple ve atoor ŋgar tsiam ila pa Maaron, na atotoi anooŋa tooni popoia siriv ivot gha taghita. Yam aghe Abaram paaghu tooni yam. Eemon anumeer gabua tana sov. Pa yau nasaav payam: Maaron, i irau isaav pa maet tane, ve tiburig timin Abaram paaghu tooni. \x * \xo 3:8 \xt Mt 7:17+; Yo 8:39; Ro 2:28+; Ga 3:7\x*   
\m
\v 9 Alooŋ. Nakavasi to Maaron igheen ila ai pughuzi ve isaŋan wa. Ai tisov tau anoŋazi popoia mako, ene aat nakavasi ighan zi tizi, ve tisik zi tizala yav ighan zi.” \x * \xo 3:9 \xt Mt 7:19\x*   
\p
\v 10 Eval tiina tilooŋ saveeŋ tana, ve tighason Yoan tighe: “Wai, ighe tauvene, pale nigham mindai?”   
\p
\v 11 Yoan iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Tamtamon tau le nonoghiiŋa ru, o igham ee pa iitete tau i le mako na. Ve tamtamon tau le aniiŋ na, i aat itaghon ŋgar raraate mon.” \x * \xo 3:11 \xt Mt 25:35+; Yems 2:15+; 1Yo 3:17\x*   
\p
\v 12 Zeran siriv to yauŋ takes tila to Yoan paam tighe irughuuz zi. Ve tighasoni tighe: “Mos puughu, yei tane pale nigham mindai?” \x * \xo 3:12 \xt Lu 7:29\x*   
\p
\v 13 Yoan iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Saawe tau ighe ayau takes, na ataghon imin tau daaba to gavman tisaav payam na. Apoi pa maet siriv izala paavo sov.”   
\p
\v 14 Ra zaaba siriv anazi tilam, ve tighasoni tighe: “Ve yei tane, pale nigham mindai?”  
\p Yoan iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Agham saghatin tamtamon sov. Ve aparoi zi, ve atombaan zi pa umbuuŋ maet toozi sov. Atuya tsiam tau tigham payam na, ena irau. Aghamu ve lolomim poia pani.”   
\p
\v 15 Saawe tana, eval tiina tighur matazi pa Mesia tighe malau mako pale ilam ivot. Tauvene tighita uraat to Yoan, ve tigham ŋgar ila lolozi tighe: “Mesia aat tauta ene, ma?”   
\p
\v 16 Tauvene Yoan isaav ghazooŋa pazi ighe: “Yau narughuuz gham pa yaa. Eemon ŋeer ee aat ilam murei payau. I tapiri tiina. Iliiv ghau kat. Uraat sorok imin polaaŋ waar to zuzuuŋa to aaghe, ene paam yau poiag irau to nagham pani mako. I pale igham Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ payam tomania yav. \f + \fr 3:16 \ft Zeran ŋgara siriv tighe yav tau Yoan isavia na, ŋgara tauvene: 1) Yesu pale igabiiz tamtamon ve ighur atuya pazi. 2) Ve siriv tighe yav tane ŋgara, ene tauvene: Yesu pale igharaat tamtamon tooni, ve ipasov ŋgar saghati toozi, imin yav ighan muun tau igheen tomania gol na, leso iŋgalaaŋ kat. 3) Ve siriv tighe yav tane izaa to saawe to Pentekos, tau Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ izilam imin yav.\f* \x * \xo 3:16 \xt Is 4:4-5; Mt 3:11; Yo 1:33; Mbaŋ 1:5, 2:3\x*   
\m
\v 17 Gabua to tiriiŋ wit, ta i ikisi ila niima ve isasaŋan. Pasaa, i pale igabiiz tamtamon ve ivureer zi imin ŋeer tau ilos wit tooni ve itiri izaa. Leso yaghur ivuvuur wit uuli ilale, ve wit anooŋa timburur tizi. Wit anooŋa tawe, i pale ighur poghania ila ruum to aniiŋ. Eemon wit uuli, i pale ikori ila yav ighani. Yav tawe, irau tirav matini mako. Ighanghan irau saawe.”  
\v 18 Tauvene Yoan ivovotia vaaru poia pa tamtamon, ve ipalot zi pa saveeŋ siriv paam, leso titoor ŋgar toozi.   
\s1 Erod ighur Yoan iloŋ ila ruum to yavyavuuŋ  
\r (Mt 14:3-4)  
\p
\v 19 Murei, Yoan iyaon Erod tau daaba to taan sirivu to Galilaia na. Pasaa, Erod isan toogha azaawa Erodias ve ivaii, ve igham ŋgar sasaghati siriv paam.  
\v 20 Tauta Erod iseeŋ ŋgar tooni saghati muul, ve ighur Yoan iloŋ ila ruum to yavyavuuŋ. \x * \xo 3:20 \xt Mk 6:17+\x*   
\s1 Yesu igham yaa  
\r (Mt 3:13-17; Mk 1:9-11)  
\p
\v 21-22 Saawe tau eval tiina tigham yaa, Yesu paam ila tomani zi ighe igham yaa. Saawe tau igham yaa ve isuŋsuŋ, sambam ikaak, ve Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ izilam imin mbuun gha izala paavo. Ra saveeŋ sambam ve izilam ighe: “Yau natug eemon ta yo. Yau lolog igheen tsio, ve yo ugham ghau lolog poia kat.” \x * \xo 3:21-22 \xt Mbo 2:7; Is 42:1; Mt 17:5; Yo 1:32\x*   
\s1 Pitiiŋ to Yesu puughu tooni  
\r (Mt 1:1-17)  
\p
\v 23 Yesu ndaman tooni irau tamoot ee saŋavul (30), ve i ipaburigin uraat tooni. Tamtamon tigham ŋgar tighe i Yosep naatu. Yosep tane, i Eli naatu. \x * \xo 3:23 \xt Lu 4:22; Yo 6:42\x*   
\m
\v 24 Eli, i Matat naatu. Matat, i Levi naatu. Levi, i Melki naatu. Melki, i Yanai naatu. Yanai, i Yosep naatu.  
\v 25 Yosep, i Matatias naatu. Matatias, i Amos naatu. Amos, i Naum naatu. Naum, i Esli naatu. Esli, i Nagai naatu.  
\v 26 Nagai, i Maat naatu. Maat, i Matatias naatu. Matatias, i Semein naatu. Semein, i Yosek naatu. Yosek, i Yoda naatu.  
\v 27 Yoda, i Yoanan naatu. Yoanan, i Resa naatu. Resa, i Zerubabel naatu. Zerubabel, i Sealtiel naatu. Sealtiel, i Neri naatu.  
\v 28 Neri, i Melki naatu. Melki, i Adi naatu. Adi, i Kosam naatu. Kosam, i Elmadam naatu. Elmadam, i Er naatu.  
\v 29 Er, i Yosua naatu. Yosua, i Elieser naatu. Elieser, i Yorim naatu. Yorim, i Matat naatu. Matat, i Levi naatu.  
\v 30 Levi, i Simeon naatu. Simeon, i Yuda naatu. Yuda, i Yosep naatu. Yosep, i Yonam naatu. Yonam, i Eliakim naatu.  
\v 31 Eliakim, i Melea naatu. Melea, i Mena naatu. Mena, i Matata naatu. Matata, i Natan naatu. Natan, i David naatu.  
\v 32 David, i Yesi naatu. Yesi, i Obet naatu. Obet, i Boas naatu. Boas, i Salmon naatu. Salmon, i Nason naatu. \x * \xo 3:32 \xt Rut 4:17-22\x*   
\m
\v 33 Nason, i Aminadap naatu. Aminadap, i Admin naatu. Admin, i Arni naatu. Arni, i Ezron naatu. Ezron, i Peres naatu. Peres, i Yuda naatu. \x * \xo 3:33 \xt Gnp 29:35\x*   
\m
\v 34 Yuda, i Yakop naatu. Yakop, i Isak naatu. Isak, i Abaram naatu. Abaram, i Tera naatu. Tera, i Naor naatu.  
\v 35 Naor, i Serug naatu. Serug, i Reu naatu. Reu, i Peleg naatu. Peleg, i Eber naatu. Eber, i Sela naatu.  
\v 36 Sela, i Kainan naatu. Kainan, i Arpaksad naatu. Arpaksad, i Sem naatu. Sem, i Noa naatu. Noa, i Lamek naatu.  
\v 37 Lamek, i Metusela naatu. Metusela, i Enok naatu. Enok, i Yared naatu. Yared, i Malalel naatu. Malalel, i Kenan naatu.  
\v 38 Kenan, i Enos naatu. Enos, i Set naatu. Set, i Adam naatu. Ve Adam, i Maaron naatu. \x * \xo 3:38 \xt Gnp 1:27\x*   
\c 4  
\s1 Sadan itoov Yesu  
\r (Mt 4:4-11; Mk 1:12-13)  
\p
\v 1-2 Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ izeev Yesu, ve i ipul yaa Yordan ve imuul ila. Ila ivot nugh ŋginaaŋa ve ileep ta sewe irau mboŋ tamoot ru. Saawe tana, Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ igham pooz pani pa laghooŋ tooni, ve Ŋeer Saghati ivotvot tooni, ve itovtoova. Mboŋ tamoot ru tana isov, ve Yesu pitoola kat. Pasaa, saawe isov tana, i ighan aniiŋ eta mako.   
\p
\v 3 Ra Ŋeer Saghati isaav pani ighe: “Laak, isaav ighe yo Maaron Naatu, na usaav pa maet tane, ve imin lem aniiŋ.”   
\p
\v 4 Eemon Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Maaron aliiŋa tau tiboode na isaav tauvene:  
\q2 ‘Aniiŋ mon irau igham tamtamon tileep poi ne mako.’” \x * \xo 4:4 \xt Lo 8:3; Is 55:1-2\x*   
\p
\v 5 Ra Sadan ighamu ve tizala nugh ee tau igheen saaŋa kat, ve rekia mon itotoi nugh naol isov tau kinik to taan tiŋginŋgin zi na pani,  
\v 6-7 ve isaav pani ighe: “Ughita. Gabua popoia ve tintiina tawe tau tamtamon tipakur zi ve tighamgham ezazi pani na, ene Maaron ipul zi tisov tighenaar ila yau nimag wa. Tauvene sei tau yau naghe nagham gabua tawe pani, ene irau nagham pani mon. Ve yo taum. Isaav ighe uput aghem payau ve upakur ghau, yau aat napuliir gabua naol tawe tisov timin lem, leso uŋgin zi.” \x * \xo 4:6-7 \xt 12:31; 1Yo 2:15, 5:19\x*   
\p
\v 8 Eemon Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Maaron aliiŋa ziiri ite tau tiboode na isaav tauvene:  
\q2 ‘Uput aghem pa Tiina tsio Maaron mon, ve ubees pa i zigani.’” \x * \xo 4:8 \xt Lo 6:13, 10:20\x*   
\p
\v 9 Ra Sadan ighamu muul gha tila Yerusalem, ve tizala tiyooz ila Rumei Tiina paavo tau igheen saaŋa kat na, ve isaav pani tauvene: “Isaav ighe onoon yo Maaron Naatu, na uleep ta sene, ve uyatov ghom uzila.  
\v 10-11 Pa Maaron aliiŋa tau tiboode na isaav ighe:  
\q2 ‘I pale imbaaŋ aŋela tooni to tiŋgin ghom.  
\q2 Yes pale tikis ghom, ve tipalot ghom.  
\q2 Leso maet ikaria aghem sov.’” \x * \xo 4:10-11 \xt Mbo 91:11+\x*   
\p
\v 12 Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Eemon Maaron aliiŋa ziiri ite isaav tauvene:  
\q2 ‘Utoov Tiina tsio Maaron tapiri sov.’” \x * \xo 4:12 \xt Lo 6:16; 1Kor 10:9\x*   
\p
\v 13 Tauvene Sadan itoov Yesu pa eez maata maata le mako, ra ipuli, ve ila isaŋan pa saawe ite paam. \x * \xo 4:13 \xt Hib 2:18, 4:15\x*   
\s1 Yesu ipaburigin uraat tooni izi Galilaia  
\r (Mt 4:12-17; Mk 1:14-15)  
\p
\v 14 Yesu imuul ila pa Galilaia ve Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ tapiri tiina igheen tooni. Tauvene vaaru ilaan irau taan sirivu tawe.  
\v 15 I ipaghazoŋai tamtamon pa Maaron aliiŋa irau nugh nugh ila rumei toozi lolozi. Ve tamtamon tisov tau tilooŋ saveeŋ tooni na, tipait eeza.   
\s1 Tamtamon to Nasaret tizor Yesu  
\r (Mt 13:53-58; Mk 6:1-6)  
\p
\v 16 Yesu imuul ila pa nugh tooni puughu Nasaret tau i itum pani gha imin olman. Ilepleep le umbom patabuyaaŋ ivot, ra itaghon ŋgar tau monmon ighamghamu na, ve iloŋ ila rumei toozi, leso isuŋ tomani zi. I iburig iyooz, leso iwaat Maaron aliiŋa pazi. \x * \xo 4:16 \xt Mt 2:23\x*   
\m
\v 17 Tizuzuun rau to propet Isaia ila tooni, ve i iraraava ve maata itaghoni izi le indeeŋ saveeŋ ziiri ee tau isaav ighe:   
\q1
\v 18-19 “Maaron Avuvu ileep tomani ghau.  
\q2 Pasaa, i ighur ghau to navotia vaaru poia pa yes mbolaaŋa.  
\q2 Ve imbaaŋ ghau nalam to nasaav pa yes tau tileep ila koiazŋa nimazi na tauvene:  
\q2 ‘Avot ala! Yam aleep ila koiamimŋa nimazi muul mako.’  
\q2 Ve yes tau matazi kumkuuma na, Maaron ighe yau nasaav pazi tauvene: ‘Matamim pakia ve aghita nugh.’  
\q2 Ve yes tau koiazŋa titatan zi ve tighurghur pataŋani pazi na, Maaron imbaaŋ ghau nalam to nagham mulin zi.  
\q2 Ve i ighe navotia saveeŋ pa tamtamon tauvene: Saawe to Ŋeer Tiina itotoi poia tooni ivot ighazooŋ, tauta ivot wa.” \x * \xo 4:18-19 \xt Is 61:1+; Yo 3:34; 2Kor 6:2\x*   
\p
\v 20 Yesu iwaat saveeŋ tane le isov, ra ilulun rau tana muul, ve ighuru ila to ŋeer tau iŋgin rumei, ve mboole izi, leso ivotia mos pazi. Tamtamon tisov tau tilepleep na, matazi ila pani,  
\v 21 ve i ipaburigin saveeŋ tooni ighe: “Saveeŋ tau aazne alooŋa, ene ighur anooŋa ivot wa.”   
\p
\v 22 Tamtamon tisov tau tilooŋ saveeŋ tooni na, tirur pa saveeŋ popoia tau ivot ila aavo na, ve tipaiti. Eemon tighe: “Wai, ŋeer tane, Yosep naatu. Mindai ta i irau isavia saveeŋ tauvene?” \x * \xo 4:22 \xt Mk 1:22; Yo 6:42, 7:15\x*   
\p
\v 23 Tauvene Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Yau nawatagh: Yam pale asik saveeŋ ziiri ee tau monmon ivotvot ila tamtamon avozi na payau aghe: ‘Dokta, matam iŋgal ve ugharaat taum imin maata.’ Yei nilooŋ tighe yo ughamgham gabua tintiina izi nugh Kapernaum. Mindai ta ugham zi izi nugh tsio puughu tane mako?” \x * \xo 4:23 \xt Mk 1:21+\x*   
\p
\v 24 Yesu iseeŋ saveeŋ tooni ighe: “Yau nasaav payam kat. Isaav ighe tamtamon eta imin propet to Maaron, ene aat tauu nugh tooni puughu tighamu mako. \x * \xo 4:24 \xt Mt 13:57; Yo 4:44\x*   
\m
\v 25 Eemon yau nasaav payam kat: Saawe to propet Ilia, uman izi rigta mako kat irau ndaman tol ve sirivu, le pitool tiina ivot irau nugh. Saawe tana, zinaara katini to Israel tilepleep. \x * \xo 4:25 \xt 1King 17:1+\x*   
\m
\v 26 Eemon Maaron imbaaŋ Ilia ila to iuul toozi eta mako. Imbaaŋo ila pa naar ee to nugh Zarepat tau igheen ila taan sirivu to Sidon.  
\v 27 Ve saawe to propet Elisa tauvene paam. Kolekole igham tamtamon katini to Israel. Eemon Elisa iuul toozi eta mako. Naeman tau ŋeer to taan sirivu to Siria na, i mon ta Elisa iuule le tiini poia.” \x * \xo 4:27 \xt 2King 5:1+\x*   
\p
\v 28 Yes tau tileep ila rumei tana loolo na, tilooŋ saveeŋ tane, le ireu lolozi.  
\v 29 Tauvene tiburig gha tiziir Yesu pa nugh toozi, ve tighamu tila tivot maetaaz tau iyooz ila nugh ziige, leso tisipiira izila. (Nugh toozi igheen izala loloz.)  
\v 30 Eemon mako. I ipas ghi ila sosozi, ve ighau gha ila. \x * \xo 4:30 \xt Yo 8:59, 10:39\x*   
\s1 Yesu iziir avuvu saghati pa ŋeer ee  
\r (Mk 1:21-28)  
\p
\v 31 Yesu izila ivot nugh Kapernaum to Galilaia, ve ileep tomani zi. Saawe to umbom patabuyaaŋ, i ipaghazoŋai zi pa Maaron aliiŋa.  
\v 32 Yes tilooŋ saveeŋ tooni le tirur pa ŋgar tooni. Pasaa, saveeŋ tooni, toman tapiri. Ve isavsaav imin tamtamon tau i le eeza pa uraat tauvene. \x * \xo 4:32 \xt Mt 7:28+; Yo 7:46\x*   
\p
\v 33 Saawe tana, ŋeer ee ilepleep tomani izi ila rumei loolo. I, avuvu saghati izeeva. Tauvene iboob aliiŋa tiina ighe:  
\v 34 “Aii, Yesu to Nasaret, ulam sene pasaa? Yei nimbaaŋ payo? Ma ulam ughe uvaghamun ghei? Yau nawatagh ghom wa. Yo ŋeer patabuyaaŋ to Maaron.” \x * \xo 4:34 \xt Mt 8:29; Mk 1:24; Yems 2:19\x*   
\p
\v 35 Eemon Yesu iyaoni ighe: “Ai! Yo uneneeŋ! Upuli ve ughau ula!” I isaav tauvene, ve avuvu saghati isik ŋeer tawe izila taan ila eval tiina naghozi. Eemon ivaghamunia mako. Ipuli ve ighau ila.   
\p
\v 36 Yes tau tighita gabua ŋgereeta tana, tisov tirur ve tivasavo zi tighe: “Wai, saveeŋ tane, gabua mindai? Ŋeer tane, i le eeza ve tapiri. Aghita. Avuvu sasaghatizi tileep ila i saamba. Pasaa, i isavsaav pazi, ve tiloŋlooŋ aliiŋa gha tighau tila.”  
\v 37 Puughu tane ta Yesu vaaru ilaan irau nugh tisov to taan sirivu tawe.   
\s1 Yesu igharaat moroghooŋ to Petrus rauliva  
\r (Mt 8:14-15; Mk 1:29-31)  
\p
\v 38 Yesu ipul rumei tana, ve malmali ila Simon ruum tooni, ve iloŋ ila. Simon rauliva imorooŋ le tiini iyes kat gha ighengheen. Tauvene tighason Yesu tighe iuule.  
\v 39 Yesu ila iyooz igharau olman tinazi ziige, ve iyaon moroghooŋ tawe. Rekia mon ve moroghooŋ ighau, ve tiini poia. Ra olman tinazi iburig gha ila igharaat lezi aniiŋ.   
\s1 Yesu igharaat moroghooŋa katini  
\r (Mt 8:16-17; Mk 1:32-34)  
\p
\v 40 Tilepleep le aaz izila, ra tamtamon tiyauur zetazŋa tisov tau moroghooŋ maata maata igham zi na tilam to Yesu, leso iuul zi. I ighur niima izala tamtamon eŋaeŋa pavozi, ve igharaat zi le tisov tinizi poia.  
\v 41 Avuvu sasaghati paam. Tipul tamtamon katini ve tighau tila, ve tiboboob tighe: “Yo Maaron Naatu!” Pasaa, yes tiwatagh tighe i Mesia. Eemon i iyaon zi, ve isaav ariaaŋ pazi ighe: “Aneneeŋ!” \x * \xo 4:41 \xt Mk 1:24, 3:11+\x*   
\s1 Yesu ipul Kapernaum ve igham uraat izi nugh siriv  
\r (Mk 1:35-39)  
\p
\v 42 Mboŋ le nughizau, ra Yesu iburig gha ipul ruum, ve ilaagh ila pa nugh ŋginaaŋa ee ighe zigani ileep ta sewe. Eemon mako. Eval tiina tiilo ve titaghoni tilam. Tilam peria tooni, ve tiŋguruuta tighe ileep tomani zi. \x * \xo 4:42 \xt Mt 14:23; Mk 6:46\x*   
\m
\v 43 Eemon i isaav pazi ighe: “Yau aat nala ve navotia saveeŋ pa pooz to nugh sambam izi nugh siriv paam. Pasaa, Maaron imbaaŋ ghau nalam pa uraat tane.” \x * \xo 4:43 \xt Lu 8:1\x*   
\m
\v 44 Tauta Yesu ilaagh irau taan sirivu to Yudea, ve ivovotia Maaron aliiŋa iloŋ ila rumei toozi.   
\c 5  
\s1 Yesu ipoi tamtamon siriv timin mbiwa tooni  
\r (Mt 4:18-22; Mk 1:16-20)  
\p
\v 1 Saawe ee, Yesu iyozyooz izi nari to yaa naliu Genesaret, \f + \fr 5:1 \ft Yaa naliu Galilaia eeza ite, ene Genesaret. Ve eeza ite imin tol, ene Tiberias.\f*  
\m ve eval tiina tilam tilivuti ve tivagiriŋi zi tighe le tilooŋ Maaron aliiŋa.  
\v 2 Yesu maata ila le ighita waaŋ ru tau titataan zi tizaa. Uraata to waaŋ tawe, yes zeran to ghamuuŋ iigh. Yes tipul waaŋ ve tila tiyaim puugh toozi.  
\v 3 Waaŋ ru tawe, ee to Simon. Yesu ila izaa waaŋ tana, ve isaav pa Simon ighe: “Ulam uzuur waaŋ ivot rig.” Tauvene Simon izaa ve igham waaŋ ivot ila rig, ra Yesu mboole izi, ve ipaghazoŋai eval tiina pa Maaron aliiŋa.   
\p
\v 4 Isavsaav le isov, ra isaav pa Simon ighe: “Tavot tala mazavan, ve araar puugh tsiam izila, mako agham lemim iigh.”   
\p
\v 5 Simon iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Wai tiina, yei nikaria uraat mboŋ gha ilam nughizau, ve nigham iigh eta mako. Eemon yo usaav, tauta aat naraar puugh izila muul.” \x * \xo 5:5 \xt Yo 21:3+\x*   
\m
\v 6 Tauvene yes titaghon Yesu aliiŋa, le iigh katini tighoon ila puugh toozi ve rigmon kanaŋ puugh perekia.  
\v 7 Tauvene tikiyav zetazŋa siriv tau tileep ila waaŋ ite na, leso tilam tiuul zi. Yes tilam ve tipit iigh tau tighoon ila puugh na, ve tizila waaŋ ru tana le rigmon kanaŋ timarum.   
\p
\v 8 Simon Petrus ighita gabua tana, le itap izi Yesu aaghe puughu, ve isaav pani ighe: “Tiina, upul ghau ve ula! Pa yau ŋeer to ghamuuŋ sosor.” \x * \xo 5:8 \xt Is 6:5\x*   
\m
\v 9-10 I isaav tauvene pasaa, yesŋa zeetŋa tau tileep izala waaŋ na, tirur pa iigh katini tau tigham zi na. Tighita gabua tana imin gabua ŋgereeta ee. Ve yes mon mako. Zebedi natŋa ru Yakobus gha Yoan tau yesŋa Petrus tiluplup zi pa uraat na, yesuru tirur pa gabua tana paam.  
\p Eemon Yesu isaav pa Petrus ighe: “Uroi sov. Aazne ve ila, yo pale ugham tamtamon tauvene.”  
\v 11 Ra tiloŋ tila tigud waaŋ toozi tizaa, ve tipuliir gabua toozi naol isov tizi tileplez, ve titaghon Yesu gha yesŋa tila. \x * \xo 5:11 \xt Lu 5:28, 14:33; Pil 3:7+\x*   
\s1 Yesu igharaat ŋeer ee tau mbotmboot kolekole ighamu  
\r (Mt 8:2-4; Mk 1:40-45)  
\p
\v 12 Saawe ee, Yesu ilepleep izi nugh ee, ve ŋeer ee ilam. Kolekole ighamu le tiini isov isaghat. I ighita Yesu, le itap izi aaghe puughu, ve ighur naagho izila pa taan, ra itaŋ raraini ighe: “Oyai, tiina tsiau, isaav ighe lolom pa uleeŋ ghau, yo irau ugharaat ghau tinig poia. Leso naŋgalaaŋ ila Maaron maata.”   
\p
\v 13 Yesu niima ikisi, ve isaav pani ighe: “Poia. Yau aat nauul ghom. Leso uŋgalaaŋ ila Maaron maata. Aiyo, tinim poia!” I isaav tauvene, ve rekia mon kolekole ighau pa ŋeer tana le tiini poia.   
\p
\v 14 Ra Yesu iŋgalsekini ighe isavia gabua tana vaaru pa tamtamon eta sov. Ve isaav pani ighe: “Ulooŋ. Aazne, tinim poia wa. Tauvene malmalim ula, ve utotoi taum pa ŋeer eta to watooŋrau, ve ugham watooŋrau pa Maaron itaghon tutuuŋ tau Mose isavia na. Leso upaghazoŋai taum pa tamtamon, ve tiwatagh tighe tinim poia ve uŋgalaaŋ ila Maaron maata wa.” \x * \xo 5:14 \xt Wkp 14:1+; Lu 17:14\x*   
\p
\v 15 Eemon mako. Yesu vaaru ilanlaan ila le irau nugh. Tauvene eval tiina kat tilala tighe tilooŋ saveeŋ tooni, ve i igharaat moroghooŋ toozi.  
\v 16 Tauta saawe siriv, i ilala pa nugh ŋginaaŋa. Leso zigani ileep ve isuŋ. \x * \xo 5:16 \xt Mt 14:23; Mk 1:35, 6:46\x*   
\s1 Yesu igharaat ŋeer narape ee ve ireu sosor tooni  
\r (Mt 9:1-8; Mk 2:1-12)  
\p
\v 17 Saawe ee, Yesu ipaghazoŋai tamtamon pa Maaron aliiŋa, ve zeran tutuuŋa tomania ŋgara siriv to tutuuŋ tileep tomani zi paam. Zeran tawe, siriv tileep nugh naol to Galilaia ve tilam, siriv tileep taan sirivu to Yudea ve tilam, ve siriv tileep Yerusalem ve tilam. Maaron tapiri ighengheen tomania Yesu, tauvene i irau igharaat yes moroghooŋa le tinizi poia.   
\p
\v 18 Yesu isavsaav ve malau mako na, zeran siriv tibaad ŋeer narape ee izala boor gha tilam. Ŋeer tawe, aaghe imaat. Irau ilaagh mako. Yes tiil eez tighe tighamu tiloŋ tila ve tighuru izi Yesu naagho.  
\v 19 Eemon eval tiina tipoon zi. Tauvene tigham narape tana, ve titaghon ndeet tizala pa ruum paavo. Ra tipas atov siriv ighau, ve titughu tomania moogh tooni iŋarui Yesu izila, le igheen izi naagho.   
\p
\v 20 Yesu ighita zeran tana ghuruuŋ ila toozi iyaryaaŋ kat. Tauvene isaav pa narape tana ighe: “Ŋeer tsiau, sosor tsio, yau nareua wa.” \x * \xo 5:20 \xt Lu 7:48\x*   
\p
\v 21 Zeran tutuuŋa ve yes ŋgara to tutuuŋ tilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve tigham ŋgar naol, ve tivasavo zi tighe: “Wai, ŋeer tane, i sei ta ivelegh Maaron tauvene? Tamtamon eta irau ireu sosor mako. Maaron mon, o irau ireu sosor.” \x * \xo 5:21 \xt Is 43:25; Mika 7:18; Lu 7:49\x*   
\p
\v 22 Yesu ighilaal ŋgar toozi wa. Tauvene ighason zi ighe: “Puughu mindai ta yam agham ŋgar naol ila lolomim?  
\v 23-24 Saa saveeŋ ta raurauai payau to nasavia, leso yam aghur ila? Nasaav pa ŋeer tane naghe: ‘Sosor tsio, yau nareua wa’, ma nasaav pani naghe: ‘Yo uburig ve ulaagh.’ Eemon yau naghe yam awatagh kat tauvene: Tamtamon Naatu, i eeza pa rewaaŋ sosor to tamtamon izi taan.” Ra isaav pa narape tana ighe: “Yau nasaav payo: Uburig, ugham moogh tsio, ve umuul ula pa ruum.”   
\p
\v 25 Rekia mon ŋeer tana iburig iyooz ila eval tiina matazi, igham moogh tooni, ve ipapait Maaron eeza pa tapiri ve poia tooni, ve imuul ila pa ruum tooni.  
\v 26 Yes tau tighita gabua ŋgereeta tana, tisov tirur pa Maaron tapiri, ve roiŋ tiina igham zi, ve tipait Maaron eeza pa tapiri ve poia tooni tighe: “Wai, gabua tau aazne taghita, ene ite kat!”   
\s1 Yesu ipoi Levi imin mbiwa tooni  
\r (Mt 9:9-13; Mk 2:13-17)  
\p
\v 27 Yesu igharaat narape tana le isov, ra ipul nugh tawe, ve ilaagh ila rig, ve ighita ŋeer ee to yauŋ takes ilepleep ila niia to uraat, eeza Levi. Yesu isaav pani ighe: “Yo ulam, utaghon ghau!”  
\v 28 Tauvene Levi iburig, ipul gabua tooni naol isov izi ileple, ve itaghon Yesu gha yesuru tila. \x * \xo 5:28 \xt Lu 5:11, 14:33; Pil 3:7+\x*   
\p
\v 29 Murei ra, Levi igham ghanghaniiŋ tiina pa Yesu izi ruum tooni. Saawe tana, Levi zeetŋa katini to yauŋ takes tomania tamtamon siriv tilam tileep tomani zi paam, ve yesŋa tilup zi pa ghanghaniiŋ.  
\v 30 Zeran tutuuŋa siriv tomania zetazŋa siriv tau lezi ŋgar tintiina pa tutuuŋ na, tighita gabua tana, ve tiyau avozi pa mbiwa to Yesu tighe: “Wai, mindai ta yamŋa zeran to ghamuuŋ takes, ve yes to ghamuuŋ sosor alup gham pa ghanghaniiŋ ve ghunuuŋ?” \x * \xo 5:30 \xt Lu 15:1+\x*   
\p
\v 31 Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Yes tau tinizi poia na, dokta le uraat pazi mako. Yes moroghooŋa mon o, i le uraat pazi.  
\v 32 Yau tauvene paam. Nalam pa poiŋ tamtamon duduŋazi mako. Nalam to napoi yes to ghamuuŋ sosor. Leso tipul ŋgar toozi sasaghati ileple, ve titoor ŋgar toozi ila pa Maaron.” \x * \xo 5:32 \xt Yo 3:17; 1Tim 1:15\x*   
\s1 Ghasoniiŋ pa ŋgar to ŋgunuuŋ tauun pa ghaniiŋ aniiŋ  
\r (Mt 9:14-15; Mk 2:18-20)  
\p
\v 33 Tamtamon siriv tisaav pa Yesu tighe: “Saawe naol, ŋeer rughuzaaŋa Yoan ziŋeera, tiŋgunŋgun tauzi pa ghaniiŋ aniiŋ itaghon suŋuuŋ ŋgara. Ve zeran tutuuŋa ziŋerazi tighamgham tauvene paam. Eemon mbiwa tsio titaghon ŋgar tauvene mako. Saawe isov, tighanghan ve tighunghun.”   
\p
\v 34 Yesu iyol ghasoniiŋ toozi ighe: “Isaav ighe ŋeer eta ivai paaghu, ve yesŋa zeetŋa tilup zi pa ghanghaniiŋ to vaiŋ tooni, pale irau agham zi lolozi ipataŋan ve tiŋgun tauzi pa ghaniiŋ aniiŋ? Mako.  
\v 35 Eemon murei, saawe eta pale ivot, o tikis vaiŋ paaghu tana, ve tighamu ipul zeetŋa gha ila. Saawe tana, zeetŋa pale lolozi ipataŋan, ve tiŋgun tauzi pa ghaniiŋ aniiŋ.” \x * \xo 5:35 \xt Yo 16:5, 6, 20\x*   
\s1 Eez muŋgaana to suŋuuŋ irau ilup tomania eez paaghu to Yesu mako  
\r (Mt 9:16-17; Mk 2:21-22)  
\p
\v 36 Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane pazi paam ighe: “Tamtamon eta irau iraŋgat uuli tooni paaghu, ve isaii izala uuli tooni muŋgaana tau perekia na mako. Pa ighe igham tauvene, ene pale ivaghamunia uuli paaghu. Ve gabua ite. Uuli paaghu, ene raraate pa uuli muŋgaana mako.  
\v 37 Vaen tauvene paam. Irau tiliŋ vaen paaghu izila vaen paatu muŋgaana ne mako. \f + \fr 5:37 \ft Yes Yuda tighagharaat yaa paatu siriv pa mekmek uuli.\f*  
\m Pasaa, vaen paaghu pale ipasaria paatu muŋgaana le diŋia ve perekia. Mako vaen imaliŋ, ve paatu paam isaghat.  
\v 38 Tauvene vaen paaghu izila patuzi paghpaaghu, o poia. \x * \xo 5:38 \xt Hib 8:13\x*   
\m
\v 39 Eemon yes tau tighunghun vaen muŋgaana na, lolozi pa vaen paaghu mako. Pale tirere pani ve tighe: ‘Ee-e, taghun vaen muŋgaana, o poia.’” \f + \fr 5:39 \ft Nonoghiiŋa paaghu ve vaen paaghu ene izaa to eez paaghu to suŋuuŋ tau Krisi ipaburigini. Ve nonoghiiŋa muŋgaana ve vaen muŋgaana izaa to eez muŋgaana tau yes Yuda titaghoni pa suŋuuŋ toozi. Isaav ighe tatoova to talup eez ru tana, ene irau ighur mako. Tataghon eez to suŋuuŋ tau Yesu isavia na mon, o poia.\f* \x * \xo 5:39 \xt Ro 10:16\x*   
\c 6  
\s1 Tamtamon Naatu iŋgin umbom patabuyaaŋ  
\r (Mt 12:1-8; Mk 2:23-28)  
\p
\v 1 Umbom patabuyaaŋ ee, Yesu tomania mbiwa tooni tilaghlaagh ila uum to wit lolozi. Ve mbiwa tooni tiŋgoor wit anooŋa siriv ve tilugluuga, leso uuli ighau ve tighan anooŋa. \x * \xo 6:1 \xt Lo 23:25\x*   
\p
\v 2 Tauvene zeran tutuuŋa siriv tau tileep tigharau zi na, tisaav pazi tighe: “Ai, aazne, ene saawe to uraat mako. Ene umbom patabuyaaŋ to Maaron. Puughu mindai ta yam agham ŋgar tau isapir pa tutuuŋ to umbom patabuyaaŋ?” \x * \xo 6:2 \xt Igham 20:10, 34:21\x*   
\p
\v 3 Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Sinaiŋ muŋgaana tau isavia saawe tau kinik David yesŋa zeetŋa siriv pitool zi na, yam awaato, ma mako?  
\v 4 Saawe tana, David iloŋ ila balbaal patabuyaaŋ to Maaron, ve igham mberet patabuyaaŋ tau tighuru ila Maaron naagho na. Mberet tawe le ŋgalsekiiŋa tauvene: Tamtamon sorok irau tighani mako. Yes zeran to watooŋrau mon, o tighani. Eemon David igham mberet tawe gha ighani, ve irei siriv pa ziŋeera gha tighan paam.” \x * \xo 6:4 \xt Wkp 24:5+; 1Sam 21:1+\x*   
\p
\v 5 Ra Yesu iparwai saveeŋ tooni ighe: “Tamtamon Naatu, i Tiina tau iŋgin umbom patabuyaaŋ to Maaron.” \x * \xo 6:5 \xt Kol 2:16+\x*   
\s1 Yesu igharaat ŋeer ee tau niima imaat  
\r (Mt 12:9-14; Mk 3:1-6)  
\p
\v 6 Tileep le umbom patabuyaaŋ ite ivot, ra Yesu iloŋ ila rumei ee, ve ipaghazoŋai tamtamon pa Maaron aliiŋa. Ve ŋeer ee ilepleep tomani zi. I niima tapir imaat.  
\v 7 Ŋgara siriv to tutuuŋ tomania zeran tutuuŋa siriv tilepleep tomani zi paam. Yes tighe tipayooz Yesu pa savsaveeŋ. Tauvene timarari tighe tighita: Pale i igharaat moroghooŋa eta ila saawe to umbom patabuyaaŋ, ma mako?  
\v 8 Eemon Yesu iwatagh ŋgar toozi wa. Tauvene isaav pa ŋeer tau niima imaat na ighe: “Ulam uyooz izi sene.” Ŋeer tana ilooŋ Yesu aliiŋa, ve iburig ila iyooz igharauu.   
\p
\v 9 Ra Yesu ighason zi ighe: “Laak. Ŋgar sindei tau yam aghita aghe iduduuŋ pa tutuuŋ to Maaron? Tauul tamtamon ve tagham poghani zi pa saawe to umbom patabuyaaŋ, ma tagham saghatin zi? Tagham mulin zi pa pataŋani toozi, ma tavaghamun zi?”   
\p
\v 10 Yesu maata ila pazi tisov, ra isaav pa ŋeer tau niima isaghat na ighe: “Uyoot nimam iduduuŋ.” Tauvene ŋeer tana iyoot niima le niima poia muul.  
\v 11 Zeran tutuuŋa ve yes ŋgara to tutuuŋ tawe tighita gabua tana le ipas atezi. Tauvene tivasavo zi tighe pale tigham mindai pa Yesu.   
\s1 Yesu ighur tamtamon saŋavul ve ru timin mbaŋooŋa tooni  
\r (Mt 10:1-4; Mk 3:13-19)  
\p
\v 12 Saawe tana, Yesu izala pa loloz ee ighe isuŋ. Mboŋ tana, isuŋsuŋ ila le nughizau.  
\v 13 Ra ipoi yes tau titaghoni na tilam tilup zi, ve ighur tamtamon toozi saŋavul ve ru timin mbaŋooŋa tooni.  
\v 14 Zeran saŋavul ve ru tawe, ezazi tauvene: Simon (i, Yesu iwaat eeza ite ighe Petrus) yesuru taazi Andreas, Yakobus gha Yoan, Pilip, Patoromai,  
\v 15 Matayu, Tomas, Yakobus ite tau Alpai naatu na, Simon ite tau tiwaato tighe Selot, \f + \fr 6:15 \ft Selot, ene Yuda siriv tau ŋgar toozi iyaryaaŋ tighe tiziir gavman to Rom.\f*   
\m
\v 16 Yudas tau Yakobus naatu, ve Yudas Iskariot tau murei ighur Yesu ila koiŋa nimazi.   
\s1 Yesu igharaat moroghooŋa ve ivotia mos  
\r (Mk 3:7-12)  
\p
\v 17 Yesu tomania mbiwa tooni tipul loloz tawe, ve tizila le tivot nugh raraate ee, ve tiyooz ta sewe. Yesu ziŋeera katini, tomania eval tiina kat tila tileep tomani zi paam. Eval tiina tawe to nugh naol to Yudea ve Yerusalem, ve yes to nari tau tileep tigharau nugh Tiro ve Sidon na paam.  
\v 18 Tilam tighe tilooŋ Yesu saveeŋ tooni, ve igharaat moroghooŋ toozi. Ve yes tau avuvu sasaghati tivaghamun zi na, i izirziir avuvu sasaghati pazi le tinizi poia.  
\v 19 Eval tiina tau tilivuti na, tisov tizuari zi tighe le titutu rigta. Pasaa, tighilaal tighe tapiri to gharatooŋ yes moroghooŋa ivotvot ila tooni, ve ighagharaat moroghooŋa tisov tinizi poia.   
\s1 Savunugha titaghon pooz to nugh sambam ŋgara ve poia to Maaron izaa toozi?  
\r (Mt 5:1-12)  
\p
\v 20 Yesu maata ila pa mbiwa tooni, ve isaav pazi ighe:  
\q2 “Yam mbolaaŋa, tintinmim pa poia to Maaron tau izaa tsiam.  
\q2 Pasaa, yam aleep ila Maaron pooz tooni loolo wa. \x * \xo 6:20 \xt Mt 25:34; Yems 2:5\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 21 Yam tau aazne pitool gham na, tintinmim pa poia to Maaron tau izaa tsiam.  
\q2 Pasaa, gabua tau ambool pani na, Maaron pale igham payam le irau lolomim.  
\q2 Yam tau lolomim ipataŋan ve ataŋ na, tintinmim pa poia to Maaron tau izaa tsiam.  
\q2 Pa murei, yam pale lolomim poia kat ve aŋiŋ. \x * \xo 6:21 \xt Mbo 126:5+; Is 55:1+; Syg 7:16+\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 22 “Ve yam tau ataghon Tamtamon Naatu, ve tighur koi payam, ve tiziir gham pa lupuuŋ toozi, ve tisik saveeŋ veleghiiŋ payam, ve tivaghamunia ezamim na, yam paam, tintinmim pa poia to Maaron tau izaa tsiam. \x * \xo 6:22 \xt Yo 15:19, 16:2; 1Pe 4:14\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 23 Lolomim poia kat ve ayaat toman tintinmim. Pasaa, atuya tsiam tiina igheen izi nugh sambam ve isasaŋan gham. Ŋgar tau aazne tigham payam na, muuŋ timbuzŋa tigham pa yes propet tau tivotia Maaron aliiŋa na paam. \x * \xo 6:23 \xt Mbaŋ 5:41, 7:52; 1Tes 2:14+\x*   
\s1 Yes tau murei pale lolozi ipataŋan  
\q1
\v 24 “Oyai, yam tau kuaz tauŋa na, akaria taumim wa.  
\q2 Onoon, aazne lemim gabua tau igham gham lolomim poia. Eemon gabua tauu to murei, yam ezamim pani mako. \x * \xo 6:24 \xt Lu 16:25; Yems 5:1\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 25 Yam tau aazne arau kat pa aniiŋ ve gabua naol na, akaria taumim wa.  
\q2 Pa murei, yam pale ambool ve pitool gham.  
\b  
\q1 Yam tau aazne aŋiŋiŋ na, akaria taumim wa.  
\q2 Pa murei, yam pale lolomim ipataŋan ve ataŋ. \x * \xo 6:25 \xt Is 65:13\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 26 Ve yam tau aazne tamtamon tisov tipapait gham na, yam paam, akaria taumim wa.  
\q2 Pa muuŋ, timbumimŋa tighamgham tauvene pa propet karomŋa tau titoom tighe tivotia Maaron aliiŋa.” \x * \xo 6:26 \xt Yo 15:19; 1Yo 4:5; Yems 4:4\x*   
\s1 Taghur loloon pa koiaanŋa  
\r (Mt 5:38-48)  
\m
\v 27 Yesu isaav pazi muul ighe: “Yam tau aloŋlooŋ ghau ne, yau nasaav payam tauvene: Lolomim pa koiamimŋa. Tamtamon tisov tau tighur koi payam na, agham poghani zi. \x * \xo 6:27 \xt Ro 12:20\x*   
\p
\v 28 Yes tau tisik saveeŋ saghati payam na, asuŋ Maaron to igham poghani zi. Ve yes tau tigham saghatin gham na, aghur zi ila suŋuuŋ tsiam. \x * \xo 6:28 \xt Lu 23:34; Mbaŋ 7:60\x*   
\m
\v 29 Isaav ighe ŋeer eta iposai paŋam, na uyol niima sov. Utoor ghom ve iposai ziige ite paam. Ve isaav ighe ŋeer eta igham nonoghiiŋa tsio to ŋgoaaŋ, na upuli igham nonoghiiŋa ite tau unonogh ghom pani na paam. \x * \xo 6:29 \xt 1Kor 6:7\x*   
\m
\v 30 Isaav ighe tamtamon eta ighason ghom pa le gabua, na ugham pani mon. Ve isaav ighe ŋeer eta igham gabua tsio eta ila, na ughasoni to ipamuule sov. Upuli imin le. \x * \xo 6:30 \xt Lo 15:7+; 1Yo 3:17\x*   
\m
\v 31 Saa ŋgar tau aghe tamtamon tigham payam, na yam aat agham ŋgar raraate tauvene pazi paam. \x * \xo 6:31 \xt Mt 7:12\x*   
\p
\v 32 “Isaav ighe lolomim pa yes tau lolozi payam na mon, pale aliiv tamtamon siriv mindai? Mako. Pasaa, ŋgar tauvene, yes zeran to ghamuuŋ sosor tighamghamu paam.  
\v 33 Ve isaav ighe agham poghania yes tau tighamgham poghani gham na mon, pale aliiv tamtamon siriv mindai? Mako. Pasaa, ŋgar tauvene, yes zeran to ghamuuŋ sosor tighamghamu paam.  
\v 34 Ve isaav ighe agagabiiz yes tau tighe tigham bun ilat tsiam, ve yes tau awatagh zi aghe yes pale tiyat duduŋai bun toozi, na ayok pazi to tigham bun. [Eemon yes tau awatagh zi aghe yes irau tiyatu rekia mako, ene irau agham pazi mako.] Isaav ighe aghamgham tauvene, ene pale aliiv tamtamon siriv mindai? Pasaa, ŋgar tauvene, zeran to ghamuuŋ sosor tighamghamu paam. Tauvene yam ataghon ŋgar tane sov.   
\p
\v 35 Yam aat ataghon ŋgar ite tauvene: Lolomim pa koiamimŋa, ve agham poghani zi. Agham gabua pazi toman lolomim poia. Ve aghur matamim pazi to tiyat gabua tsiam sov. Leso agham lemim atuya tiina, ve amin Maaron Tiina Tau Iliiv Zimaronŋa Tisov na natŋa. Pasaa, yes zeran sasaghatizi, ve yes tau tighita poia tooni imin kaut sorok ve lolozi iveghveegh pani na, i ighamgham poghani zi paam. \x * \xo 6:35 \xt Ro 5:8\x*   
\m
\v 36 Tauvene lolomim isaghatin tamtamon ve auul zi, imin Tamamim Maaron loolo isaghatin zi ve iuluul zi.”   
\s1 Tagabiiz zetaanŋa taghe yes sasaghatizi rekia sov  
\r (Mt 7:1-6)  
\p
\v 37 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Agabiiz tamtamon aghe yes sasaghatizi rekia sov. Ve aghur pataŋani iŋarui zi pa sosor toozi rekia sov. Pa ighe yam agham tauvene, ene pale Maaron igham ŋgar raraate payam paam. Yam aat apul zeetmimŋa sosor toozi. Leso Maaron ipul sosor tsiam paam. \x * \xo 6:37 \xt Mt 6:14; Ro 2:1; Yems 2:13\x*   
\p
\v 38 Auul, o aghita uleeŋ ilat payam paam. Poia tau izaa tsiam, ene pale tiina le tiina kat. Pale imin tau tipavon nakaral le ivon kat ve imaliŋ. Pasaa, saa uleeŋ tau yam agham pa tamtamon, ene pale ŋgar eemon imuul pa yam taumim.” \x * \xo 6:38 \xt Lp 19:17; Mk 4:24; Ga 6:7+\x*   
\p
\v 39 Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane pazi paam, ighe: “Mindai, ŋeer eta tau maata kumkuuma na, irau igherev iitete tau maata kumkuuma paam, ve itotoi eez pani? Mako. Ene pale yesuru ve titap tizila puura. \x * \xo 6:39 \xt Mt 15:14\x*   
\m
\v 40 Ŋeer paaghu eta irau iliiv paduduŋaaŋ tooni ne mako. Eemon isaav ighe igham ŋgar to paduduŋaaŋ tooni isov imin le, ene pale yesuru ŋgar toozi raraate. \x * \xo 6:40 \xt Mt 10:24+; Yo 13:16, 15:20\x*   
\p
\v 41 Mindai ta yo rekia mon matam ila pa rabrab tau igheen ila etam ite maata? Eemon ai sirivu tiina tau igheen ila taum matam na, uyamaana mako.  
\v 42 Isaav ighe ai sirivu tiina igheen ila matam ve ughilaalo mako, mindai ta usaav pa etam ite ughe: ‘O, rabrab tau igheen ila matam na, yau irau nauul ghom ve natapaara izi.’ Yo ŋeer to karom! Upamir taum pa ghuruuŋ ila tsio! Ai sirivu tiina tau igheen ila taum matam na, upasu izi imin maata. Leso ughit poghania rabrab tau igheen ila etam ite maata na, ve utapaara izi.” \x * \xo 6:42 \xt Ro 2:1+\x*   
\s1 Taghilaal ai ila anoŋazi  
\r (Mt 7:16-18, 12:33-35)  
\p
\v 43 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Ai poia irau ighur anooŋa saghati mako. Ve ai saghati irau ighur anooŋa poia mako.  
\v 44 Tauvene ai anooŋa ta itotoi ai: Ene ai poia, ma saghati? Mindai, waar tuatua irau ighur anooŋa poia eta, leso tawidi? Mako.  
\v 45 Tamtamon tauvene paam. Zeran popoiazi tipapavon lolozi pa ŋgar popoia. Tauvene tighamgham ŋgar popoia ivotvot. Ve zeran sasaghatizi tipapavon lolozi pa ŋgar sasaghati. Tauta tighamgham ŋgar sasaghati ivotvot. Pasaa, ŋgar tau loloon ivon pani, tauta ivotvot ila avoon.   
\s1 Zeran ru tirau ruum  
\r (Mt 7:24-27)  
\p
\v 46 “Mindai ta yam awatwaat ghau aghe: ‘Tiina tsiau, Tiina tsiau’, eemon ataghon saveeŋ tsiau mako? \x * \xo 6:46 \xt Yems 2:26\x*   
\m
\v 47 Yau aat napaghazoŋai gham pa ŋgar tsiam tane. Tamtamon tisov tau tilam tsiau, ve tilooŋ saveeŋ tsiau ve titaghoni, \x * \xo 6:47 \xt Ro 2:13; Yems 1:22\x*   
\m
\v 48 ene yes timin ŋeer tau irau ruum. I ighelia ruum rira tizila le koŋia kat ila mboŋar tau igheen ila taan loolo na paavo. Tauvene saawe tau uman tiina izi, ve yaa ivot toman tapiri le itok ruum tooni, ruum katia mako. Pasaa, ŋeer tana irau ruum ariaaŋa.  
\v 49 Eemon tamtamon tau ighe iloŋlooŋ saveeŋ tsiau, ve itaghoni mako, ene i imin ŋeer tau ighelia ruum rira tizila tuŋia mako. Tauvene saawe tau uman tiina izi, ve yaa ivot toman tapiri le itok ruum tooni, rekia mon ruum imatit izila ve imbiriis gha ilale.”   
\c 7  
\s1 Daaba ee tau iŋgin zaaba to Rom na ighur ila ariaaŋ  
\r (Mt 8:5-13)  
\p
\v 1 Yesu ivotia saveeŋ tana pa tamtamon le isov, ra iburig gha iloŋ ila pa nugh Kapernaum.  
\v 2 Daaba ee to Rom ilepleep ta sewe. I iŋgin zaaba irau ndiŋndiŋ ee (100). Ve i le besooŋa ee, tau i loolo pani kat. Besooŋa tawe, moroghooŋ tiina ighamu le igharau ighe imaat.  
\v 3 Saawe tau daaba tana ilooŋ tighe Yesu ilam, i imbaaŋ zolmana siriv to yes Yuda tila pani. Leso tighasoni to ilam igharaat besooŋa tooni.  
\v 4 Tauvene tila tivot to Yesu, ve titaŋ raraini tighe: “Aa tiina tsiei, nighe yo uul ŋeer tawe, o poi. Pasaa, i ŋeer poia ee.  
\v 5 I loolo igheen to iit Yuda, ve irau lemai rumei paam.”   
\p
\v 6 Tauvene Yesu ila tomani zi gha yesŋa tila. Tila le tigharau ruum, ve daaba tana imbaaŋ ziŋeera siriv tila tivot to Yesu, ve tisavia aliiŋa pani tighe: “Tiina, daaba tsiei aliiŋa ilat payo ighe: ‘Ukari ghom pa laghooŋ sov. Pa yau poiag irau to uloŋ ulam ruum tsiau mako.  
\v 7 Ve yau poiag irau to nalat peria tsio ne mako. Eemon yau naghur ilat tsio tauvene: Isaav ighe usaav mon, ene aat besooŋa tsiau tiini poia.  
\v 8 Pasaa, yau nawatagh pa taug. Yau paam naleep ila daaba tsiau sambazi, ve tighur ghau to naŋgin yes zaaba tau tileep ila yau sambag ne. Tauvene isaav ighe nasaav pa zaaba tsiau eta naghe: “Ula!”, ene aat ila. Ve ighe nasaav pa ite: “Ulam!”, ene aat ilam. Ve ighe nasaav pa besooŋa tsiau eta naghe: “Ugham uraat tane.” Ene aat igham uraat tana itaghon aliŋag.’”   
\p
\v 9 Yesu ilooŋ daaba tana aliiŋa le irur pani. Ra itoor ghi, maata imuul pa eval tiina tau titaghoni na, ve isaav pazi ighe: “Yau nasaav payam kat. Yau naghita tamtamon eta to Israel tau ghuruuŋ ila tooni iyaryaaŋ kat imin daaba tawe ne mako.” \x * \xo 7:9 \xt Mt 15:28\x*   
\m
\v 10 Ra zeran tau daaba tana imbaaŋ zi na, timuul tila pa ruum, le tighita besooŋa tawe tiini poia.   
\s1 Yesu ipaburigin naar ee naatu pa mateegh  
\p
\v 11 Murei ra, Yesu tomania mbiwa tooni tiburig gha tila pa nugh ee, eeza Nain. Ve eval tiina titaghon zi gha yesŋa tila.  
\v 12 Tila tigharau ataman to didiiŋ tiina tau ilivut nugh tawe, ve tizaa to tamtamon siriv tau tibaad mateegh ee ve tivot. Ŋeer paaghu tau imaat na, naar ee naatu eemon kat. Tauvene eval tiina to nugh tawe tilaagh tomania naar tawe, gha yesŋa tila.   
\p
\v 13 Tiina Yesu ighita naar tana, le loolo isaghatini. Tauvene isaav pani ighe: “Olman tinazi, utaŋ sov!”  
\v 14 Ra iŋarui mateegh tana ila, ve ikis boor. Tauvene yes tau tibadbaad mateegh na aghezi tuŋia. Ve Yesu isaav ighe: “Ŋeer paaghu, yau nasaav payo: Uburig!” \x * \xo 7:14 \xt Lu 8:54; Mbaŋ 9:40\x*   
\p
\v 15 Rekia mon mateegh tana iburig, mboole izi, ve aavo pakia ve isavsaav. Ra Yesu ikis niima, ve ighuru ila to tiina. \x * \xo 7:15 \xt 1King 17:17+; 2King 4:32+\x*   
\m
\v 16 Tamtamon tighita gabua tana, le roiŋ tiina igham zi tisov, ve tipait Maaron eeza pa tapiri ve poia tooni tighe: “Onoon kat, aazne propet tiina ee ilam ileep tomani ghiit wa. Maaron maata iŋgal tamtamon tooni, tauta ilam to iuul zi!” \x * \xo 7:16 \xt Lu 1:68, 76, 24:19\x*   
\m
\v 17 Tauvene Yesu vaaru pa gabua tane ilaan irau nugh nugh to yes Yuda, ve ila pa nugh tisov tau tigheen tigharau taan toozi na paam.   
\s1 Yoan imbaaŋ ziŋeera ru tila to Yesu  
\r (Mt 11:2-19)  
\p
\v 18 Yoan ziŋeera siriv tila, ve tipaes pa Yoan pa gabua naol tau Yesu ighamgham zi na. Tauvene Yoan ipoi ziŋeera ru tilam,  
\v 19 ve imbaaŋ zi ighe tila to Tiina toit Yesu ve tighasoni tauvene: “Uleeŋa tau pale Maaron imbaaŋo ilam na, ene yo taum tane, ma nisaŋan ŋeer ite paam?”   
\p
\v 20 Tauvene yesuru tila tivot to Yesu, ve tisaav pani tighe: “Ŋeer rughuzaaŋa Yoan imbaaŋ ghei nilam to nighason ghom: Uleeŋa tau pale Maaron imbaaŋo ilam na, ene yo taum tane, ma nisaŋan ŋeer ite paam?”   
\p
\v 21 Saawe tana, Yesu igharaat tamtamon katini tau moroghooŋ sasaghati maata maata ivaghamun zi na, le tinizi poia. Ve izirziir avuvu sasaghatizi tighaughau pa tamtamon. Ve yes tau matazi kumkuuma na, i igharaat matazi le tighita nugh.  
\v 22 Tauvene iyol ghasoniiŋ toozi ighe: “Uraat tau yamru aghita ve saveeŋ tau alooŋa ne, amuul ala, ve apaesia pa Yoan. Asaav pani tauvene: Matazi kumkuuma tighita nugh, ve narapeŋa tiburig tilaagh. Yes tau kolekole igham zi na, tinizi poia ve tiŋgalaaŋ ila Maaron maata. Taliŋazi paamu tilooŋ saveeŋ, mateegha tiburig, ve yes mbolaaŋa tiloŋlooŋ vaaru poia.  
\v 23 Ve tamtamon tau ighe ighita uraat tsiau, ve irere ghau mako, ene pale tintini pa poia to Maaron tau pale izaa tooni.” \x * \xo 7:23 \xt Is 29:18, 35:5, 61:1; Lu 4:18\x*   
\s1 Yesu ipait Yoan  
\p
\v 24-25 Yoan mbaŋooŋa tooni tana tipul Yesu ve tila, ra Yesu isavia Yoan pa eval tiina tau yesŋa tilepleep na ighe: “Laak, saawe tau yam ala nugh ŋginaaŋa na, aghe aghita saa? Pispiiz raua tau yaghur iravu ila ilam? Ma ala aghe aghita ŋeer eta tau inonogh ghi pa uuli popoia? Mako. Aghita. Yes tau tinonogh zi pa uuli tau ŋgeretazi popoia, ve tigham lepoogh poia kat na, tileep izi nugh tauvene mako. Yes tileep ila ruum tintiina to yes kinik.  
\v 26 Tauvene yam ala aghe aghita saa kat ta sewe? Yam aat ala to aghita propet to Maaron, ne? Ve ene onoon. Yoan, i propet ee. Eemon yau nasaav payam: Yoan, i propet mon mako. I igham uraat siriv paam tau iliiv yes propet.  
\v 27 I ŋeer ta muuŋ tibood saveeŋ iŋaruini tauvene:  
\q2 ‘Ulooŋ. Yau pale nambaaŋ besooŋa tsiau ee imuuŋ payo.  
\q2 I pale ivotia aliŋag pa tamtamon, ve igharaat eez payo.’ \x * \xo 7:27 \xt Mal 3:1; Mk 1:2\x*   
\p
\v 28 Yau nasaav payam: Tamtamon tisov tau tinazŋa tipoop zi izi taan ne, eta eeza iliiv Yoan mako. Eemon isaav ighe ŋeer sorok eta ileep ila pooz to Maaron loolo ve ighita anooŋa tooni, ene pale ighit katin poia to Maaron le iliiv Yoan.”   
\p
\v 29 (Eval tiina tomania zeran siriv to yauŋ takes paam, tilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve tiyok pani tighe: “Maaron ŋgar tooni, ene iduduuŋ.” Tisaav tauvene pasaa, tighur ila Yoan saveeŋ tooni, ve tigham yaa wa. \x * \xo 7:29 \xt Lu 3:12\x*   
\m
\v 30 Eemon zeran tutuuŋa ve yes ŋgara to tutuuŋ tizor eez tau Maaron ighuru pazi. Tauta tigham yaa ila to Yoan mako.) \x * \xo 7:30 \xt Mt 21:32\x*   
\p
\v 31 Yesu iseeŋ saveeŋ tooni ighe: “Tamtamon to aazne, gabuazi mindai? Pale nasavi zi izaa to saa?  
\v 32 Yes timin ziŋer geegeu tau tirou taghon maaran aate, ve tiboboob ila pa zetazŋa tighe:  
\q2 ‘Yei nirav ambam payam,  
\q2 eemon ator mako.  
\q2 Ve nimbou taŋizŋiiz,  
\q2 eemon lolomim isaghat ve ataŋ mako.’   
\p
\v 33 “Aghita. Saawe tau ŋeer rughuzaaŋa Yoan ilam ve igham uraat tooni, i iŋgunŋgun tauu pa ghaniiŋ aniiŋ ve ghunuuŋ vaen. Eemon yam lolomim pani mako, ve aghe avuvu saghati izeeva.  
\v 34 Ve saawe tau Tamtamon Naatu ilam ve igham uraat tooni, i ighanghan ve ighunghun. Eemon i paam, yam lolomim pani mako, ve aghe: ‘Aghita. Ewe ŋeer tau ipaak yes zeran to ghamuuŋ sosor ve yes tau tiyauyau takes na, ve yesŋa tiluplup zi pa ghaniiŋ ve ghunuuŋ.’ \x * \xo 7:34 \xt Lu 5:29, 15:1+\x*   
\m
\v 35 Eemon yes tau titaghon ŋgar poia to Maaron na, tipaghazoŋai ŋgar tawe tighe ene iduduuŋ mon.”   
\s1 Livaa ee to ghamuuŋ sosor ve ŋeer tutuuŋa ee  
\p
\v 36 Zeran tutuuŋa toozi ee, eeza Simon, isain Yesu ighe ila ruum tooni pa ghanghaniiŋ. Tauvene Yesu ila ve mboole izi tomani zi, ve tighanghan. \x * \xo 7:36 \xt Lu 11:37\x*   
\p
\v 37 Livaa ee to nugh tawe, i livaa to ghamuuŋ sosor. I ilooŋ tighe Yesu ilepleep ila ruum to ŋeer tutuuŋa tana pa ghanghaniiŋ. Tauvene rekia mon igham ŋgoreeŋ, ve ila ighe ighita Yesu. Ŋgoreeŋ tawe, vaazi poia ve atuya tiina, ve igheen ila paatu paghuuna loolo.  
\v 38 I ila ivot, ve iput ghi izi Yesu muuri igharau aaghe, ve itaŋtaŋ. I isaghav Yesu aaghe, ve maata suuru itaptap izala, ve imusmusu pa daaba raua. Ve igham ŋgoreeŋ tana gha iliŋi izala Yesu aaghe.   
\p
\v 39 Ŋeer tutuuŋa tau isain Yesu pa ghanghaniiŋ na, ighita ŋgar tau livaa tana ighamu, ve igham ŋgar ila loolo ighe: “Wai, isaav ighe onoon ŋeer tane propet tauu to Maaron, kanaŋ ighilaal ighe livaa tau ikiskisi ne, i livaa to sosor.”   
\p
\v 40 Tauvene Yesu isaav pani ighe: “Simon, yau leg saveeŋ rig naghe nasavia payo.”  
\p Simon iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Poia. Mos puughu, usaav lak!”   
\p
\v 41 Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane pani ighe: “Saawe ee, zeran ru tila to ŋeer ee, ve tigham bun ila tooni. Ee igham maet denari \f + \fr 7:41 \ft Isaav ighe tamtamon eta igham uraat pa aaz ee, mboŋoozo ve ila ravrav, ene tigham denari ee pani imin le atuya.\f*  
\m ndiŋndiŋ liim (500), ve ite igham pius liim (50).  
\v 42 Eemon murei, yesuru irau tiyat bun toozi mako. Tauvene ŋeer tau igham maet pazi na, loolo isaghatin zi, ve ipul bun toozi. Laak, zeran ru tane, sei ta pale ighur loolo kat pa ŋeer tawe iliiv iitete?”   
\p
\v 43 Simon iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Aat i tau igham bun tiina, ve ŋeer tana ipul bun tooni na.”  
\p Yesu isaav pani ighe: “Aliŋam tana iduduuŋ.”  
\v 44 Ra itoor ghi, maata ila pa livaa tana, ve isaav pa Simon muul ighe: “Matam ilam pa livaa tane. Yo usain ghau pa ghanghaniiŋ, tauta nalam ruum tsio. Eemon ugham leg yaa to namin agheg mako. Ve ughita livaa tane. I imin agheg pa maata suuru, ve imusu pa daaba raua.  
\v 45 Ve saawe tau naloŋ nalam ruum tsio, yo uyaŋin payau rigta mako. Eemon livaa tane, i ikaria yaŋiniiŋ pa agheg. Ipuli mako.  
\v 46 Ve yo uliŋ ŋgoreeŋ rigta izala dabag mako. Eemon i iliŋ ŋgoreeŋ tau vaazi poia na izala agheg.   
\p
\v 47 “Tauvene yau nasaav payo. Onoon, livaa tane igham sosor naol. Eemon sosor tooni ta katini ne, yau nareu zi tisov. Tauta i loolo payau kat. Eemon isaav ighe ŋeer eta inumeer ighe i le sosor ŋgiira mon to Maaron ireua, ene pale loolo payau geeg mako.” \x * \xo 7:47 \xt Mbo 32:1\x*   
\m
\v 48 Yesu isavsaav pa Simon le isov, ra isaav pa livaa tana ighe: “Sosor tsio ta naol ne, yau nareu zi tisov wa.” \x * \xo 7:48 \xt Mt 9:2; Mk 2:5+; Lu 5:20+\x*   
\p
\v 49 Yes tau tileep tomania Yesu pa ghanghaniiŋ tana, tilooŋ saveeŋ tooni le tigham ŋgar naol, ve tivasavo zi tighe: “Ŋeer tane, i sei ta ighe ireu sosor to tamtamon paam?”   
\p
\v 50 Ve Yesu isaav pa livaa tana muul ighe: “Ghuruuŋ ila tsio, tauta igham mulin ghom wa. Ula toman lolom poia.” \x * \xo 7:50 \xt Mt 9:22; Mk 10:52; Lu 17:19, 18:42\x*   
\c 8  
\s1 Zilivaa siriv tilaghlaagh tomania Yesu ve tiuluule  
\p
\v 1 Yesu ipaburigin laghooŋ tooni muul, ve ilaagh irau nugh tintiina ve geegeu, ve ivovotia vaaru poia pa pooz to Maaron. Mbiwa tooni saŋavul ve ru,  
\v 2 tomania zilivaa siriv tilaagh tomania. Zilivaa tawe, muuŋ Yesu iziir avuvu sasaghati tighau pazi ve igharaat zi pa moroghooŋ toozi. Toozi ee, ene Maria to nugh Magdala. Muuŋ, Yesu iziir avuvu sasaghati liim ve ru tighau pani.  
\v 3 Ve Yoana tau azaawa Kuza iŋgin uraat siriv to Erod na, ve Susana, tomania zilivaa siriv paam. Yes tiuluul Yesu tomania mbiwa tooni pa lezi aniiŋ ve gabua siriv paam. \x * \xo 8:3 \xt Mt 27:55\x*   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to suruvaaŋ uuv  
\r (Mt 13:1-9; Mk 4:1-9)  
\p
\v 4 Saawe ee, eval tiina kat to nugh nugh tila to Yesu, ve i isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane pazi ighe:   
\p
\v 5 “Pai ee, ŋeer ee igham wit uuve, ve ila uum tooni ighe isuruuv zi. Saawe tau isusuruuv uuv tawe, siriv timburur tizi eez. Tauvene tamtamon tivaghaaza, ve man tiroov tila ve tighan suvinia.  
\v 6 Ve siriv timburur izi nugh tau mboŋar tiina igheen siiŋa, ve taan ŋgiira mon igheen izala paavo. Tauvene rekia mon titum tizaa. Eemon malau mako rauazi timalai ve timatmaat. Pasaa, taan tawe loolo gorgori. Yaa mako.  
\v 7 Ve uuv siriv, timburur ila waar tuatua lolozi. Tauvene waar tawe titum tomania wit tizaa, ve tinduruv zi le timatmaat.  
\v 8 Eemon uuv siriv titaptap tizala taan poia. Tauvene titum poi tizaa, ve tisov anoŋazi katini irau ndiŋndiŋ ee (100).”  
\p Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane le isov, ra isaav aliiŋa tiina ighe: “Tamtamon tau ighe le taliiŋa, i aat ilooŋ saveeŋ tane ve igham ŋgar pani poi.”   
\s1 Puughu tau Yesu isavsaav ila saveeŋ palelaaŋ  
\r (Mt 13:10-17; Mk 4:10-12)  
\p
\v 9 Mbiwa tooni tilooŋ saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane, ve tighasoni pa puughu.   
\p
\v 10 Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Pooz to Maaron, ene ŋgara yoŋgaaŋa. Eemon yam, Maaron igham poghani gham, ve ipaghazoŋai pooz tooni ŋgara le ighazooŋ payam. Ve tamtamon siriv, yes tiloŋlooŋ mos ila saveeŋ palelaaŋ mon. [Pasaa, lolozi ivool wa.]  
\q2 ‘Tauta aat matazi tighitghita gabua, eemon irau tighilaal puughu mako.  
\q2 Ve taliŋazi tiloŋlooŋ saveeŋ, eemon irau tigham ŋgar pani mako.’” \x * \xo 8:10 \xt Is 6:9+; Mbaŋ 28:26; Ro 11:8\x*   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to suruvaaŋ uuv puughu  
\r (Mt 13:18-23; Mk 4:13-20)  
\p
\v 11 Yesu isaav pazi muul ighe: “Saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane, puughu tauvene: Wit uuve, ene izaa to Maaron saveeŋ tooni. \x * \xo 8:11 \xt 1Pe 1:23\x*   
\m
\v 12 Uuv siriv tau timburur tizi eez, ene izaa to tamtamon tau tilooŋ Maaron aliiŋa, eemon rekia mon Sadan ila gha isan saveeŋ tawe ighau pa lolozi. Leso tighur ila to Maaron sov. Pa ighe tighur ila tooni, ene pale igham mulin zi.  
\v 13 Ve uuv siriv tau timburur izi nugh tau mboŋar tiina igheen siiŋa ve taan ŋgiira mon igheen izala paavo, ene izaa to tamtamon tau tilooŋ Maaron aliiŋa, ve tighamu toman lolozi poia kat. Eemon saveeŋ tawe igheen tuŋia ila lolozi mako. Yes timin aniiŋ tau waria izila taan loolo geeg mako. Tauvene tighur ila saawe tuuku mon, ve isaav ighe tovaaŋ eta ivot pazi, ene rekia mon titap ve tighur murizi pa Maaron.  
\v 14 Ve uuv siriv tau timburur ila waar tuatua lolozi, ene izaa to tamtamon tau tilooŋ saveeŋ to Maaron, eemon pataŋani naol to taan lepoogha, tomania kuaz ve gabua popoia maata maata tau tamtamon lolozi ighaar pani na, ene ikau ŋgar toozi. Tauvene saveeŋ tau igheen ila lolozi na, ighur anooŋa poia eta ivot mako. Yes timin uuv ta itum izaa eemon anooŋa imatuugh mako. \x * \xo 8:14 \xt 1Tim 6:9, 17; 2Tim 4:10\x*   
\m
\v 15 Ve uuv siriv tau titap tizala taan poia, ene izaa to yes tau ŋgar toozi poia ve lolozi eemon ila pa Maaron. Tauvene tilooŋ saveeŋ tooni, ve tikisi ariaaŋ ila lolozi, ve ghuruuŋ ila toozi ighurghur anooŋa popoia.” \x * \xo 8:15 \xt Hib 10:36; Yems 1:25\x*   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to lam  
\r (Mt 5:14-16; Mk 4:21-25)  
\p
\v 16 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Isaav ighe tamtamon eta itun lam, pale ipagudu pa oon, ma ighuru ila boor saamba? Mako. Pale isaroni izaa ituuk. Leso mbonari isul tamtamon tau tiloŋ tila ruum loolo na. \x * \xo 8:16 \xt Mt 5:15; Lu 11:33\x*   
\m
\v 17 Tauvene gabua eta irau iyooŋ mako. Gabua isov tau ŋgozaaŋ, ene pale tivoti zi le tighazooŋ. Ve ŋgar isov tau yoŋgaaŋ na, ene pale tivot mataghare le eval tiina tiwatagh zi. \x * \xo 8:17 \xt Mt 10:26; Lu 12:2\x*   
\m
\v 18 Tauvene aghur taliŋamim ve agham ŋgar poi pa saveeŋ tau aloŋlooŋa na. Pa tamtamon tau ighe iwatagh Maaron aliiŋa ve itaghoni, ene pale Maaron iuule ve iseeŋ ŋgar tooni pa ŋgar siriv muul. Eemon isaav ighe tamtamon eta inumeer sorok ighe i iwatagh Maaron aliiŋa, ve itaghoni mako, ene pale Maaron iwalaav ŋgar tooni tana pani, ve i ileep sorok.” \x * \xo 8:18 \xt Mt 13:12, 25:29\x*   
\s1 Yesu tiina ve tazŋa  
\r (Mt 12:46-50; Mk 3:31-35)  
\p
\v 19 Saawe tana, Yesu tiina ve tazŋa tilam tighe tighita. Eemon eval tiina tilivuti ve tipoon zi.  
\v 20 Tauvene tipaes pani tighe: “Ou, tinam tomania tazimŋa tilam tiyozyooz muuri we. Tighe tighit ghom.”   
\p
\v 21 Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Tinaŋ ve tazigŋa, ene yes tau tilooŋ Maaron saveeŋ tooni ve titaghoni.” \x * \xo 8:21 \xt Yo 15:14+; Ro 8:29; Hib 2:11+\x*   
\s1 Yesu isaav, ve yaghur ve dibom imaat  
\r (Mt 8:23-27; Mk 4:35-41)  
\p
\v 22 Saawe ee, Yesu tomania mbiwa tooni tizaa waaŋ, ve isaav pazi ighe: “Aiyo, tala tavool pa yaa naliu ziige ite.” Tauvene tivot tila.  
\v 23 Tiraav tila, ve Yesu izi igheen le loolo iveegh kat. Malau mako ve yaghur tiina izaa le ipei dibom tintiina. Ereman ivon ila waaŋ loolo, le rigmon kanaŋ timarum gha tilalez.   
\p
\v 24 Tauvene mbiwa tooni tila tivaaŋ Yesu, ve tisaav pani tighe: “Tiina, Tiina, uburig lak! Paita tamarum gha talaleen tane!” Yesu iburig ve iyaon yaghur ve dibom, le yaghur imot ve dibom imaat, ve taun izi.  
\v 25 Ra isaav pa mbiwa tooni ighe: “Ghuruuŋ ila tsiam igheen sindei?”  
\p Mbiwa tooni tighita gabua tana, le roiŋ tiina igham zi ve ŋgar toozi imbool. Ve tivasavo zi tighe: “Wai, ŋeer tane sei kat, ta isaav pa yaghur ve dibom, ve tilooŋ aliiŋa ve titaghoni?” \x * \xo 8:25 \xt Mbo 65:7, 89:9, 107:29\x*   
\s1 Yesu iziir avuvu saghati pa ŋeer ee izi nugh Gerasa  
\r (Mt 8:28-34; Mk 5:1-20)  
\p
\v 26 Yesu tomania mbiwa tooni tiraav tila tilooŋ nari to yes Gerasa tau igheen ila yaa naliu Galilaia ziige ite.  
\v 27 Yesu iyaat izi pa waaŋ, ve ŋeer ee to nugh tawe ilaagh ŋaruini ila. I, avuvu sasaghati katini tizeeva le ŋgar tooni ikaukau kat. Tauvene muuŋ ve ilam, i inonogh ghi pa uuli eta mako. Ilaghlaagh tiini ŋginaaŋa. Ve ileep ila ruum eta mako. Ilepleep iloŋ ila maet puura siriv tau tigharaat zi timin naal pa mateegha.   
\p
\v 28-29 I ighita Yesu, le iyak saghat, ve itap izi Yesu naagho. Yesu isaav ariaaŋ pa avuvu saghati tau izeev ŋeer tana ighe ipuli ve ighau ila. Eemon i iboob aliiŋa tiina ighe: “Aii Yesu! Yo Maaron Tiina Tau Iliiv Zimaronŋa Tisov na Naatu. Ulam sene pasaa? Yau nambaaŋ payo? Yau nataŋ rarai ghom. Ughur yavyavuuŋ payau sov!” Ŋeer tana, saawe naol tau avuvu saghati tawe ipazaagha, tamtamon titoova to tikauu pa ravraav toman sen. Leso ileep le aate izi. Eemon gabua eta irau ikisi ne mako. I ikuup motmotin ravraav ve sen tana tizi, ve avuvu saghati ipazaagha gha ighau ila pa nugh ŋginaaŋa muul.   
\p
\v 30 Yesu ighasoni ighe: “Ezam sei?”  
\p I iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Yau ezag ‘Legion’ \f + \fr 8:30 \ft Zaaba ŋgun ee tau irau tamtamon 6,000, ene yes Roma tiwaat zi tighe ‘Legion’.\f*  
\m (o ‘Ndiŋndiŋ Ndiŋndiŋ’).” I isaav tauvene pasaa, avuvu sasaghati tau tizeeva na, yes eval kat.  
\v 31 Ra titaŋ rarai Yesu muul tighe iziir zi tila tileep puura saghati tau le puughu mako na sov. \x * \xo 8:31 \xt Syg 9:2, 20:1-3\x*   
\p
\v 32 Nugh tawe, ŋgai umbaal tiina ee tilepleep izi loloz ziige ve tighanghan. Tauvene avuvu sasaghati tau tizeev ŋeer tana na titaŋ rarai Yesu tighe iyok pazi, leso tizeev zi tiloŋ tila ŋgai tawe lolozi.  
\v 33 Yesu iyok pazi, tauvene tipul ŋeer tana, ve tiŋarui ŋgai tawe tila, le tizeev zi tiloŋ tila lolozi. Ra ŋgai tawe tilaan taghon sariipa tizila, ve tiyaat tizila yaa loolo, gha tighun yaa le tisov timataar.   
\p
\v 34 Yes tau tiŋginŋgin ŋgai na, tighita gabua tana, ve tighau tila tipaesia vaaru izi nugh toozi ve nugh siriv tau tigharau zi na paam.  
\v 35 Tauvene tamtamon tisov tila tighe tighita gabua tau ivot na. Tila tivot to Yesu, ve tighita ŋeer tau avuvu sasaghati tipuli na, ŋgar tooni poia ivot wa. I inonogh ghi pa nonoghiiŋa ee, ve mboole izi igharau Yesu aaghe. Tauvene roiŋ tiina igham zi.   
\p
\v 36 Ra yes tau tighita gabua tau ivot na tipaes pa eval tiina pa eez tau Yesu igharaat ŋeer tana, ve iziir avuvu sasaghati tighau pani.  
\v 37 Eval tiina to nugh Gerasa ve nugh siriv tau tigheen tigharau na, tilooŋ paesiiŋ toozi tana, le roiŋ tiina kat igham zi. Tauvene tighason Yesu tighe ipul zi, ve ila pa nugh ite paam. Tauvene Yesu tomania mbiwa tooni tipul zi, ve tizaa waaŋ toozi tighe timuul tila.   
\p
\v 38 Ve ŋeer tau avuvu sasaghati tipuli na, ilam ighason Yesu ariaaŋ ighe iyok pani, ve yesŋa tila. Eemon Yesu iziire ighe:  
\v 39 “Mako. Umuul ula pa nugh tsio, ve usavia uraat tiina tau Maaron igham payo na.” Tauvene ŋeer tana imuul ila, ve ivotia uraat tiina tau Yesu igham pani na vaaru le irau nugh.   
\s1 Yesu igharaat livaa ee, ve ipaburigin Yairus natliva pa mateegh  
\r (Mt 9:18-26; Mk 5:21-43)  
\p
\v 40 Yesu tomania mbiwa tooni tigham waaŋ, ve timuul tila pa yaa naliu ziige tau papazoge tileep pani na. Eval tiina tileep ta sewe ve tisasaŋani. Tauvene tighita ilam peria, ve tighamu toman lolozi poia.  
\v 41 Malau mako ve daaba ee tau iŋgin rumei toozi na, ilam ivot toozi paam. Eeza Yairus. I itap izi Yesu aaghe puughu, ve itaŋ raraini ighe yesuru tila ruum tooni.  
\v 42 Pasaa, natliva imorooŋ le ighe imaat. I natliva eemon kat. Ve ndaman tooni irau saŋavul ve ru.  
\p Tauvene Yesu itaghoni gha tila. Tilaagh tila, ve eval tiina titaghon zi ve tivavagiriŋi zi ila le tigiriŋ Yesu paam.  
\v 43 Livaa ee ilaagh tomani zi paam. I, moroghooŋ to zilivaa ikisi irau ndaman saŋavul ve ru wa. I ipul maet tooni isov pa gholiiŋ yes uraata to gharatooŋ moroghooŋa. Eemon eta irau iuule mako.  
\v 44 I itaghon Yesu ila ila le itut Yesu nonoghiiŋa tooni aavo ziige, ve rekia mon siŋ imot pani le tiini poia muul.   
\p
\v 45 Tauvene Yesu ighason zi ighe: “Ai, sei itut ghau?”  
\p Yes tisov tiyol aliiŋa tighe: “Yei mako.”  
\p Ve Petrus isaav pani ighe: “Tiina, ughita. Ene eval tiina tilivut ghom ve tivagiriŋi zi. Tauta eta itut ghom.”   
\p
\v 46 Eemon Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Mako. Toozi eta aat itut ghau. Pasaa, nayamaan naghe tapirig to uleeŋ igham tamtamon eta wa.”   
\p
\v 47 Livaa tawe ighilaal ighe irau iŋgooz tauu muul mako. Tauvene roiŋ ighamu le tiini irur, ve ila itap izi Yesu naagho. Ra ivotia puughu tau i itut Yesu na ila eval tiina tana matazi. Ve ipaes pazi paam pa Yesu tapiri tau iuule le rekia mon moroghooŋ tooni isov.  
\v 48 Yesu ilooŋ saveeŋ tooni, ve isaav pani ighe: “Livug, ghuruuŋ ila tsio, tauta iuul ghom gha tinim poia wa. Ula toman lolom poia.”   
\p
\v 49 Yesu isavsaav soone, ve ŋeer ee ileep Yairus ruum tooni gha ilam, ve ipaes pa Yairus ighe: “Olman, ugherev sorokin mos puughu tana ilam sov. Pa natum livaa imaat wa.”   
\p
\v 50 Yesu ilooŋ saveeŋ tana, ve isaav pa Yairus ighe: “Uroi sov. Ukis ghuruuŋ ila tsio ariaaŋ, o natum livaa iburig muul.”   
\p
\v 51 Tila peria ruum, ve Yesu iŋgalsekin tamtamon ighe eta iloŋ ila ruum loolo tomani zi sov. Ra igham Petrus, Yoan, ve Yakobus, tomania livaa marani taama ve tiina, ve yes mon tiloŋ tila.  
\v 52 Saawe tana, eval tiina tau tileep muuri na titaŋtaŋ pa livaa marani toman oroor tiina. Eemon Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Yam ataŋ sov. Livaa marani imaat mako. I igheen mon.” \x * \xo 8:52 \xt Yo 11:11+\x*   
\p
\v 53 Yes tilooŋ saveeŋ tooni tane, ve tiŋiŋ pani. Pasaa, yes tiwatagh: Livaa marani imaat wa.  
\v 54 Eemon Yesu ila ikis niima, ve isaav pani toman aliiŋa tiina ighe: “Livaa marani, uburig!” \x * \xo 8:54 \xt Yo 11:43+\x*   
\m
\v 55 Rekia mon livaa marani avuvu imuul ilam, ve iburig. Ra Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Agham le aniiŋ ilam gha ighan.”  
\v 56 Livaa marani taama ve tiina tighita kaut ŋgereeta tana le ŋgar toozi imbool. Ve Yesu iŋgalsekin zi ariaaŋ ighe tisavia gabua tau ivot na vaaru pa tamtamon eta sov. \x * \xo 8:56 \xt Lu 5:14\x*   
\c 9  
\s1 Yesu imbaaŋ mbiwa tooni saŋavul ve ru pa uraat  
\r (Mt 10:1-15; Mk 6:7-13)  
\p
\v 1 Murei ra, Yesu ipoi mbiwa tooni saŋavul ve ru tilam tilup zi, ve irei tapiri irau zi, leso tigharaat moroghooŋ maata maata. Ve ighur avuvu sasaghati tisov tileep ila sambazi, leso tiziir zi tighau pa tamtamon.  
\v 2 Ve imbaaŋ zi tila ighe tivotia pooz to Maaron pa tamtamon, ve tigharaat yes moroghooŋa le tinizi poia. \x * \xo 9:2 \xt Mt 28:19+; Mk 16:15+\x*   
\m
\v 3 Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Saawe tau ala, na alaagh tomania gabua naol sov. Tauvene akis gabua eta imin titi, pepeel, aniiŋ, ma maet sov. Ve nonoghiiŋa tsiam paam, agham ru sov. Ee mon ta igheen ila tinimim, ene irao.  
\v 4 Isaav ighe ala avot nugh eta, ruum sindei tau ighe tighur gham pani, na aleep ila ruum tana mon le irau apul nugh tawe ve ala.  
\v 5 Ve isaav ighe nugh eta lolozi pa ghamuuŋ gham mako ve tizor gham, na aghatuun aghemim ve ŋgaupup toozi izi, o apul nugh toozi ve ala. Leso imin ilaal pazi pa sosor toozi.” \x * \xo 9:5 \xt Lu 10:4+\x*   
\p
\v 6 Yesu isavsaav pazi le isov, ra tipuli, ve tila tilaagh irau nugh nugh, ve tivovotia vaaru poia pa tamtamon. Ve nugh sindei tau tila pani na, tigharaat moroghooŋa toozi paam.   
\s1 Erod igham ŋgar naol pa Yesu  
\r (Mt 14:1-2; Mk 6:14-16)  
\p
\v 7 Erod, i daaba tau iŋgin taan sirivu to Galilaia. Ilooŋ Yesu vaaru pa uraat tau i ighamghamu na, le igham ŋgar naol. Pasaa, tamtamon siriv tisavsaav tighe Yesu, i ŋeer rughuzaaŋa Yoan tau imaat na, ve Maaron ipaburigini pa mateegh.  
\v 8 Ve tamtamon siriv tighe i propet Ilia tau ivot muul. Ve siriv tighe Yesu, i propet muŋganazi ee tau imaat alok wa, ve aazne iburig muul gha ilam.  
\v 9 Tauta Erod isaav pa tauu ighe: “Yoan, yau narav motin luua wa. Ewe sei kat tau naloŋlooŋ vaaru tighe i ighamgham gabua ŋgeretazi ivotvot?” Tauvene iliil eez ighe le ighita Yesu. \x * \xo 9:9 \xt Lu 23:8\x*   
\s1 Yesu ipan tamtamon ndiŋndiŋ ndiŋndiŋ liim (5,000)  
\r (2King 4:42-44; Mt 14:13-21; Mk 6:30-44; Yo 6:1-13)  
\p
\v 10 Yesu mbaŋooŋa tooni tila tigham uraat le isov, ra timuul tilam tivot tooni, ve tipaes pani pa uraat tau tighamu na. Yesu igham zi gha yesŋa tipul eval tiina, ve tila pa taan sirivu tau igheen igharau nugh Betsaida. Leso zigazi tileep.  
\v 11 Eemon eval tiina tilooŋ varuzi, ve titaghon zi tila. Yesu ighit zi, ve igham zi toman loolo poia, ve isavsaav pazi pa pooz to Maaron, ve igharaat moroghooŋa toozi le tinizi poia.   
\p
\v 12 Tilepleep le ravrav izi, ra mbiwa tooni saŋavul ve ru tana tila tisaav pani tighe: “Ughita. Ene taleep izi nugh ŋginaaŋa. Usaav pa eval tiina tane gha tila pa nugh siriv tau tigheen tataŋgan ne. Leso tiil lezi aniiŋ ve nugh to ghenooŋ.”   
\p
\v 13 Eemon Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Mako. Yam taumim agham aniiŋ pazi.”  
\p Yes tiyol aliiŋa tighe: “Wai, iit leen aniiŋ naol mako. Ughita. Ene mberet liim, ve iigh ru mon. Pale irau eval tiina tane wa? Ma mindai? Ughe nila nighol aniiŋ siriv paam pazi?”  
\v 14 Tisaav tauvene pasaa, eval tiina tawe, zitamoot mon irau ndiŋndiŋ ndiŋndiŋ liim (5,000) ma vene.  
\p Yesu isaav pazi muul ighe: “Avalagh tamtamon ila ŋgun ŋgun, ve asaav pazi mbolezi izi. Aghur tamtamon irau tamoot ru saŋavul (50) ila ŋgun eŋaeŋa.”   
\p
\v 15 Tauvene titaghon Yesu aliiŋa, ve tila tighur eval tiina tana ila ŋgun ŋgun, ve mbolezi izi.  
\v 16 Ra Yesu igham mberet liim tomania iigh ru tawe, ikis zi, ve maata izala pa sambam ve ipait Maaron pa aniiŋ tana. Isuŋ le isov, ra iteev mberet tomania iigh ru tana, ve ighur zi ila mbiwa tooni nimazi, ve anazi tila tireii pa eval tiina tawe.  
\v 17 Tisov tighan le apozi isuŋ. Ve avozi muuri tau izi na, tigoog zi, ve tinonogh zi tila nakaral saŋavul ve ru le tivoniir.   
\s1 Petrus ivotia Yesu ighe i Mesia  
\r (Mt 16:13-20; Mk 8:27-30)  
\p
\v 18 Saawe ee, Yesu tomania mbiwa tooni zigazi tileep, ve i isuŋsuŋ. Isuŋ le isov, ve ighason zi ighe: “Laak, tamtamon tigham ŋgar payau tighe yau sei?”   
\p
\v 19 Yes tiyol ghasoniiŋ tooni tighe: “Zeran siriv tighe yo ŋeer rughuzaaŋa Yoan, siriv tighe yo propet Ilia, ve siriv tighe propet muŋganazi tau timaat alok wa, yo toozi ee tau iburig pa mateegh gha ilam.”   
\p
\v 20 Yesu ighason zi muul ighe: “Ve yam taumim, aghe yau sei?”  
\p Petrus iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Yo Mesia. Maaron ighur ghom to ugham mulin tamtamon tooni itaghon saveeŋ mbuaaŋ tooni.” \x * \xo 9:20 \xt Yo 6:68, 11:27\x*   
\p
\v 21 Petrus isavsaav le isov, ra Yesu iŋgalsekin zi ariaaŋ ighe tivotia saveeŋ tana pa tamtamon eta sov.   
\s1 Yesu isavia mateegh ve burigiiŋ tooni  
\r (Mt 16:21-23; Mk 8:31-33)  
\p
\v 22 Saawe tana, Yesu isaav ghazooŋa pa mbiwa tooni ighe: “Tamtamon Naatu, i aat ibaad pataŋani naol, ve yavyavuuŋ tiina ighamu itaghon Taama Maaron ŋgar tooni. Ve yes pooza tomania daaba to watooŋrau ve yes ŋgara to tutuuŋ pale tizori, ve tiravu imaat. Eemon mboŋ imin tol, Maaron pale ipaburigini pa mateegh.”   
\s1 Eez to tataghon Yesu  
\r (Mt 16:24-28; Mk 8:34–9:1)  
\p
\v 23 Yesu isaav pa tamtamon tisov tau yesŋa tilepleep na ighe: “Isaav ighe tamtamon eta ighe imin leg ve itaghon eez tsiau, i aat itatan tauu, ibaad ai pambarooŋ tooni irau saawe, ve ilam itaghon ghau. \x * \xo 9:23 \xt Mt 10:38+; Lu 14:27\x*   
\m
\v 24 Pa ighe tamtamon eta iil eez pa tauu leso ileep poia izi taan, ene pale ilale. Ve isaav ighe tamtamon eta loolo eemon ve ipul tauu payau, i aat igham lepoogh poia ila to Maaron. \x * \xo 9:24 \xt Lu 17:33; Yo 12:24+\x*   
\m
\v 25 Isaav ighe tamtamon eta igham gabua popoiazi naol isov to taan, eemon i tauu ilale, ene pale gabua naol tana tiuule mindai? Mako.   
\p
\v 26 “Isaav ighe tamtamon eta maaya payau ve saveeŋ tsiau, ve ipaisamun ghau, saawe tau Tamtamon Naatu imuul ilam, ve itotoi yesuru Taama Maaron, ve aŋela tooni patabuyaaŋa tapirizi ve mbonarizi ivot ighazooŋ, ene pale i maaya pa tamtamon tana paam, ve ipaisamuna. \x * \xo 9:26 \xt Mt 10:33; Lu 12:9; 2Tim 2:12\x*   
\p
\v 27 “Ve alooŋ. Yau nasaav payam kat. Tamtamon siriv tau itiŋa tayozyooz ne, aat timaat soone, ve tighita Maaron itotoi pooz tooni ivot ighazooŋ.” \f + \fr 9:27 \ft Paesiiŋ to saveeŋ ziiri tane igheen ila Mk 9:1.\f*   
\s1 Yesu itotoi mbonari ivot ighazooŋ  
\r (Mt 17:1-8; Mk 9:2-8)  
\p
\v 28 Yesu isavia saveeŋ tane le isov, ve mboŋ liim ve tol ilam ila, ra igham Petrus, Yoan, ve Yakobus, ve yes paaŋ mon tizala loloz ee. Leso isuŋ ta sewe.  
\v 29 I isuŋsuŋ, ve naagho itoora, ve nonoghiiŋa tooni paam ipisosooŋ le isul toman mbonari tiina.  
\v 30-31 Malau mako ve zeran ru, Mose gha Ilia, tivot tooni toman mbonarizi tiina, ve yesŋa Yesu tisavsaav pa uraat tau i pale ighamu izi Yerusalem, ve eez to i igham mulin tamtamon, ve ipul taan gha imuul izala pa sambam. \f + \fr 9:30-31 \ft Lukas ibood saveeŋ ila yes Grika aliŋazi ighe Mose gha Ilia tisavsaav pa ‘Eksodos’ to Yesu. Puughu tauvene: Buk to Baibol tau imin ru pani, ‘Kisim Bek’, tiwaat eeza ila Grik aliŋazi tighe ‘Eksodos.’ Saveeŋ tane, puughu tauvene: ‘eez to tavot tala.’ Buk tawe isavia eez tau Maaron igham mulin yes Israela timbuzŋa pa pataŋani toozi, ve igham zi tipul Isip, ve timin i tauu le. Yesu uraat tooni, ene ŋgara raraate. Pasaa, mateegh ve burigiiŋ tooni, ene eez paaghu tau Maaron igham mulin ghiit pa pataŋani to sosor toit. Leso saghati tapiri ikis ghiit muul sov, ve tamin Maaron le.\f*  
\v 32 Eemon Petrus tomania zeetŋa ru tigheen le lolozi iveegh kat. Saawe tau tiburig gha matazi ighazooŋ, ra tighita Yesu mbonari, ve zeran ru tau tiyozyooz tomania. \x * \xo 9:32 \xt Igham 34:29; Yo 1:14; 2Pe 1:16+\x*   
\m
\v 33 Tilepleep le zeran ru tawe tighe tipul Yesu, ve Petrus isaav ila pa Yesu ighe: “Tiina, taleep ta sene, poia kat. Mindai, pale nirau balbaal tol? Ee payo, ee pa Mose, ve ee pa Ilia.” Aliiŋa tane, i igham ŋgar poi ve isaav mako. Isiki sorok.   
\p
\v 34 Petrus isavsaav, ve taitai izi le ikau zi. Tauvene roiŋ tiina igham zi. \x * \xo 9:34 \xt Igham 40:34+\x*   
\m
\v 35 Ra tilooŋ Maaron aliiŋa ivot ila taitai tawe loolo ighe: “Ena yau natug. Yau taug nasiigho ve naghuru pa uraat tsiau wa. Alooŋ aliiŋa, ve ataghoni!” \x * \xo 9:35 \xt Mbo 2:7; Is 42:1; Lu 3:22\x*   
\m
\v 36 Saveeŋ tane isov, ve matazi ila le tighita Yesu zigani. Gabua tau tighita na, tisavia pa tamtamon eta rekia mako. Igheen toozi mon le murei ra, tivotia.   
\s1 Yesu iziir avuvu saghati pa ŋeer marani ee  
\r (Mt 17:14-20; Mk 9:14-29)  
\p
\v 37 Yesu tomania mbiwa tooni tol tana tileep mboŋ nughizau, ra tipul loloz, ve timuul tizila le tizaa to eval tiina kat tau tiŋarui zi tilam.  
\v 38-39 Ŋeer ee tau ileep ila eval tiina tawe sosozi na, iboob ila pa Yesu ighe: “Mos puughu, yau nataŋ rarai ghom: Ulam ughita natug tane ve uule lak! I natug eemon, ve avuvu saghati izeeva. Ighe izaa pani, ene rekia mon iyak tiina, itap izila taan, tuua ipardaŋdaŋ, ve ambeera izi. Gabua tane ivavaghamunia le isaghat kat. Ve ipulpuli mako.  
\v 40 Yau nataŋ rarai mbiwa tsio naghe tiziir avuvu saghati tane ighau pani. Eemon titoova, le tirao mako.”   
\p
\v 41 Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Oyai, yam tamtamon to aazne, aghur ila mako, ve ŋgar tsiam ikaukau kat. Itiŋa takaria lepoogh wa. Tauvene naghe pa ŋgar tsiam ivot ve aghilaal rig. Eemon mako. Monmon yam agham pataŋani payau. Pale ŋeez o namariau? Poia. Ugham natum ilam.”   
\p
\v 42 Ŋeer marani iŋarui Yesu ilam, ve avuvu saghati tawe izaa pani, ve isiki izila taan, ve igham tuua ipardaŋdaŋ. Tauvene Yesu iyaon avuvu saghati ighau ve igharaat ŋeer marani gha tiini poia, ra ighuru imuul ila to taama.  
\v 43 Yes tau tighita kaut ŋgereeta tana, tisov tirur pa Maaron tapiri, le ŋgar toozi imbool.  
\s1 Yesu iyol aliiŋa muul pa mateegh tooni  
\r (Mt 17:22-23; Mk 9:30-32)  
\p Tamtamon tighita uraat ŋgeretazi naol tau Yesu ighamgham zi na, ve tisov avozi ikaak. Tauvene Yesu isaav pa mbiwa tooni ighe:  
\v 44 “Yam aghur taliŋamim poi pa saveeŋ tane. Tamtamon Naatu, pale tighuru ila koiŋa nimazi.” \x * \xo 9:44 \xt Lu 9:22\x*   
\m
\v 45 Mbiwa tooni tilooŋ saveeŋ tane, eemon tighazooŋ pani mako. Tikankaan pani. Pasaa, puughu iyooŋ pazi. Eemon tighason Yesu pa saveeŋ tooni puughu mako. Pasaa tiroi. \x * \xo 9:45 \xt Lu 18:34\x*   
\s1 Sei ta eeza tiina kat?  
\r (Mt 18:1-5; Mk 9:33-37)  
\p
\v 46 Saawe ee, mbiwa tooni tivazorai zi pa toozi sei ta eeza tiina iliiv zi tisov. \x * \xo 9:46 \xt Mk 10:35+; Lu 22:24+\x*   
\m
\v 47 Yesu iwatagh ŋgar tau igheen ila lolozi wa. Tauvene igham ŋeer marani ee ilam, ipayooze ila ziige,  
\v 48 ve isaav pazi ighe: “Isaav ighe tamtamon eta maata iŋgal ghau, ve igham marani tane ve iuule pa yau ezag, ene i igham ghau paam. Ve isaav ighe tamtamon eta igham ghau, ene i igham Tamaŋ tau imbaaŋ ghau nalam ne paam. Pasaa, yes tau tileep ila yam sosomim, ve tamtamon matazi veleghin zi tighe lezi ezazi mako, ene Maaron ighit zi ighe ezazi tintiina.” \x * \xo 9:48 \xt Mt 10:40+; Yo 13:20\x*   
\s1 Tamtamon tau ighe ighur koi pait mako, ene imin etaan  
\r (Mk 9:38-40)  
\p
\v 49 Yoan ilooŋ saveeŋ tana, ve isaav pa Yesu ighe: “Tiina, yei nighita ŋeer ee izirziir avuvu sasaghati ila yo ezam. Eemon i itaghon ghiit pa lupuuŋ toit tane mako. Tauvene yei niŋgalsekini nighe igham tauvene sov.”   
\p
\v 50 Eemon Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Ai, yam agham vene sov. Pa tamtamon tau ighe ighur koi payam mako, ene imin etamim ve irau iuul gham.” \x * \xo 9:50 \xt Mt 12:30; Lu 11:23; 1Kor 3:1-9\x*   
\s1 Nugh ee to Samaria lolozi pa ghamuuŋ Yesu mako  
\p
\v 51 Yesu saawe tooni tau Maaron ighe ighamu imuul izala pa nugh sambam, ene ilam igharau wa. Tauvene ŋgar tooni iyaryaaŋ ighe izala pa Yerusalem.  
\v 52 I imbaaŋ tamtamon siriv timuuŋ tila pa nugh ee to Samaria, leso tigharaat eez pani.  
\v 53 Eemon tamtamon to nugh tawe tilooŋ Yesu ŋgar tooni iyaryaaŋ ighe izala pa Yerusalem, tauvene lolozi pa ghamuuŋni mako. \x * \xo 9:53 \xt Yo 4:9\x*   
\m
\v 54 Mbiwa tooni ru, Yakobus gha Yoan, tighita gabua tana le irau lolozi mako. Tauvene tighason Yesu tighe: “Tiina, ughe nigham mindai? Pale nighason Maaron, leso igham yav sambam ve izilam, gha ighan tamtamon tawe?” \x * \xo 9:54 \xt 2King 1:10+; Mk 3:17\x*   
\p
\v 55 Eemon Yesu itoor ghi ve iyaon zi.  
\v 56 Ra tipaburigin laghooŋ toozi muul, ve tila pa nugh ite.   
\s1 Eez to tataghon Yesu  
\r (Mt 8:19-22)  
\p
\v 57 Yes tilaghlaagh taghon eez tila, ve ŋeer ee isaav pa Yesu ighe: “Nugh sindei tau yo ughe ula pani, yau aat nataghon ghom ve ituru tala.”   
\p
\v 58 Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Ŋgavuun sagsagŋa lezi niazi ila taan puura. Ve man tau tirovroov ila taitai saamba, lezi rumazi izala ai. Eemon Tamtamon Naatu, i le niia to ghenooŋ mako.” \x * \xo 9:58 \xt 2Kor 8:9; Pil 2:6+\x*   
\p
\v 59 Ra Yesu isaav pa ŋeer ite ighe: “Ulam utaghon ghau.”  
\p Eemon ŋeer tawe iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Tiina, mindai? Irau upul ghau namuul nala naleep tomania tamaŋ? Ve nasaŋani le imaat gha natavia, o nalat nataghon ghom?”   
\p
\v 60 Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Mako. Yes tau lezi ghilalooŋ pa Maaron mako ve titaghon eez to mateegh na, yes irau titavia mateegha. Eemon yo aat ula uvotia pooz to Maaron pa tamtamon.”   
\p
\v 61 Ra ŋeer ite, aana ilam ve isaav pa Yesu ighe: “Tiina, yau naghe nataghon ghom. Ve mindai? Irau upul ghau namuul nala pa nugh tsiau ve yeŋa zetagŋa nileep rig? Ve nakis nimazi le isov, o nalat nataghon ghom.”   
\p
\v 62 Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Mako. Tamtamon eta ighe igham pooz pa waaŋ ve maata imulmuul, ene irau igham uratoi pooz to Maaron mako.” \x * \xo 9:62 \xt Lu 17:32; Pil 3:13+\x*   
\c 10  
\s1 Yesu imbaaŋ tamtamon tamoot tol saŋavul ve ru (72) pa uraat  
\p
\v 1 Murei ra, Tiina toit Yesu ighur tamtamon tamoot tol saŋavul ve ru (72) paam pa uraat, ve imbaaŋ zi ighe tilaagh ruŋruŋa, ve timuuŋ tila pa nugh naol isov tau i ighe ila pazi na, ve tigharaat eez pani.  
\v 2 Ve isaav pazi ighe: “Alooŋ. Aniiŋ katini timatuugh wa. Eemon uraata to lupuuŋ aniiŋ, yes eval mako. Tauvene aghason Uum Taama tau iŋginŋgin uraat to lupuuŋ aniiŋ na. Leso imbaaŋ uraata siriv muul tila pa uraat to lupuuŋ aniiŋ tooni. \x * \xo 10:2 \xt Mt 9:37+; Yo 4:35\x*   
\m
\v 3 Ala. Yau nambaaŋ gham ala amin sipsip natŋa tau tileep ila ŋgavuun sagsagŋa sosozi. Tauvene matamim imomoos poi pa taumim. \x * \xo 10:3 \xt Mt 10:16; Mbaŋ 20:29; 1Kor 15:32\x*   
\m
\v 4 Saawe tau ala, na alaagh tomania gabua naol imin lugluug, pepeel, ma zuzuuŋa to aghemim sov. Ve isaav ighe azaa to ŋeer eta izi eez livuugha, na asavsaav tomania sov. Matamim pa laghooŋ mon, ve malmalimim ala. \x * \xo 10:4 \xt 2King 4:29; Lu 9:3+\x*   
\p
\v 5 “Ruum sindei tau aloŋ ala, na asavia saveeŋ palotiiŋ pa ruum tana tamtamona imin maata aghe: ‘Maaron aat igham gham aleep poia toman lolomim luuma.’  
\v 6 Isaav ighe ruum tana taama, i ŋeer to ŋgar luuma, ene pale luuma to Maaron tau asavia na igheen tooni. Ve ighe mako, ene pale palotiiŋ tsiam imuul pa taumim.  
\v 7 Ruum sindei tau papazoge tighur gham aleep pani na, aleep ta sena mon. Asakia ala ruum ite paam sov. Ve saa aniiŋ ma yaa tau tigham payam, na arere sov. Aghan ve aghun mon. Pa yes uraata irau tigham lezi atuya. \x * \xo 10:7 \xt Mt 10:10; 1Kor 9:11+; 1Tim 5:18\x*   
\m
\v 8 Tauvene isaav ighe yam aloŋ ala pa nugh eta, ve tigham gham toman lolozi poia, ve tigham lemim aniiŋ, na arere sov. Aghan mon. \x * \xo 10:8 \xt 1Kor 10:27\x*   
\m
\v 9 Agharaat moroghooŋa to nugh tana le tinizi poia, ve asaav pazi tauvene: ‘Pooz to Maaron, ene ilam igharau gham wa!’  
\v 10-11 Eemon isaav ighe yam ala avot nugh eta, ve lolozi pa ghamuuŋ gham mako, na ala ayooz maaran aate, ve aghatuun aghemim, ve asaav pazi aghe: ‘Aghita. Aazne, yei nighatuun aghemai, leso ŋgaupup to nugh tsiam izi. Ene imin ilaal payam pa sosor tsiam. Yam irau awatagh kat tauvene: Pooz to Maaron ilam igharau gham wa.’” \x * \xo 10:10-11 \xt Lu 9:5; Mbaŋ 13:51, 18:6\x*   
\p
\v 12 Yau nasaav payam kat: Saawe to Mboŋ Murei, pataŋani tiina kat pale iŋarui nugh tana tamtamona le iliiv pataŋani tau pale ivot pa yes tamtamon to Sodom. \x * \xo 10:12 \xt Gnp 19:24+; Mt 10:15\x*   
\s1 Yesu iyaon nugh siriv tau titoor ŋgar toozi mako  
\r (Mt 11:20-24)  
\p
\v 13 “Oyai, yam tamtamon to Korazin ve Betsaida, akaria taumim wa! Pasaa, yau nagham gabua ŋgeretazi tintiina naol tivot izi nugh tsiam. Eemon atoor ŋgar tsiam ila pa Maaron soone. Imin ta nugh Tiro ve Sidon tau tikankaan pa Maaron na, tighita gabua tauvene, kanaŋ lolozi ipataŋan pa sosor toozi, ve tinonogh zi pa nonoghiiŋa to moŋiiŋ, ve mbolezi izi ila ŋgaupup loolo, ve titoor ŋgar toozi alok wa.  
\v 14 Tauvene yau nasaav payam: Saawe to Mboŋ Murei, ve Maaron ighe igabiiz tamtamon ve ighur atuya pazi, i pale ighur atuya raurauai pa tamtamon to nugh ru tana. Eemon yam, pale agham atuya tiina kat pa sosor tsiam.  
\v 15 Ve yam tamtamon to nugh Kapernaum paam, yam agham ŋgar aghe Maaron pale ipakur gham, ve igham gham azala pa nugh sambam? Mako kat! Yam pale azila nugh saghati to yes mateegha.” \x * \xo 10:15 \xt Is 14:13+\x*   
\p
\v 16 Yesu isaav muul pa mbiwa tooni ighe: “Isaav ighe tamtamon eta ilooŋ aliŋamim, ene i ilooŋ ghau paam. Ve ighe tamtamon eta izor gham, ene i izor ghau paam. Ve isaav ighe tamtamon eta izor ghau, ene i izor Ŋeer tau imbaaŋ ghau nalam ne paam.” \x * \xo 10:16 \xt Mt 10:40; Yo 13:20; 1Tes 4:8; 1Yo 4:6\x*   
\s1 Uraata tamoot tol saŋavul ve ru (72) timuul tila to Yesu ve tipaesia uraat toozi  
\p
\v 17 Yes tamoot tol saŋavul ve ru (72) tau Yesu imbaaŋ zi pa uraat na, tila tilaagh pa uraat toozi le isov, ra timuul tila, ve tisaav pani toman tintinizi tighe: “Tiina, uraat tsiei ilaan poi, ve avuvu sasaghati paam tileep ila sambamai. Saawe tau niziir zi ila yo ezam, yes tilooŋ ghei ve tighau.”   
\p
\v 18 Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Yau naghita Sadan itap sambam ve izilam pa taan imin nugh ighani milia. \f + \fr 10:18 \ft Zeran ŋgara siriv tighe Yesu saveeŋ tooni tane, puughu tauvene: Uraat tau uraata tooni tighamu na, ene itotoi ighe Maaron itatan Sadan tapiri wa.\f* \x * \xo 10:18 \xt Yo 12:31; Syg 12:7+\x*   
\m
\v 19 Alooŋ. Yau nagham lemim tapirimim to avaghaaz moot sasaghati tomania mboolmamalau (o skorpion), ve atatan koiaan Sadan tapiri le isov. Ve gabua eta irau ivaghamun gham ne mako. \x * \xo 10:19 \xt Mbo 91:13; Mk 16:18; Mbaŋ 28:5\x*   
\m
\v 20 Eemon yam tintinmim pa avuvu sasaghati tau tileep ila sambamim ve tilooŋ aliŋamim na sov. Tintinmim pasaa, tibood ezamim ila rau to nugh sambam wa.” \x * \xo 10:20 \xt Igham 32:32; Pil 4:3; Hib 12:23; Syg 20:12, 21:27\x*   
\p
\v 21 Saawe duduuŋ tana, Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ igham Yesu loolo poia le poia kat. Tauvene isaav ighe: “O Tamaŋ, yo Tiina tau uŋgin sambam ve taan. Yau napait ghom toman lolog poia. Pasaa, yes tau lezi ŋgar tintiina ve tighazooŋ pa gabua naol na, yo uŋgooz uraat tsiau tane puughu pazi. Ve upaghazoŋaini pa yes tau titatan tauzi ezazi, ve tinumeer ghom imin yes geegeu tinumeer tamazŋa ve tinazŋa. Aa Tamaŋ, yo utaghon taum lolom ve poia tsio, tauta ugham tauvene. \x * \xo 10:21 \xt 1Kor 1:20, 26, 3:18+\x*   
\p
\v 22 “Tamaŋ Maaron ighur gabua naol isov tilam nimag wa. Ve i mon ta iwatagh katin tauu Naatu. Tamtamon ite paam mako. Ve Tamaŋ Maaron tauvene paam. Tamtamon eta iwataghi kat mako. Tauu Naatu, ve yes tau Naatu ipaghazoŋai zi pani na, yes mon ta tiwataghi.” \x * \xo 10:22 \xt Mt 28:18; Yo 1:18, 3:35, 10:15, 17:26\x*   
\p
\v 23 Ra Yesu itoor ghi, naagho ila pa mbiwa tooni, ve isaav pazi ighe: “Yam tau aghita uraat tsiau ne, tintinmim pa poia to Maaron tau izaa tsiam! \x * \xo 10:23 \xt Mt 13:16+\x*   
\m
\v 24 Pa yau nasaav payam: Muuŋ, propet ve kinik naol tighe le tighita gabua tau yam aghita. Eemon yes tighita mako. Ve tighe le tilooŋ saveeŋ tau yam aloŋlooŋa ne. Eemon tilooŋa mako.” \x * \xo 10:24 \xt 1Pe 1:10+\x*   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to ŋeer to Samaria tau itotoi ŋgar poia  
\r (Lu 18:18-30)  
\p
\v 25 Saawe tana ŋeer ee tau le ŋgar tiina pa tutuuŋ na, iburig ve ighe itoov Yesu. Tauvene ighasoni ighe: “Mos puughu, pale nagham mindai, gha leso naleep matag yaryaare le alok?”   
\p
\v 26 Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Saveeŋ tau igheen ila tutuuŋ na, yo uwaato ve ugham ŋgar pani mindai?”   
\p
\v 27 Ŋeer tana iyol aliiŋa ighe:  
\q2 “Lolom pa Tiina tsio Maaron. Ughur lolom tomania ŋgar tsio ve tapirim isov ila pani.  
\q2 Ve lolom pa zetamŋa ve ugham poghani zi, imin lolom pa taum.” \x * \xo 10:27 \xt Wkp 19:18; Lo 6:5\x*   
\p
\v 28 Yesu ilooŋ saveeŋ tooni, ve isaav pani ighe: “Saveeŋ tsio, ene iduduuŋ. Ugham tauvene, o ugham lepoogh poia ila to Maaron, ve uleep matam yaryaare le alok.” \x * \xo 10:28 \xt Wkp 18:5; Mt 19:17\x*   
\p
\v 29 Eemon ŋeer tana ighe ipaghazoŋai tauu ighe i ŋeer duduuŋa. Tauvene ighason Yesu muul ighe: “Zetagŋa savunugha ta yo ughe yau naghur lolog pazi na?”   
\p
\v 30 Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Pai ee, ŋeer ee ileep Yerusalem, ve ighe izila pa nugh Yeriko. I ilaghlaagh taghon eez ila, ve malau mako umbuuŋa siriv tivot tooni, gha tiravu tiravu le naagho isaghat kat. Rigmon kanaŋ imaat. Ve tiyauur nonoghiiŋa tomania gabua tooni isov. Ra tipuli izi, ve tighau tila.   
\p
\v 31 “Malau mako ve ŋeer ee to watooŋrau itaghon eez tawe ilam, le ighita ŋeer tana ighengheen izi eeze. Eemon iuule mako. Isalivu, ve malmali taghon eez ziige gha ila.  
\v 32 I ilam ila, ve uraata ee to Rumei Tiina aana ilam, ve ighita ŋeer tana ighengheen. Eemon i paam, iuule mako, ve isalivu, ve malmali taghon eez ziige gha ila. \f + \fr 10:32 \ft Ŋeer to watooŋrau ve uraata to Rumei Tiina tiroi pa tigharau ŋeer tana pasaa, tutuuŋ to Mose isaav tauvene: Isaav ighe tamtamon eta igharau mateegh eta, ene aat ighamu isaghat ila Maaron maata. Tamtamon tauvene aat igham watooŋrau ve igharaat mulin tauu le iŋgalaaŋ ila Maaron maata, o iloŋ ila Rumei Tiina muul. Ughita Namba 19:11-16.\f*   
\p
\v 33 “Ra Samaria tamazi ee, aana ilam peria nugh tau ŋeer tana ighengheen pani na. I ighita, le loolo isaghatini kat, ve ighe iuule.  
\v 34 Tauvene ilaagh ŋaruini ila, ve iliŋ ŋgoreeŋ tomania vaen izala zaab aav niia, ve ikauu. Ra iiti izala doŋki tooni paavo, ve ighamu ila pa ruum to yes loomba, ve iŋgini ta sewe.  
\v 35 Mboŋ nughizau, ra iwaan maet denari ru ila lugluug tooni, ighur zi ila to ŋeer tau iŋgin ruum tawe, ve isaav pani ighe: ‘Nagham maet tane payo, leso uŋgin poghania ŋeer tane. Ve isaav ighe irao mako, yo uule pa maet tsio le irau namuul nalam. Mako nayol mulin maet tsio.’”   
\p
\v 36 Yesu isavia saveeŋ tane le isov, ra ighason ŋeer ŋgara to tutuuŋ tana ighe: “Laak, yo ugham ŋgar mindai pa zeran tol tana? Sei ta imin ŋeer tau yes umbuuŋa tiravu na, iitete?”   
\p
\v 37 Ŋeer tana iyol aliiŋa ighe: “I tau loolo isaghatini ve iuule na.”  
\p Tauvene Yesu isaav pani: “Tauta ena. Ula ve utaghon ŋgar raraate mon.”   
\s1 Yesu ila ighita Marta ve Maria  
\p
\v 38 Yesu tomania mbiwa tooni tilaagh taghon eez tila le tivot nugh ee. Livaa ee to nugh tawe, eeza Marta. I igham Yesu gha tila ruum tooni. \x * \xo 10:38 \xt Yo 11:1, 12:2+\x*   
\m
\v 39 Marta tazliva, eeza Maria. Maria mboole izi igharau Yesu aaghe puughu, ve iloŋlooŋ saveeŋ tooni.  
\v 40 Eemon Marta maata imin naol pa uraat to ŋginiiŋ yes loomba toozi. Tauvene ila to Yesu, ve isaav pani ighe: “Tiina, yo ugham ŋgar payau, ma mako? Ughita. Tazigliva ipul ghau, ve zigau naghamgham uraat. Usaav pani ilam iuul ghau lak!”   
\p
\v 41 Eemon Tiina toit Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Aa Marta, yo matam imin naol pa uraat, tauta lolom ipataŋan ve ugham ŋgar naol.  
\v 42 Yo aat ugham ŋgar pa gabua ee mon. Pa ene irao. Tazimliva Maria igabiiz poi. Tauta izuari ghi pa gabua tau poia le poia kat. Ve gabua tane, eta irau iwalaava pani ne mako.”   
\c 11  
\s1 Eez to suŋuuŋ  
\r (Mt 6:9-13)  
\p
\v 1 Saawe ee, Yesu isuŋsuŋ izi nugh ee. Isuŋ le isov, ra mbiwa tooni ee isaav pani ighe: “Tiina, yei nighe upaduduuŋ ghei pa eez to suŋuuŋ imin Yoan ipaduduuŋ ziŋeera.”   
\p
\v 2 Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Saawe tau yam aghe asuŋ, na asaav tauvene:  
\q2 ‘Tamamai, ugham tamtamon tisov tipatab pa yo ezam.  
\q2 Pooz tsio ilam irau nugh le isov. \x * \xo 11:2 \xt Syg 11:15\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 3 Ugham aniiŋ to aazne payei. \f + \fr 11:3 \ft Saveeŋ tane isaav pa aniiŋ mon mako. Aniiŋ ilup gabua naol tau iuul ghiit pa lepoogh toit. Tauvene saa gabua tau aazne tambool pani, ene tasuŋ Maaron pani, leso iuul ghiit pa gabua tana.\f* \x * \xo 11:3 \xt Mbo 23:1; Pil 4:19; 1Tim 6:8\x*   
\b  
\q1
\v 4 Upul sosor tsiei. Pasaa, tamtamon tisov tau tigham sosor payei na, yei nipul sosor toozi paam.  
\q2 Upul tovaaŋ ivot payei sov.’” \f + \fr 11:4 \ft Eez ite to tatoor saveeŋ ziiri tane, ene vene: “Upul ghei nitap pa tovaaŋ sov.”\f* \x * \xo 11:4 \xt Mt 18:21+; Yo 17:15; Ep 4:32; 2Tes 3:3\x*   
\s1 Maaron pale ilooŋ suŋuuŋ toit  
\r (Mt 7:7-11)  
\p
\v 5-6 Yesu isaav pazi muul tauvene: “Isaav ighe tsiam eta loom tooni ilam pa mboŋ anooŋa, ve le aniiŋ eta to igham pani mako, ene pale igham mindai? I aat ila to iitete eta, ve ighasoni ighe: ‘Ou, etag ite, ugham leg mberet tol ilam. Leso naghamu ila pa loom tsiau. Pasaa, i ileep nugh malau ilam, ve yau leg aniiŋ eta to nagham pani mako. Pale nayoli murei.’   
\p
\v 7 “Ve ighe iitete tau ileep ruum loolo na, imbuzir pani ighe: ‘Ah, uparara ghau pasaa! Yau napoon ataman ila ivool, ve toman natugŋa nigheen wa. Irau naburig ve nauul ghom mako.’”   
\p
\v 8 Ve Yesu iseeŋ saveeŋ tooni muul ighe: “Mindai? Ighe iitete iyol aliiŋa tauvene, pale ŋeer tana ipuli? Mako. I aat inoknok ghasoniiŋni. Ve yau nasaav payam. Iitete tana pale ilooŋ aliiŋa, ve iburig gha igham gabua naol isov tau ŋeer tana imbool pani na. Onoon, i maata iŋgal ighe ŋeer tana i eeta ve iuule ne mako. Pale iuule pasaa, ŋeer tana maaya mako ve inoknok ghasoniiŋni.” \x * \xo 11:8 \xt Lu 18:1+\x*   
\p
\v 9 Ra Yesu iseeŋ saveeŋ tooni muul ighe: “Tauvene yau nasaav payam: Aghason, o aghamu. Ailo, o andeeŋa. Aseŋ ataman, o ataman ikaak payam. \x * \xo 11:9 \xt Mk 11:24; Yo 15:7; 1Yo 5:14+\x*   
\p
\v 10 “Pasaa, tamtamon tisov tau tighason, ene aat tighamu. Ve isaav ighe tiilo, ene aat tindeeŋa. Ve ighe tiseŋseŋ ataman, ene aat ataman ikaak pazi.  
\v 11 Mindai? Isaav ighe tamtamon tsiam eta naatu ighason taama pa iigh, pale taama igham moot pani?  
\v 12 Ma isaav ighe i ighason taama pa man atoli, pale taama igham araraaŋ pani? Ene aat mako.  
\v 13 Aghita. Yam zeran to ghamuuŋ ŋgar sasaghati naol. Eemon aghamgham gabua popoiazi mon pa natmimŋa. Ve Tamamim tau ileep sambam, poia tooni, ene iliiv gham kat. Tauvene tamtamon tisov tau tighasoni pa Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ na, i aat ilooŋ zi, ve igham pazi.” \x * \xo 11:13 \xt Yo 4:10, 7:38+; Mbaŋ 2:38\x*   
\s1 Yesu koiŋa tighe i igham uraat toman Sadan tapiri  
\r (Mt 12:22-30; Mk 3:22-27)  
\p
\v 14 Ŋeer ee, avuvu saghati izeeva ve ighamu aavo ivool. Yesu iziir avuvu saghati tawe ighau pani, ragha ŋeer tana aavo pakia ve isavsaav. Yes tau tileep ve tighita kaut ŋgereeta tana, tirur pani ve ŋgar toozi imbool.  
\v 15 Eemon tamtamon toozi siriv tisaav tighe: “Ewe Belsebul tau daaba to avuvu sasaghati na ipaloti. Tauta i le tapiri to iziir avuvu sasaghati tighau.”  
\v 16 Ve tamtamon siriv tighe titoov Yesu. Tauvene tizoornugh tighe i igham gabua ŋgereeta eta imin ilaal pazi. Leso tiwatagh tighe Maaron to sambam ileep tomania pa uraat tooni. \x * \xo 11:16 \xt Mt 16:1; Mk 8:11\x*   
\p
\v 17 Eemon Yesu iwatagh ŋgar toozi wa. Tauvene isaav pazi ighe: “Isaav ighe kinik eta tomania tamtamon tooni tivaghuru koi pa tauzi ve tivalagh zi tileep lez lez, ene pale nugh toozi isaghat kat, ve tamtamon tileep pani muul mako. Ve ruum paam. Isaav ighe tamtamona tivaghuru koi pa tauzi ve tivavalaghi zi, ene pale tireu mbirisai ruum toozi, ve lupuuŋ toozi isaghat.   
\p
\v 18 “Sadan tauvene paam. Isaav ighe tamtamon tooni tivaghuru koi pa tauzi ve tivavalaghi zi, ene pale pooz tooni iyaryaaŋ mindai? Mako. Laak, yam aghe yau nazirziir avuvu sasaghati pa Belsebul tapiri.  
\v 19 Ighe tauvene, mindai pa ziŋeramim tau tizirziir avuvu sasaghati na? Sei ipalot zi pa ŋgar toozi tawe? Ŋgar tau yes tighamu, ene itotoi ighe ŋgar tsiam iduduuŋ mako.  
\v 20 Eemon isaav ighe yau nazirziir avuvu sasaghati pa Maaron tapiri, ene itotoi ighe pooz to Maaron ilam peria tsiam wa. \x * \xo 11:20 \xt Igham 8:19\x*   
\p
\v 21 “Isaav ighe ŋeer ariaaŋa eta igharaat ghi pa malmal, ve iyooz ariaaŋ pa ŋginiiŋ ruum tooni, ene pale gabua tooni naol isov tighenaar poi.  
\v 22 Eemon isaav ighe tamtamon eta tau tapiri iliiv ŋeer ariaaŋa tana ila peria tooni, ve igham malmal le iliivo, ene pale iyauur gabua naol isov to malmal tau ŋeer ariaaŋa tana inumeer zi na, tomania gabua tooni siriv, ve irei zi pa zeetŋa. \x * \xo 11:22 \xt Kol 2:15; 1Yo 3:8, 4:4; Syg 20:2\x*   
\p
\v 23 “Isaav ighe tamtamon eta ipaak ghau mako, ene i imin koiag. Ve ighe ŋeer eta iuul ghau pa lupuuŋ tamtamon mako, ene pale ireu zi timbiriis.” \x * \xo 11:23 \xt Mk 9:40; Lu 9:50\x*   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to avuvu saghati tau ighau ila ve imuul ilam  
\r (Mt 12:43-45)  
\p
\v 24-25 Yesu isaav pazi muul ighe: “Isaav ighe avuvu saghati ipul ŋeer eta ve ighau ila, ene pale ivalaghlaagh izi nugh ŋginaaŋa tau le yaa mako na, ve iil le niia to ileep pani ve imariau. Isaav ighe iil le mako, ene pale isaav pa tauu ighe: ‘Yau aat namuul nala nagig niag muŋgaana tau napuli ve nalam ne!’ Tauvene i aat imuul ila. Ighe ila ivot ve ighita tizaar ruum loolo, ve tigharaata le paghuuna kat,  
\v 26 ene pale ila iyau zeetŋa liim ve ru paam tau tiliivo pa ghamuuŋ ŋgar sasaghati na, ve yesŋa timuul tilam tizeev tamtamon tana, ve tileep le tileep kat. Irau tipuli muul mako. Tauvene i pale isaghat kat. Muuŋ, lepoogh tooni poia rig. Ve aazne, isaghat le isaghat kat!” \x * \xo 11:26 \xt Yo 5:14; Hib 6:4+; 2Pe 2:20+\x*   
\s1 Poia to Maaron izaa to sei?  
\p
\v 27 Yesu isavia saveeŋ tane, ve livaa ee tau ileep ila eval tiina sosozi na, iboob ila pani ighe: “Livaa tau ipoop ghom ve igham payamyam payo na, i aat tintini pa poia to Maaron tau izaa tooni.” \x * \xo 11:27 \xt Lu 1:28, 42, 48\x*   
\p
\v 28 Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Saveeŋ tsio poia. Eemon yes tau tilooŋ Maaron aliiŋa ve titaghoni, ene aat tintinizi kat pa poia to Maaron tau izaa toozi.” \x * \xo 11:28 \xt Mt 7:21; Lu 8:15; Yo 14:21; Yems 1:25\x*   
\s1 Yesu imin ilaal pa tamtamon itaghon ŋgar tau muuŋ Yona ighamu na  
\r (Mt 12:38-42)  
\p
\v 29 Saawe tana, tamtamon katini tila to Yesu. Tauvene i isaav pazi ighe: “Zeran to aazne, sasaghatizi kat. Pasaa, tizuari zi tighe le tighita gabua ŋgereeta eta imin ilaal pazi, o tighur ila. Ve gabua eemon geeg ta pale Maaron itotoia imin ilaal pazi. Ite paam mako. Ene gabua imin muuŋ ivot pa saawe to propet Yona.  
\v 30 Yona tomania saveeŋ tooni imin ilaal pa tamtamon to Ninive. Tamtamon Naatu tauvene paam. Pale imin ilaal pa zeran to aazne. \x * \xo 11:30 \xt Yona 1:17, 2:10, 3:4\x*   
\p
\v 31 “Muuŋ, garwaat tinazi tau igham pooz pa taan sirivu tau igheen ila pa daudau puughu na ilaagh malau kat ilam to ilooŋ ŋgar popoia to kinik Solomon. Ve aazne, gabua tau iliiv kat pa Solomon na, ivotvot ila sosomim. [Eemon yam aghilaalo mako.] Tauvene saawe to Mboŋ Murei, ve Maaron ighe igabiiz tamtamon ve ighur atuya pazi, livaa tawe pale iburig tomania yam zeran to aazne, mako ivotia sosor tsiam ivot ighazooŋ. \x * \xo 11:31 \xt 1King 10:1+; 2Sto 9:1+\x*   
\p
\v 32 “Yes Ninivea \f + \fr 11:32 \ft Ninive, ene nugh tiina to yes Asiria. Yes Ninivea, Yuda mako, ve tiwatagh Maaron mako. Eval tiina irau nugh nugh tiroiroi pazi pasaa, zaaba toozi lolozi isaghatin tamtamon mako, ve tighurghur pataŋani naol pazi.\f*  
\m tauvene paam. Muuŋ, tilooŋ saveeŋ tau Yona ivotia na, ve rekia mon tighilaal ve titoor ŋgar toozi ila pa Maaron. Ve aazne, gabua tau iliiv kat pa ŋgar tau Yona ighamu na, ivotvot ila sosomim. [Eemon yam aghilaalo mako.] Tauvene saawe to Mboŋ Murei, ve Maaron ighe igabiiz tamtamon ve ighur atuya pazi, yes Ninivea pale tiburig tomania yam zeran to aazne, mako Maaron isees matamim.” \x * \xo 11:32 \xt Yona 3:5+\x*   
\s1 Ghazooŋa ve ndoroom  
\r (Mt 5:14-16, 6:22-23)  
\p
\v 33 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Isaav ighe tamtamon eta itun lam, pale iŋgooza ma ipagudu pa uur? Mako. Pale isaroni izaa ituuk. Leso mbonari igham nugh ighazooŋ pa yes tau tiloŋ tila ruum na. \x * \xo 11:33 \xt Mk 4:21; Lu 8:16; Pil 2:15+\x*   
\m
\v 34 Mataan, ene imin lam tau igheen ila anoŋaan. Pasaa, taghita ghazooŋa pani. Tauvene isaav ighe matam poia ve ughilaal ghazooŋa to Maaron, ene itotoi ighe ŋgar to ghazooŋa ivon ila lolom wa. Eemon isaav ighe matam ikumkuum, ve ughilaal ghazooŋa to Maaron mako, ene itotoi ighe ŋgar to ndoroom ivon ila lolom.  
\v 35 Tauvene uyamaan ghom. Mako pale unumeer sorok ughe ghazooŋa to Maaron igheen ila lolom wa. Eemon mako. Lolom ivonvon pa ŋgar to ndoroom soone.  
\v 36 Ighe ndoroom rigta ipaak anoŋam sirivu eta mako, ve anoŋam isov itaghon ŋgar to ghazooŋa mon, ene pale gabuam isov itotoi ghazooŋa to Maaron raraate imin lam mbonari igham nugh ighazooŋ.”   
\s1 Yesu iyaon zeran tutuuŋa ve yes ŋgara to tutuuŋ  
\r (Mt 23:1-36; Mk 12:38-40)  
\p
\v 37 Yesu isavsaav, ve ŋeer ee to tutuuŋ ighasoni ighe yesuru tila ruum tooni ve tighan. Tauvene tiloŋ tila ruum tooni, ve mbolezi izi pa ghanghaniiŋ.  
\v 38 Ŋeer tawe ighita Yesu itaghon tutuuŋ toozi to miniiŋ nimazi mako, ve igham aniiŋ gha ighan mon. Tauvene irur ve igham ŋgar naol. \x * \xo 11:38 \xt Mt 15:1+; Mk 7:1+\x*   
\p
\v 39 Tiina toit Yesu isaav pani ighe: “Yam zeran tutuuŋa amin tamtamon tau imin rubruub le muuri iŋgalaaŋ kat. Eemon loolo, ene tiŋtiŋai. Pasaa, ŋgar tau yam aghamgham zi ila tamtamon matazi, ene agharaat zi le popoia kat. Eemon lolomim, ene ivon pa ŋgar to umbuuŋ ve ŋgar sasaghati maata maata. \x * \xo 11:39 \xt Mk 7:4; Tit 1:15\x*   
\m
\v 40 Yam lemim ŋgar mako! Mindai, Maaron ighur gabua tau tigheen ghazooŋa mon, ve ighur gabua lolozi mako?  
\v 41 Eemon isaav ighe lolomim isaghatin yes mbolaaŋa ve arei gabua tsiam siriv pazi, ene pale ŋgar tsiam isov iŋgalaaŋ, ve gabua eta irau igham gham asaghat ila Maaron maata mako. \x * \xo 11:41 \xt Is 58:6+; Lu 12:33; Yems 1:27\x*   
\p
\v 42 “Yam zeran tutuuŋa, akaria taumim wa! Onoon, saiŋ soroksorok tau aghagharaat sur pani na, yam matamim iŋgalŋgal pa valaghiiŋ zi timin ŋgun saŋavul, ve aghamgham ŋgun eŋaeŋa pa Maaron. Ene poia. Ŋgar tana, apuli sov. Eemon tutuuŋ tau tintiina kat ila Maaron maata na, lolomim iveghveegh pazi. Tutuuŋ tauvene: ‘Ugabiiz poghania pataŋani to tamtamon, ve ugharaata le iduduuŋ,’ ve ‘Lolom pa Maaron.’ Tutuuŋ tauvene, yam ataghon zi paam, o poia. \x * \xo 11:42 \xt Lo 6:5; Mika 6:8\x*   
\p
\v 43 “Yam zeran tutuuŋa, akaria taumim wa! Pa saawe tau aloŋ ala rumei, yam aghe le aleep ila paŋ popoiazi mon tau tighur zi pa yes tau ezazi tintiina na. Ve isaav ighe alaagh ila maaran aate, na aghe tamtamon tighit gham, ve tisavia saveeŋ popoia payam imin pakuruuŋ gham. \x * \xo 11:43 \xt Lu 14:7, 20:46\x*   
\m
\v 44 Onoon kat, yam akaria taumim wa! Yam amin naal \f + \fr 11:44 \ft Yes Yuda tighita tighe mateegha niazi, ene nugh saghati tau igham zi tisaghat ila Maaron maata. Tauvene lolozi pa tigharau nugh tauvene mako.\f*  
\m tau tamtamon tiwatagh zi mako, tauvene tighe pa nugh poia mon ve tilaghlaagh izala pavozi.”   
\p
\v 45 Ra ŋeer ŋgara ee to tutuuŋ, iburig ve iyol Yesu aliiŋa ighe: “Mos puughu, saveeŋ tau yo usiki na, ene imin yo uvelegh ghei paam!”   
\p
\v 46 Yesu isaav pani ighe: “Yam ŋgara to tutuuŋ paam, akaria taumim wa! Pasaa, yam aseeŋ Maaron tutuuŋ tooni pa tutuuŋ naol itaghon taumim ŋgar tsiam. Tauta agham pataŋani tintiina pa tamtamon imin ai posaaŋ tau pataŋani kat pa badooŋ. Eemon yam aghur nimamim ŋguruuŋa eta to iuul zi pa badooŋ ne mako. \x * \xo 11:46 \xt Mbaŋ 15:10; Ga 5:1\x*   
\p
\v 47-48 “Yam akaria taumim wa! Agham ŋgar pa yes propet tau muuŋ timbumimŋa tighur koi pazi ve tiravuur zi timatmaat. Zeran tawe ta aazne yam agharaat naal toozi pavozi le paghunazi kat. Ŋgar tsiam tana itotoi ighe yam paam ayok pa ŋgar sasaghati tau timbumimŋa tighamgham zi na aghe ene ŋgar poia. \x * \xo 11:47-48 \xt Mbaŋ 7:51+\x*   
\m
\v 49 Puughu tane, ta Maaron ivotia ŋgar tooni ighe: ‘Yau aat nambaaŋ yes propet tomania mbaŋooŋa tsiau tila pa zeran tawe. Eemon yes pale tighur koi pazi, ve tirav siriv timatmaat, ve tighur pataŋani naol pa siriv, ve tinaan zi taghon nugh nugh gha tila.’  
\v 50-51 Tauvene atuya tau pale izaa to tamtamon to aazne, ene aat tiina kat. Pasaa, propet tisov tau tamtamon tirav zi timatmaat na, siŋ toozi atuya pale izaa toozi. Yau nasaav payam kat. Saawe tau Maaron ighur sambam ve taan, ilam mateegh to Avel, ve taghon taghon ilam le mateegh to propet Sakaria tau ileep iloŋ ila Rumei Tiina loolo igharau artaal ve tiravu imaat na, tamtamon to aazne siŋ toozi aat imaliŋ imin yatuuŋ siŋ to yes tisov tawe. \x * \xo 11:50-51 \xt Gnp 4:8; 2Sto 24:20+\x*   
\p
\v 52 “Yam ŋgara to tutuuŋ, akaria taumim wa! Pasaa, ki tau ikaak ataman pa tamtamon leso tiwatagh katin Maaron, ta yam aŋguaaza pazi. Yam taumim aloŋ ala mako. Ve yes tau tizuari zi tighe tiwatagh katin Maaron ve tiloŋ tila nugh tooni na, yam aponpoon eez pazi.”   
\p
\v 53-54 Yesu isavia saveeŋ tane le isov, ra iburig ve ivot ila muuri. Zeran tutuuŋa tomania yes ŋgara to tutuuŋ tana atezi yavyav pani kat. Tauvene saawe tana ve ila, tinoknok ghasoniiŋni pa gabua maata maata, ve tisasaŋan. Tighe i isavia saveeŋ eta isosor, o imin le puughu to tikisi.   
\c 12  
\s1 Tapamir tauun pa ghuruuŋ ila toit sov  
\r (Mt 10:26-27, 16:6; Mk 8:15)  
\p
\v 1 Saawe tana, tamtamon eval le eval kat tilam tighe tilooŋ Yesu saveeŋ tooni. Yes tilam tilup zi le lezi sooso mako, tivavagiriŋi zi. Yesu ipaburigin saveeŋ tooni, ve iveveen mbiwa tooni imin maata ighe: “Ayamaan gham pa yis to zeran tutuuŋa. Ene yau nasavia gabuazi tau tipapamir tauzi pa ghuruuŋ ila toozi. \x * \xo 12:1 \xt 1Kor 5:6+\x*   
\m
\v 2 Alooŋ. Gabua eta irau iyooŋ mako. Gabua isov tau zunuaaŋ, ene pale tipool zi, leso tigheen ghazooŋa. Ve ŋgar tau ŋgozaaŋ na, ene pale ivot mataghare. \x * \xo 12:2 \xt Mk 4:22; Ro 2:16; Hib 4:13\x*   
\m
\v 3 Tauvene saveeŋ tau yam asavia ila ndoroom loolo imin ŋgozaaŋ, ene pale ivot pa mataaz le eval tiina tilooŋa. Ve saveeŋ tau yam akamuun pani ila ruum loolo, ene pale tamtamon tiyooz izala ruum toozi pavozi ve tibobaini. \f + \fr 12:3 \ft Isaav ighe yes Yuda tighe eval tiina tiwatagh saveeŋ eta, ene tiyooz ila ruum toozi pavozi ve tibobaini, imin iit tayooz ila maaran ve tabobai saveeŋ.\f*   
\s1 Taroi pa Maaron mon  
\r (Mt 10:28-31)  
\p
\v 4 “Aa zetagŋa, yau nasaav payam. Yes tau tighe tirav gham amaat na, aroi pazi sov. Pa ighe tirav gham amaat, ene isov tana. Tivaghamunia anoŋamim mon. Murei, irau tigham gabua eta payam muul mako. \x * \xo 12:4 \xt Hib 13:6\x*   
\m
\v 5 Tauvene yau nasaav payam: Aroi pa Maaron mon. Pa i tapiri tiina, ve yam aleep ila i niima. Isaav ighe loolo pa ravuuŋ tamtamon eta imaat, ene i irau isik tamtamon tana anunu izila nugh saghati paam. Tauta nasaav payam: Aroi pa Maaron mon. \x * \xo 12:5 \xt Hib 10:31; Yems 4:12\x*   
\p
\v 6 “Aghita. Man niuruuŋgu, ene man sorok. Irau taghol liim pa maet siŋsiŋai ru mon. Eemon Maaron irau loolo iveegh pa eta mako.  
\v 7 Ve yam ndamomim ve aliiv kat pa niuruuŋgu ta katini ne. Ve i iwatagh katin gham. Dabamim raua paam, i ininiir zi tisov. Tauvene yam aroi sov. I pale maata iŋgal gham.” \x * \xo 12:7 \xt Lu 21:18; Mbaŋ 27:34\x*   
\s1 Tapaisamun Yesu eeza sov  
\r (Mt 10:32-33, 12:32)  
\p
\v 8 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Yau nasaav payam. Isaav ighe tamtamon eta isaav ghazooŋa ila tamtamon matazi ighe i imin leg ve itaghon ghau, ene pale Tamtamon Naatu paam, isaav ghazooŋa ila Maaron aŋela tooni matazi ighe tamtamon tana imin i le wa. \x * \xo 12:8 \xt Syg 3:5\x*   
\m
\v 9 Eemon, isaav ighe ŋeer eta ipaisamun tauu ila tamtamon matazi ighe i tamtamon tsiau mako, ene pale Tamtamon Naatu ipaisamuna paam ila Maaron aŋela tooni matazi. \x * \xo 12:9 \xt Mk 8:38; Lu 9:26; 2Tim 2:12; 1Yo 2:23\x*   
\p
\v 10 “Isaav ighe tamtamon eta isik saveeŋ saghati iŋarui Tamtamon Naatu, ene sosor tooni tana, Maaron irau ireua pani. Eemon isaav ighe isik saveeŋ saghati iŋarui Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ ve ivelegh uraat tooni, ene sosor tauvene, Maaron irau ireua mako. \x * \xo 12:10 \xt Mk 3:28+; Hib 6:4, 10:26\x*   
\p
\v 11 “Isaav ighe tikis gham, ve tipayooz gham iloŋ ila rumei, ma tipayooz gham ila yes pooza ve yes daaba to nugh naghozi, na lolomim bubu ve ail ŋgar ve saveeŋ to asavia pazi na sov. \x * \xo 12:11 \xt Mk 13:11; Lu 21:14+\x*   
\m
\v 12 Pa saawe tau tipayooz gham pa savsaveeŋ, Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ tauu pale ipaghazoŋai gham pa saa saveeŋ tau Maaron ighe yam asavia.” \x * \xo 12:12 \xt Mt 10:19+\x*   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to kuaz tauu ta le ŋgar mako  
\p
\v 13 Ŋeer ee ileep ila eval tiina sosozi, ve isaav pa Yesu ighe: “Mos puughu, usaav pa toghag, leso ivalagh gabua tau tamamai ipul zi payei na, ve igham leg siriv.”   
\p
\v 14 Eemon Yesu isaav pani ighe: “Wai, ŋeer tsiau, sei ighur ghau to nagharaat saveeŋ tsiam ve navalagh gabua tsiam?”  
\v 15 Ra Yesu isaav pa eval tiina ighe: “Matamim izaa ve ayamaan gham pa ŋgar to loloon ighaar pa gabua maata maata to taan. Alooŋ. Isaav ighe tamtamon eta i le gabua katini to taan, gabua tawe mon irau ighamu ileep poia ne mako.” \x * \xo 12:15 \xt Mbo 62:10; Lu 4:4; 1Tim 6:6, 17\x*   
\p
\v 16 Ra i isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ pazi ighe: “Pai ee, kuaz tauu ee, taan tooni ŋgoreeŋa tiina. Tauvene gabua isov tau i ivazogh zi na, titum tizaa le anoŋazi katini.  
\v 17 I ighita anoŋazi tawe, ve igham ŋgar ighe: ‘Wai, pale nagham mindai pa aniiŋ tsiau tane? Naghur zi sindei? Pa balbaal tsiau tirao mako.’  
\v 18 Ra ŋgar ee ivot pani: ‘Aa, ŋgarig gha matag iŋgal ŋgar ee! Yau aat nareu balbaal tsiau muŋganazi tizi, ve narau paghpaaghu ve tintiina. Leso naghur aniiŋ tsiau tomania gabua tsiau naol isov tiloŋ tila.  
\v 19 Isov, mako nasaav pa taug naghe: Aa, ŋgarig gha narao kat! Gabua popoia naol tau nandou zi ne, ene aat iuul ghau irau ndaman katini. Aazne ve ila, yau aat namariau, ve naghan ma naghun, ve naleep toman lolog poia mon.’ \x * \xo 12:19 \xt 1Kor 15:32; Yems 5:5\x*   
\p
\v 20 “Eemon Maaron isaav pani ighe: ‘Aa, yo borau! Lem ŋgar mako kat! Mboŋ aazne, yo aat umaat. Ve sei pale ighamuur gabua tsio tau undou zi na?’” \x * \xo 12:20 \xt Mbo 39:6, 49:16+\x*   
\p
\v 21 Ra Yesu iparwai saveeŋ tooni ighe: “Ŋgar raraate mon pale ivot pa tamtamon tisov tau tindou lezi kuaz to taan, eemon timbool pa ŋgar popoia tau Maaron loolo pani na.” \x * \xo 12:21 \xt Mt 6:19+; 1Tim 6:18+\x*   
\s1 Loloon bubu sov  
\r (Mt 6:25-34)  
\p
\v 22-23 Yesu iseeŋ saveeŋ tooni muul, ve isaav pa mbiwa tooni ighe: “Tauvene yau nasaav payam: Lolomim bubu pa lepoogh tsiam to taan sov. Agham ŋgar naol pa lemim aniiŋ to ghaniiŋ, ma nonoghiiŋa to anonogh gham pani na sov. Onoon, aniiŋ ve nonoghiiŋa iuul ghiit pa lepoogh to taan. Eemon gabua tauvene irau iuul ghiit to tagham lepoogh poia ila to Maaron ne mako. Ve lepoogh tawe, ta gabua tauu. \x * \xo 12:22-23 \xt Pil 4:6; Hib 13:5; 1Pe 5:7\x*   
\m
\v 24 Agham ŋgar pa man kool. Yes tivazogh aniiŋ mako, ve tiyau aniiŋ anooŋa mako. Ve lezi balbaal to ndouŋ aniiŋ toozi iloŋ ila ne mako. Maaron tauu ipanpan zi. Ve yam, Maaron ighit gham ighe yam, o gabua tauu. Aliiv kat pa man ta naol ne.  
\v 25 Mindai? Isaav ighe tsiam eta igham ŋgar naol pa lepoogh tooni to taan, ve iil eez to iseeŋ saawe tooni le malau rig, pale irao? Ene aat mako.  
\v 26 Isaav ighe yam irau agham gabua ŋgiira tana mako, puughu mindai ta lolomim bubu, ve agham ŋgar naol pa gabua siriv to taan imin aniiŋ ma nonoghiiŋa?   
\p
\v 27 “Aghita manman tau tiyozyooz we. Titum mindai? Tauzi tigham uraat, ma tigharaat lezi nonoghiiŋa eta to tinonogh zi pani? Mako. Eemon yau nasaav payam. Muuŋ, kinik Solomon, i eeza tiina kat, ve inonogh ghi pa nonoghiiŋa tau popoiazi kat. Eemon nonoghiiŋa tooni eta ŋgereeta poia irau manman tawe ruŋguzi mako. \x * \xo 12:27 \xt 1King 10:4+; 2Sto 9:3+\x*   
\m
\v 28 Ve aghita kikiliiŋ tau ruŋguzi popoiazi we. Ene kaut sorok. Aazne, ighengheen. Ve bogzo pale tiravu ve tizaare ila yav ighani. Eemon Maaron tauu ipabood kikiliiŋ tawe le paghuuna kat. Laak, isaav ighe i maata iŋgalŋgal gabua sorok tauvene, i pale maata iŋgal gham paam, ve igham lemim nonoghiiŋa. Oyai, ghuruuŋ ila tsiam ŋgiira rigmon kat! \x * \xo 12:28 \xt Mt 10:29\x*   
\m
\v 29 Tauvene lolomim bubu ve arav taumim pa ghamuuŋ aniiŋ to ghaniiŋ ve yaa to ghunuuŋ na sov.  
\v 30 Pa gabua tauvene, ta nughmariŋ to taan tau tiwatagh Maaron mako na tiravrav tauzi pa ghamuuŋ zi. Tamamim Maaron iwatagh: Isaav ighe yam ambool pa gabua tauvene, irau aleep poia ne mako. [Tauvene i pale iuul gham.]  
\v 31 Yam aat azuari gham pa taghoniiŋ pooz tooni imin maata. O i tauu maata iŋgal gham pa gabua naol tana paam.” \x * \xo 12:31 \xt Mbo 37:4, 25; Ro 14:17\x*   
\s1 Gabua to sambam, ene kuaz tauu  
\r (Mt 6:19-21)  
\p
\v 32 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “O yam sipsip to Maaron, onoon yam eval mako. Eemon aroi sov. Pa Tamamim Maaron loolo poia payam, ve ighe igham gham aleep ila pooz tooni loolo leso aghita anooŋa tooni. \x * \xo 12:32 \xt Mt 25:34; Lu 22:29+\x*   
\m
\v 33 Tauvene agholia gabua tsiam, ve arei maeta pa yes mbolaaŋa. Ene eez to agharaat lemim lugluug tau irau isaghat mako, ve andou lemim kuaz izi nugh sambam. Kuaz to nugh tawe irau isov mako. Igheen irau saawe. Umbuuŋa irau tiumbu mako, ve up paam irau ivaghamunia mako. \x * \xo 12:33 \xt Lu 18:22; Mbaŋ 2:45; 1Tim 6:18+\x*   
\m
\v 34 [Tauvene azuari gham pa nugh tawe.] Pa nugh tau yam aghita aghe kuaz tsiam igheen pani, ene aat lolomim iyaryaaŋ pani.”   
\s1 Besooŋa to Maaron aat tisaŋan muleeŋ to Tiina toozi  
\r (Mt 24:45-51; Mk 13:32-37)  
\p
\v 35 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Yam agharaat gham pataghaaŋ, ve matamim iŋgal lam tsiam ighan irau saawe, ve asasaŋan. \x * \xo 12:35 \xt Mt 25:1+; 1Tes 5:5+; 1Pe 1:13\x*   
\m
\v 36 Ataghon ŋgar to yes besooŋa tau tiina toozi ileep ila marewaaŋ to vaiŋ, ve ighe imuul ilam. Yes tighurghur matazi ve tisasaŋani. Leso saawe tau ighe i imuul ilam peria ve iseŋ ataman, ene aat rekia mon ve tikaak ataman pani.  
\v 37 Yau nasaav payam kat. Yes besooŋa tau tiina toozi imuul ilam, ve ighit zi tighurghur matazi ve tisasaŋani, ene pale tintinizi pa poia tau pale izaa toozi. Pasaa, tiina toozi pale igharaat ghi pa ŋgaliiŋ aniiŋ, mako isaav pazi mbolezi izi, ve i tauu ilam ve iŋgal lezi aniiŋ, ve ibees pazi.   
\p
\v 38 “Isaav ighe tiina toozi ilam pa mboŋ anooŋa, ma nugh itun, ve ighit zi tighurghur matazi ve tisasaŋani, ene pale tintinizi pa poia tau pale izaa toozi.   
\p
\v 39 “Agham ŋgar poi. Isaav ighe ruum taama eta iwatagh saawe duduuŋ tau umbuuŋa eta ighe ilam, ene irau igheen mako. Pale imamaat ve iŋgin ruum tooni poi. Mako pale umbuuŋa tana ireu ruum tooni, ve iloŋ ila ium gabua tooni. \x * \xo 12:39 \xt 1Tes 5:2+\x*   
\m
\v 40 Yam tauvene paam. Agharaat gham pataghaaŋ ve asasaŋan. Pa Tamtamon Naatu pale ilam pa saawe eta tau yam awataghi mako, ve ipaperekin gham.” \x * \xo 12:40 \xt Mk 13:33; Syg 16:15\x*   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to besooŋa poia ve besooŋa saghati  
\r (Mt 24:45-51)  
\p
\v 41 Yesu isavia saveeŋ tane le isov, ra Petrus ighasoni ighe: “Tiina, mindai? Saveeŋ palelaaŋ tsio tana iŋarui ghei, ma ila pa tamtamon tisov?”   
\p
\v 42 Tiina toit Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Isaav ighe besooŋa eta ŋgar tooni poia, ve tiini ibees pa uraat tau tighuru ila niima, ene pale tiina tooni ighuru imin daaba. Leso iŋgin ruum tooni tomania besooŋa tooni siriv, ve igham lezi aniiŋ ila saawe tau tiina tooni ighuru.  
\v 43 Besooŋa tau ighe tiina tooni ila pa nugh ite, ve imuul ilam le ighita besooŋa tana igham katin uraat tooni, ene aat tintini pa poia tau pale izaa tooni.  
\v 44 Onoon kat, yau nasaav payam. Tiina tooni pale ighuru imin daaba, ve iŋginiir gabua tooni naol isov. \x * \xo 12:44 \xt Lu 19:17+\x*   
\p
\v 45 “Eemon isaav ighe besooŋa eta loolo ighur ighe: ‘Ah, tiina tsiau irau rekia imuul ilam soone.’ Tauvene iburig gha irav sorokin zeetŋa siriv, zitamoot ve zilivaa. Ve ighanghan ve ighunghun le ivaghamgham. Besooŋa tana aat iyamaan ghi.  
\v 46 Pasaa, tiina tooni pale imuul ilam ipaperekin besooŋa tana pa saawe eta tau i iwataghi mako. Mako ilos matini le uuli imotmot, ve isiki izila nugh saghati. Leso ileep ta sewe tomania yes tau matazi iŋgal uraat toozi mako, ve tizorzoor i aliiŋa.   
\p
\v 47 “Tauvene besooŋa tau iwatagh ŋgar tau tiina tooni loolo pani na, eemon igharaat ghi pa uraat mako, ve itaghon ŋgar to tiina tooni mako, ene pale tilos matini. \x * \xo 12:47 \xt Yems 4:17\x*   
\m
\v 48 Eemon besooŋa tau ighe ikankaan pa ŋgar to tiina tooni, ve isosor pa gabua siriv, ene pale tiina tooni loolo kuruŋia pani ve ilosi kat mako. Pasaa, tamtamon tisov tau Maaron igham lezi gabua katini, ene pale ighur maata pazi to tigham uratoi gabua tawe, leso anoŋazi katini tivot. Ve isaav ighe Maaron inumeer ŋeer eta, ve ighur gabua tiina ila niima to iŋgini, ene pale Maaron ighur maata pani to igham anooŋa tiina ivot.”   
\s1 Yesu pale imin puughu pa tamtamon tivalaghi zi  
\r (Mt 10:34-36)  
\p
\v 49 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Yau nalam to nasik yav \f + \fr 12:49 \ft Yav tau Yesu isavia na, zeran ŋgara siriv tighe ene izaa to uraat to Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ. Ve siriv tighe izaa to Yesu saveeŋ tooni, ma atuya tau pale iŋarui tamtamon pa sosor toozi.\f*  
\m izi taan. Ve naghe yav tana iyaryaar, o poia!  
\v 50 Eemon pataŋani tiina aat igham ghau imin maata. Le isov, o gabua tana ivot. Tauvene yau aat naleep toman lolog ipataŋan ve napasov uraat tana le isov. \x * \xo 12:50 \xt Mk 10:38+; Yo 12:27\x*   
\m
\v 51 Mindai? Yam aghe pa yau nalam to napasovuur malmal isov to taan, ve nalup tamtamon timin eemon? Mako. Yau nasaav payam. Yau pale namin puughu pa tamtamon tivarewai zi, ve tileep soghan soghan pa tauzi.  
\v 52 Saawe tane ve ila, toŋvetaz irau tivalupu zi timin eemon muul mako. Ighe yes liim, ve tilup zi ila ruum eemon, ene pale tivavalaghi zi, ve tol tileep ila ziige ee, ve ru ila ziige ite.  
\v 53 Ve tamazŋa ve tinazŋa toman natuzŋa pale tivavalaghi zi ve tileep soghan soghan pa tauzi paam. Ve zilivaa tomania rauaz livaŋa tauvene paam, pale tileep soghan soghan pa tauzi.” \x * \xo 12:53 \xt Mika 7:6\x*   
\s1 Tamtamon tighilaal gabua tau ivotvot ne mako  
\r (Mt 16:2-3)  
\p
\v 54 Yesu isaav pa eval tiina tauvene: “Isaav ighe yam aghita taitai iyooz ila ragh puughu, ene aat rekia mon asaav aghe: ‘O, uman ighe ilam tane.’ Le onoon, uman ilam.  
\v 55 Ve isaav ighe yaghur ilaagh yavaar ilam, ene asavsaav aghe: ‘O, ene aat nugh ituntun.’ Le onoon, gabua ivot imin tau yam asavia.  
\v 56 Yam zeran to karom. Apapamir taumim pa ghuruuŋ ila tsiam! Puughu mindai ta yam irau agabiiz nugh, eemon gabua tau ivotvot pa saawe tane, yam aghilaal puughu mako.”   
\s1 Rekia ve tagharaat saveeŋ toit tomania Maaron  
\r (Mt 5:25-26)  
\p
\v 57 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Ŋgar duduuŋa, yam awataghi wa. Puughu mindai ta agabiiz poi mako?  
\v 58 Isaav ighe tamtamon eta ighe ipayooz ghom pa savsaveeŋ, na usaŋan sov. Saawe tau yamru alaghlaagh ala pa nugh to gharatooŋ saveeŋ, na rekia mon utoova to ugharaat saveeŋ tsio tomania ŋeer tana le loolo poia. Mako pale igherev ghom ula to daaba to gharatooŋ saveeŋ, ve daaba tawe ighur ghom ula uraata tooni niima, ve aana ighur ghom uloŋ ula ruum to yavyavuuŋ.  
\v 59 Onoon kat, yau nasaav payo. Yo irau uvot rekia ne mako. Pale ulepleep ta sewe le irau upasov atuya tau tighuru payo na le isov kat.” \x * \xo 12:59 \xt Mt 18:34\x*   
\c 13  
\s1 Ighe tatoor loloon mako, ene pale talaleen  
\p
\v 1 Saawe tana, tamtamon siriv tau tileep tomani zi na, tipaesia zeran siriv to Galilaia varuzi pa Yesu. Tighe saawe tau zeran tawe tigham watooŋrau pa Maaron, Piladus irav zi timatmaat, ve siŋ toozi imaliŋ tomania siŋ to gabua tau tirav zi timin watooŋrau na.  
\v 2 Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Yam agham ŋgar mindai pa zeran tawe? Aghe tiliiv tamtamon tisov to Galilaia pa ghamuuŋ sosor, tauta pataŋani tawe ivot pazi ne? \x * \xo 13:2 \xt Yo 9:2+\x*   
\m
\v 3 Mako kat! Ve yau nasaav payam: Isaav ighe atoor ŋgar tsiam ila pa Maaron mako, na yam asov pale alalemim raraate imin zeran tawe. \x * \xo 13:3 \xt Mbo 7:12\x*   
\m
\v 4 Ve yes saŋavul liim ve tol (18) tau tileep igharau yaa naliu Siloam, ve ruum tau daaba malaua na ipol izala pavozi, ve irav zi timatmaat na, yam agham ŋgar pazi mindai? Aghe sosor toozi iliiv tamtamon tisov tau tileep Yerusalem we, tauta pataŋani tawe ivot pazi ne?  
\v 5 Mako kat! Ve yau nasaav payam: Isaav ighe atoor ŋgar tsiam ila pa Maaron mako, na yam pale asov alalemim raraate imin zeran tawe.”   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to ai tau le anooŋa mako  
\p
\v 6 Ra Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ pazi ighe: “Pai ee, ŋeer ee ivazogh ai fik ila vaen tooni loolo. Ai tawe itum izaa ve murei ra, ŋeer tana ila ilaghova. Ighe anooŋa, o igham le siriv. Eemon ila le ighita anooŋa eta mako.  
\v 7 Tauvene isaav pa uraata tooni tau iŋgin vaen na ighe: ‘Ulooŋ. Yau nalala nalamlam pa yauŋ ai tane anooŋa irau ndaman tol wa. Eemon naghita anooŋa eta mako. Uŋgori ighau! Ipasov sorokin taan ŋgoreeŋa pasaa?’ \x * \xo 13:7 \xt Mt 3:10, 7:19; Yo 15:2, 6\x*   
\p
\v 8 “Eemon uraata tooni iyol aliiŋa ighe: ‘Wai, tiina tsiau, uvaghamunia ai pasaa? Upuli igheen pa ndaman tane, ve nakep taan tomania ŋgai taae, ve naghuru ila ai puughu.  
\v 9 Ve taghita pa ndaman murei. Ighe iyanooŋ, o poia. Ve ighe mako, o taŋgori ighau.’” \x * \xo 13:9 \xt 2Pe 3:9, 15\x*   
\s1 Yesu igharaat moroghooŋ to livaa ee ila saawe to umbom patabuyaaŋ  
\p
\v 10 Umbom patabuyaaŋ ee, Yesu ipaghazoŋai tamtamon pa Maaron aliiŋa iloŋ ila rumei.  
\v 11 Livaa ee ileep tomani zi paam. I, avuvu saghati iravrav matin tapiri ve ivaghamunia le nduume ikook irau ndaman saŋavul liim ve tol (18) wa. Tauvene irau iyooz duduuŋ mako.  
\v 12 Yesu ighita, ve ipoii ilam, gha isaav pani ighe: “Livaa, moroghooŋ tsio irau ikis ghom muul mako.”  
\v 13 Ra ighur niima izala paavo, ve rekia mon livaa tawe tiini poia gha iyooz duduuŋ, ve ipait Maaron eeza pa tapiri ve poia tooni.   
\p
\v 14 Eemon ŋeer tau iŋgin rumei na, ighita gabua tana le irau loolo mako. Pasaa, Yesu igharaat livaa tana pa saawe to umbom patabuyaaŋ. Tauvene ŋeer tana iyaon yes tau tileep iloŋ ila rumei na ighe: “Ai, wik ta naol ne, iit leen saawe liim ve ee to uraat. Isaav ighe lolomim pa ŋeer tane igharaat moroghooŋ tsiam, na alam pa saawe to uraat. Alam pa saawe to umbom patabuyaaŋ sov!” \x * \xo 13:14 \xt Igham 20:8+\x*   
\p
\v 15 Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Yam zeran to karom. Apapamir taumim pa ghuruuŋ ila tsiam! Umbom patabuyaaŋ ta naol ne, yam asov apaspas makau ve doŋki tsiam, ve agham zi tila tighunghun yaa. \x * \xo 13:15 \xt Lu 14:5; Yo 7:22+\x*   
\m
\v 16 Ve aghita livaa tane. I Abaram paaghu tooni. Eemon Sadan ikisi irau ndaman saŋavul liim ve tol (18) wa. Tauvene isaav ighe yau nauule ve nagham mulini pa pataŋani tooni ila saawe to umbom patabuyaaŋ, ene iduduuŋ. Ma yam agham ŋgar mindai?” \x * \xo 13:16 \xt Is 58:6+; Lu 6:9\x*   
\p
\v 17 Yesu isavia saveeŋ tane, le koiŋa tisov mayazi. Eemon eval tiina tisov tintinizi. Pasaa, tighita gabua tintiina tau Yesu ighamgham zi na, le tighilaal tapiri ve poia tooni.   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to mastet uuve  
\r (Mt 13:31-32; Mk 4:30-32)  
\p
\v 18 Ra Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Pooz to Maaron, ene ŋgara mindai? Pale nasavia izaa to saa?  
\v 19 Ene imin mastet uuve \f + \fr 13:19 \ft Mastet uuve, ene geegeu kat imin dog paatu ma mbuas uuve.\f*  
\m tau ŋeer ee ighamu ila, ve isuruuva ila uum tooni. Murei ra, uuv marani tawe  
\m itum izaa tiina ve ghitooŋa imin ai, ve ighur booga naol. Tauvene man tau tirovroov ila taitai saamba na, tirau rumazi izala booga.” \x * \xo 13:19 \xt Mt 24:14\x*   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to yis  
\r (Mt 13:33)  
\p
\v 20 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Pooz to Maaron, ene ŋgara mindai? Pale nasavia izaa to saa?  
\v 21 Ene imin yis rig tau livaa ee ikepu tomania palawa tiina. Yis rigmon tana iloŋ ila irau palawa tawe loolo le ipasaria.”   
\s1 Ataman to tagham lepoogh poia ila to Maaron, ene tiina mako.  
\r (Mt 7:13-14, 21-23)  
\p
\v 22 Yesu ighe izala pa Yerusalem. Tauvene itaghon eez ila ve ighe peria nugh marani ma nugh tiina eta, mako ivotia Maaron aliiŋa pazi. Ighamgham tauvene taghon taghon gha ila.  
\v 23 Ŋeer ee iburig ve ighasoni ighe: “Tiina, mindai? Tamtamon tau pale Maaron igham mulin zi ve tileep poia na, yes eval, ma eŋaeŋa mon?”   
\p
\v 24 Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Eez to tataghon pooz to Maaron ve taloŋ tala nugh tooni, ene atamana tiina mako. Marani kat. Tauvene azuari gham to aloŋ ala. Pa tamtamon eval pale titoova to tiloŋ tila, eemon tirao mako. \x * \xo 13:24 \xt Pil 3:12+; 1Tim 6:12\x*   
\p
\v 25 “Tauvene agham ŋgar poi. Murei, ruum tauŋa pale iburig, ve ipoon ataman. Ve ighe ayozyooz muuri, ve aseŋseŋ ataman ve ataŋ raraini aghe: ‘Tiina, ukaak ataman payei lak!’ Ene pale iyol aliŋamim ighe: ‘Yam savunugha? Yau nakankaan payam. Alaagh mindai ta alam?’ \x * \xo 13:25 \xt Mt 25:10+\x*   
\p
\v 26 “Mako yam ayol aliiŋa aghe: ‘Wai, tiina tsiei, muuŋ taluplup ghiit pa ghanghaniiŋ ve ghunuuŋ, ve yo upaghazoŋai tamtamon pa Maaron aliiŋa izi nugh tsiei. Lolom iveegh payei?’   
\p
\v 27 “Eemon i pale isaav payam ighe: ‘Yam savunugha? Yau nasaav payam wa. Yau nakankaan payam. Yam zeran to ghamuuŋ ŋgar sasaghati naol. Asov aghau ala soghan payau!’” \x * \xo 13:27 \xt Mt 25:41\x*   
\p
\v 28 “Tauvene yam pale lolomim isaghat kat, ve ayakyak toman livomim kikikia. Pasaa, aghita Abaram, Isak, ve Yakop, tomania propet tisov tilup zi tomania Maaron izi nugh tooni. Eemon yam o tisik gham avot ala muuri. \x * \xo 13:28 \xt Mt 8:11, 13:42, 24:51\x*   
\m
\v 29 Saawe tana ighe ivot, ene pale nughmariŋ tilam tilup zi izi Maaron nugh tooni, ve mbolezi izi pa ghanghaniiŋ. Yes to ragh puughu, yavaar puughu, daudau puughu, ve kaagu puughu. \x * \xo 13:29 \xt Lu 14:15; Syg 19:9\x*   
\p
\v 30 “Ve alooŋ. Zeran siriv tau aazne tileep murei geeg, ene pale tila timuuŋ. Ve zeran siriv tau aazne timuŋmuuŋ, ene pale anazi tizi tileep murei geeg.” \x * \xo 13:30 \xt Mt 19:30, 20:16\x*   
\s1 Yesu loolo ipataŋan pa Yerusalem  
\r (Mt 23:37-39)  
\p
\v 31 Saawe duduuŋ tana, zeran tutuuŋa siriv tilam ve tipaes pa Yesu tighe: “Ulooŋ. Upul nugh tane, ve ughau ula pa nugh ite paam! Pa Erod ŋgar tooni iyaryaaŋ ighe irav ghom umaat.”   
\p
\v 32 Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Ŋeer tawe, i irau saa? I imin ŋgavuun sagsag tau geegeu. Yam ala asavia aliŋag pani tauvene: ‘Ulooŋ. Aazne ve bogzo, yau aat nazirziir avuvu sasaghati ve naghagharaat moroghooŋa. Ve ezau, \f + \fr 13:32 \ft Saveeŋ ‘ezau’, ene izaa to saawe tau Yesu iparwai uraat tooni izi Yerusalem.\f*  
\m o naparwai uraat tsiau le isov kat.’  
\v 33 Tauvene aazne, bogzo, ve ezau, yau aat nataghon eez tau Maaron ighuru payau na. Pasaa, irau tirav propet eta to Maaron izi nugh ite paam mako. Tiravu imaat izi Yerusalem, o iduduuŋ.”   
\p
\v 34 Ra Yesu isaav muul toman loolo ipataŋan ighe: “O Yerusalem, Yerusalem, yo nugh tau uravrav propet to Maaron timatmaat. Ve yes uraata tau i imbaaŋ zi tilat payo na, yo uravrav zi pa maet gha timatmaat. Saawe naol, yau naghe nalup tamtamon tsio tilam tsiau. Leso napagud zi imin tatareek ipagud natŋa pa baage. Eemon yes lolozi pa tilam mako.  
\v 35 Tauvene Maaron pale ipul rumei tsio igheen sorok ve le tamtamona mako. Ve yau nasaav payo: Yo aat ughit ghau muul mako, le irau ŋgar to tamtamon tsio ivot, ve tisaav tighe: \x * \xo 13:35 \xt Mt 23:37+; Lu 21:20, 24\x*  
\q2 ‘Poia to Maaron izaa to ŋeer tane ve ipaloti.  
\q2 Pa i igham Maaron naagho ta ilam!’” \x * \xo 13:35 \xt Mbo 118:26\x*   
\c 14  
\s1 Yesu igharaat ŋeer ee tau sariiŋ tiina ighamu  
\p
\v 1 Umbom patabuyaaŋ ee, Yesu ila ruum to ŋeer ee pa ghanghaniiŋ. Ŋeer tawe, i daaba ee to zeran tutuuŋa. Saawe tana, tamtamon siriv tau tileep tomani zi na, matazi ilala pa Yesu tighe tighita pale igham saa ŋgar? \x * \xo 14:1 \xt Lu 11:37\x*   
\p
\v 2 Malau mako ve ŋeer ee iburig iyooz ila Yesu naagho. I, sariiŋ tiina ighamu.  
\v 3 Tauvene Yesu ighason ila pa zeran tutuuŋa ve yes ŋgara to tutuuŋ ighe: “Laak, yam agham ŋgar mindai? Isaav ighe tagharaat yes moroghooŋa pa saawe to umbom patabuyaaŋ, ene iduduuŋ pa tutuuŋ to Maaron, ma mako?” \x * \xo 14:3 \xt Mt 12:10; Lu 6:9\x*   
\m
\v 4 Yes tisavia saveeŋ eta mako. Tineneeŋ mon. Tauvene Yesu niima ila ikis ŋeer tana, igharaata le tiini poia, ve isaav pani gha ila.   
\p
\v 5 Ra ighason zi muul ighe: “Mindai, saawe to umbom patabuyaaŋ, isaav ighe tsiam eta naatu, ma makau tooni itap izila puura to yaa, pale ipuli igheen? Mako. I pale rekia mon ila ve ighamu izaa.” \x * \xo 14:5 \xt Mt 12:11; Lu 13:15\x*   
\p
\v 6 Yes tilooŋ saveeŋ tane le tilil pa savsaveeŋ. Tauvene tineneeŋ mon.   
\s1 Tapakur tauun sov  
\p
\v 7 Tamtamon siriv tau tisain zi tilam pa ghanghaniiŋ tana na, tizazain tauzi tighe tileep ila paŋ popoiazi tau tighuru pa yes tau ezazi tintiina na. Yesu ighita ŋgar tana, ve isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ pazi tauvene: \x * \xo 14:7 \xt Mt 23:6\x*   
\p
\v 8 “Isaav ighe ŋeer eta isain ghom pa ghanghaniiŋ to vaiŋ, na mbolem izi sorok ila paŋ tau tighuru pa yes tau ezazi tintiina na sov. Pa ighe ghanghaniiŋ taama isain ŋeer eta tau eeza tiina iliiv ghom na ilam paam,  
\v 9 ene pale ghanghaniiŋ taama ilat, ve isaav payo ighe: ‘Enes, uburig upul paŋ tane, ve ŋeer tawe ilam mboole izi.’ Ene pale uburig toman mayam tiina, ve umuul ula uleep paŋ ta murei geeg we.  
\v 10 Tauvene isaav ighe tisain ghom pa ghanghaniiŋ eta, na upakur ghom ve ula mbolem izi muŋgaaŋ sov. Ula mbolem izi ila paŋ tau igheen murei geeg. Pa ighe ghanghaniiŋ taama ilam, ve isaav payo ighe: ‘Etag ite, uburig ulam mbolem izi muŋgaaŋ igharau ghau.’ Ighe i igham tauvene, ene imin ipakur ghom ila eval tiina tau yamŋa aghanghan na naghozi.  
\v 11 Pa tamtamon tau ighe ipakur tauu eeza, ene pale titatan eeza izi. Ve isaav ighe tamtamon eta itatan tauu eeza, ene pale tipakuru, ve eeza imin tiina.” \x * \xo 14:11 \xt Mt 23:12; Lu 18:14; Yems 4:6; 1Pe 5:5\x*   
\p
\v 12 Ra Yesu isaav pa ŋeer tau isaini ilam pa ghanghaniiŋ tana ighe: “Isaav ighe ugham ghanghaniiŋ, na upoi zetamŋa, toŋvetaz tsio, ziiri waaro tsio, ma yes kuaz tauŋa tau tileep tigharau ghom na sov. Pa murei, yes pale tisain ghom pa ghanghaniiŋ tomani zi ve tiyol mulin nimam. Ene atuya tsio.  
\v 13-14 Tauvene isaav ighe yo ugham ghanghaniiŋ, na upoi yes tau irau tigham ghanghaniiŋ mako na, imin yes mbolaaŋa, yes narapeŋa, ve yes tau matazi kumkuuma na. Leso poia to Maaron izaa tsio, ve saawe tau i ipaburigin tamtamon duduŋazi pa mateegh, ene pale i tauu iyol nimam, ve igham lem atuya poia.” \x * \xo 14:13-14 \xt Lo 14:29; Yo 5:29\x*   
\s1 Poiŋ to Maaron tau ilam pait na, tambuzir pani sov  
\r (Mt 22:1-10)  
\p
\v 15 Yes tau yesŋa Yesu tilup zi pa ghanghaniiŋ ila boor eemon na, tamtamon toozi ee ilooŋ Yesu saveeŋ tooni, ve isaav pani ighe: “Yes tau tiloŋ tila Maaron nugh tooni pa ghanghaniiŋ ta sewe, ene pale tintinizi pa poia to Maaron tau pale izaa toozi.” \x * \xo 14:15 \xt Lu 13:29; Syg 19:9\x*   
\p
\v 16 Yesu iyol aliiŋa pa saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane ighe: “Pai ee, ŋeer ee ighe igham ghanghaniiŋ tiina. Tauvene isain tamtamon katini ighe tilam pa ghanghaniiŋ tana.  
\v 17 Saawe tau ghanghaniiŋ ighe ivot, i imbaaŋ besooŋa tooni ee imuul ila, leso isaav pa yes tau poiŋ to tiina tooni igham zi na ighe: ‘Ai, yam alam rekia! Pa tigharaat gabua tisov wa.’   
\p
\v 18 “Eemon yes tisov tinizi imum. Tauvene tipalele saveeŋ, leso tila pa ghanghaniiŋ tawe sov. Ŋeer tau besooŋa tana ila ivot tooni imin maata na, isaav pani ighe: ‘Poia, irau to nalat. Eemon leg uraat rig. Yau naghol taan sirivu ee, ve aazne naghe nala naghita.’  
\v 19 Ŋeer ite imin ru aana isaav pani ighe: ‘Poia, irau to nalat. Eemon naghol bapolo saŋavul, ve aazne naghe nala natoov zi pa uraat.’   
\m
\v 20 Ve ŋeer ite imin tol aana isaav pani ighe: ‘Yau ŋgarig gha navai. Tauvene irau nalat mako.’ \x * \xo 14:20 \xt 1Kor 7:33\x*   
\p
\v 21 “Besooŋa tana imuul ila to tiina tooni, ve ipaesia aliŋazi pani. Tiina tooni ilooŋ saveeŋ tooni le aate yavyav kat, ve isaav pani: ‘Ighe tauvene, na rekia mon umuul ula, ve ulaagh taghon eez tintiina ve geegeu to nugh, ve uyau yes mbolaaŋa, yes narapeŋa, ve yes tau matazi kumkuuma na, ve yamŋa alam.’   
\p
\v 22 “Tauvene besooŋa tana imuul ila ve igham uratoi tiina tooni aliiŋa. Le isov, ra imuul ilam, ve ipaes pani ighe: ‘Tiina tsiau, aliŋam tau yo usavia na, tauta nagham uratoini le isov. Eemon ruum to ghanghaniiŋ, sooso ighengheen soone.’   
\p
\v 23 “Tiina tooni iyol aliiŋa: ‘Ighe tauvene, na upul nugh tane ve ula ulaagh taghon eez ve uum zigezi, ve umbuur ariaaŋ pa tamtamon, ve yamŋa alam. Leso tipavon ruum tsiau le ivon kat.  
\v 24 Yau nasaav payam. Yes tau poiŋ tsiau igham zi ve tinizi imum na, toozi eta irau aavo itut aniiŋ tsiau mako le mako kat!’” \x * \xo 14:24 \xt Mt 21:43; Mbaŋ 13:46\x*   
\s1 Tagabiiz tauun poi, o tataghon Yesu  
\r (Mt 10:37-38)  
\p
\v 25 Eval tiina titaghon Yesu gha yesŋa tilaghlaagh. Yesu itoor ghi ve isaav pazi ighe:  
\v 26 “Isaav ighe tamtamon eta loolo pa taama, tiina, azaawa, natŋa, toŋvetaz tooni, ma tauu lepoogh tooni iliiv ghau, ene irau imin ziŋerag ve itaghon ghau ne mako.  
\v 27 Ve isaav ighe ŋeer eta ibaad ai pambarooŋ tooni \f + \fr 14:27 \ft Ai pambarooŋ toit, ene pataŋani maata maata tau tabaado pa Yesu eeza.\f*  
\m ve itaghon ghau mako, ene i paam, irau imin ziŋerag mako. \x * \xo 14:27 \xt Mt 16:24+; Lu 9:23+; 2Tim 3:12\x*   
\p
\v 28 “Isaav ighe tsiam eta igham ŋgar pa raoŋ ruum tau daaba malaua na, i aat ileep ve inin poghania maet tooni imin maata. Pale irau ipasov ruum, ma mako? Isaav ighe maet tooni irau, ene aat ipaburigin uraat.  
\v 29-30 Pa ighe ipaburigin uraat to raoŋ ruum, ve ipasovu mako, ene pale tamtamon tisov tau tighita uraat tooni, tiŋiŋ pani ve tiveleghi tighe: ‘Wai, ŋeer tawe igham tiini pa raoŋ ruum tiina na. Ipasovu wa?’   
\p
\v 31 “Ve kinik tau ighe igham malmal pa kinik ite, ene pale itaghon ŋgar raraate mon. Ighe i le zaaba 10,000 mon, ve kinik ite le zaaba 20,000. Ene aat igabiiz zaaba tooni imin maata, ve igham ŋgar poi: Irau tigham malmal pa kinik ite tawe, ma mako?  
\v 32 Ighe mako, saawe tau kinik tawe ilaghlaagh malau soone, i aat imbaaŋ uraata siriv tila to tigharaat saveeŋ, leso malmal ivot sov.” \x * \xo 14:32 \xt 2Kor 5:20\x*   
\p
\v 33 Ra Yesu iparwai saveeŋ tooni ighe: “Yam tauvene paam. Isaav ighe tsiam eta ighur muuri pa gabua tooni naol isov mako, ene irau imin ziŋerag ve itaghon ghau ne mako.” \f + \fr 14:33 \ft Saveeŋ tane, ŋgara tauvene: Iit aat taghur Krisi imuuŋ pa gabua toit naol isov: maet, taan, uraat, toŋvetaz toit, ezaan, ve gabua ta naol ne.\f* \x * \xo 14:33 \xt Lu 5:11, 28; Pil 3:7+\x*   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to te (o sol)  
\r (Mt 5:13; Mk 9:50)  
\p
\v 34 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Te, \f + \fr 14:34 \ft Paesiiŋ to saveeŋ ziiri tane igheen ila Mt 5:13. \f*  
\m ene gabua poia. Eemon isaav ighe tapiri isov ve tetei muul mako, ene pale tagharaata mindai? Mako. \x * \xo 14:34 \xt Hib 6:4-6\x*   
\m
\v 35 Te tauvene, le uraat muul mako. Irau takep tomania ŋgai taae to igham taan ŋgoreeŋa ne mako. Tauvene tisiki ilale. Tamtamon tau ighe le taliiŋa, i aat ilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve igham ŋgar pani poi.”   
\c 15  
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to sipsip tau ilale  
\r (Mt 18:12-14)  
\p
\v 1 Saawe ee, tamtamon siriv to yauŋ takes, tomania zeran siriv to ghamuuŋ sosor tila to Yesu tighe tilooŋ saveeŋ tooni.  
\v 2 Zeran tutuuŋa siriv tomania ŋgara siriv to tutuuŋ tighit zi, ve tiyau avozi pa Yesu tighe: “Wai, ŋeer tawe, mindai ta igham zeran to ghamuuŋ sosor toman loolo poia, ve yesŋa tiluplup zi pa ghanghaniiŋ?” \x * \xo 15:2 \xt Lu 5:30; Mbaŋ 11:3\x*   
\p
\v 3 Tauvene Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane pazi ighe:   
\p
\v 4 “Isaav ighe tsiam eta le sipsip ndiŋndiŋ ee (100), ve iŋginŋgin zi izi nugh ŋginaaŋa, ve eta ilale, ene pale igham mindai? I pale ipul sipsip tooni tamoot paaŋ saŋavul liim ve paaŋ (99) tana tileep, ve ila iil sipsip tooni tau ilale na, le irau indeeŋa. \x * \xo 15:4 \xt Ezek 34:11, 16; Lu 19:10; Yo 10:11\x*   
\m
\v 5 Saawe tau ighe indeeŋa, ene aat iiti izala avaara,  
\v 6 ve ibaado imuul ila pa nugh tooni toman tintini. Mako ipoi zeetŋa ve yes tau tileep tigharauu na tilam, ve isaav pazi ighe: ‘Alam, itiŋa loloon poia ve tintiniin! Pa sipsip tsiau tau ilale na, nandeeŋa wa!’ \x * \xo 15:6 \xt 1Pe 2:25\x*   
\p
\v 7 “Yau nasaav payam. Isaav ighe ŋeer eta to ghamuuŋ sosor ipul ŋgar tooni saghati ileple, ve itoor ŋgar tooni ila pa Maaron, ene yes to nugh sambam tighamgham tauvene paam. Lolozi poia kat, ve tintinizi pa ŋeer eemon tana iliiv zeran tamoot paaŋ saŋavul liim ve paaŋ (99) tau tinumeer tighe tiduduuŋ ila Maaron maata ve lezi puughu eta to titoor ŋgar toozi mako.”   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to maet tau ilale  
\p
\v 8 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Isaav ighe livaa eta le maet silva saŋavul, ve eta ilale, ene pale igham mindai? I pale itun lam, ve izaar ruum loolo, ve maata ines poi pa maet tana le irau indeeŋa.  
\v 9 Saawe tau ighe indeeŋa, i pale ipoi zeetŋa ve yes tau tileep tigharauu na tilam, ve isaav pazi ighe: ‘Alei, alam itiŋa loloon poia ve tintiniin. Pa maet tsiau tau ilale na, nandeeŋa wa.’   
\p
\v 10 “Yau nasaav payam: Isaav ighe ŋeer eta to ghamuuŋ sosor ipul ŋgar tooni saghati ileple, ve itoor ŋgar tooni ila pa Maaron, ene ŋgar raraate ivotvot ila aŋela to Maaron sosozi paam. Yes lolozi poia kat, ve tintinizi pa ŋeer eemon tana.”   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to ŋeer tau loolo igheen to natŋa ru kat  
\p
\v 11 Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ ite paam pazi ighe:  
\p “Saawe ee, ŋeer ee ilepleep. I natŋa ru.  
\v 12 Tilepleep ve ŋeer muria iburig, ve isaav pa taama ighe: ‘Tamaŋ, yau naghe yo uvalagh gabua tsio, ve saa gabua tau yo ughe upuli imin leg, na ugham payau pataghaaŋ.’ Taama itaghon aliiŋa, ve ivalagh gabua tooni imin ru, ve ighur sirivu ila pa ŋeer muria, ve sirivu igheen pa ŋeer olman.   
\p
\v 13-14 “Saawe siriv ilam ila, ra naatu muria iyau gabua tooni naol isov, ve iburig tomania gha ila pa nugh malau. Ila ivot ta sewe, ra isuruuv maet tooni pa gabua soroksorok naol le maet isov. Malau mako ve pitool tiina ivot izi nugh tawe. Tauta mbolaaŋ igham ŋeer tana le lepoogha poia mako.  
\v 15 Tauvene ila ighason nugh tauŋa ee pa uraat. I iyok pani, ve imbaaŋo ila pa ŋginiiŋ ŋgai tooni.  
\v 16 I pitoola kat. Eemon eta igham le aniiŋ mako. Tauvene ighe le ighan ŋgai aniiŋ toozi siriv. Eemon aniiŋ tawe paam, eta igham pani mako.   
\p
\v 17 “I ilepleep ila le ighilaal ighe i isosor wa. Ra ipasawal muul pa lepoogh tooni ta muuŋ na ighe: ‘Oyai, uraata to tamaŋ tighanghan le apozi isuŋ, ve aniiŋ sirivu izi igheen. Ve yau tane, aazne namaat pa pitool.  
\v 18 Tambaaŋo. Yau aat namuul nala pa tamaŋ. Saawe tau nala navot tooni, ene aat nasaav pani naghe: Tamaŋ, yau nagham sosor pa Maaron to sambam, ve nagham sosor payo paam. \x * \xo 15:18 \xt Mbo 51:4\x*   
\m
\v 19 Yau poiag mako. Tauvene irau uwaat ghau ughe natum muul sov. Mindai, irau uyok ve namin uraata payo?’   
\p
\v 20 “I igharaat ŋgar tooni le isov, ra imuul ila pa taama. Ilaghlaagh malau soone, ve taama maata ila le ighita. Rekia mon ighilaalo ve loolo isaghatini. Tauvene ilaan ila isaghavu, ve itaŋ pani.  
\v 21 Ra naatu isaav pani ighe: ‘Tamaŋ, yau nagham sosor pa Maaron to sambam, ve nagham sosor payo paam. Yau poiag mako. Tauvene irau uwaat ghau natum muul mako.’   
\p
\v 22 “Eemon taama irav motin saveeŋ tooni, ve isaav pa yes besooŋa tooni ighe: ‘Ai, yam rekia ala agham nonoghiiŋa malaua tau paghuuna kat na ilam, ve anonogh natug tane pani. Ve agham ring, ve aghuru ila niima ŋguruuŋa, ve azeev zuzuuŋa ila aaghe.  
\v 23 Ve yam siriv ala agham makau naatu toman tumbuuŋa tau naghuru pa ghanghaniiŋ na, ve aravu. Leso tagham ghanghaniiŋ pa natug tane toman tintiniin.  
\v 24 Pasaa, iit taghe pa i imaat wa. Eemon mako. Maata yaryaare, ve imuul ilam ivot. Taghe pa i ilale wa. Eemon mako. Aazne, taghita muul.’ Tauvene besooŋa tooni tila tigham uraat itaghon olman aliiŋa. Ra tilup zi pa ghanghaniiŋ toman tintinizi. \x * \xo 15:24 \xt Ep 2:1, 5\x*   
\p
\v 25 “Malau mako ve naatu olman aana ileep uum gha ilam. Ilaagh ilam igharau ruum, ve ilooŋ oroor tiina. Ambam itaŋtaŋ ve tighamgham narogho.  
\v 26 Tauvene ipoi besooŋa ee ilam, ve ighasoni ighe: ‘Ai, ewe tigham saa?’   
\p
\v 27 “Besooŋa tana iyol aliiŋa ighe: ‘Taghe pa tazim imaat wa. Eemon mako. Imuul ilam toman tiini poia! Tauta tamam loolo poia kat, ve irav makau naatu tau ighuru pa ghanghaniiŋ na gha tighanghan pani.’   
\p
\v 28 “Naatu olman ilooŋ saveeŋ tane, le irau loolo mako ve aate yavyav kat. Tauta loolo pa iloŋ ila ruum mako. Tauvene taama ivot ila tooni, ve itoova to irav aate.  
\v 29 Eemon i isaav pa taama ighe: ‘Tamaŋ, ndaman katini, yau naleep tomani ghom, ve nakaria uraat payo. Nazoor aliŋam rigta mako. Eemon aaz eta, yo upakur ghau pa gabua eta mako. Mako kat. Imin ta ugham leg mekmek naatu eta to yeŋa zetagŋa nighanghan toman tintiinmai, kanaŋ lolog poia rig. Eemon mako.  
\v 30 Ve natum tawe, i ila ve yesŋa zilivaa to eez tivaghamunia gabua tsio le isov. Eemon saawe tau imuul ilam, yo urav makau naatu poia tau taghuru pa ghanghaniiŋ na pani!’   
\p
\v 31 “Taama iyol aliiŋa ighe: ‘O natug, saawe isov, ituru talepleep. Ve gabua tsiau ta naol ne, ene yo tsio.  
\v 32 Ughita. Iit taghe pa tazim imaat wa. Eemon ileep maata yaryaare. Ve taghe pa ilale wa. Eemon aazne, ilam peria ve taghita muul. Tauvene isaav ighe tagham ghanghaniiŋ pani toman tintiniin, ene iduduuŋ.’”   
\c 16  
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to uraata tau iil eez pa tauu leso murei ileep poia  
\p
\v 1 Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane pa mbiwa tooni ighe: “Pai ee, kuaz tauu ee ilepleep. I le uraata ee tau iŋginŋgin gabua tooni. Eemon zeran siriv tilam ve tiŋgal saveeŋ pa uraata tooni tawe tighe i isusuruuv maet tomania gabua siriv to tiina tooni soroksorok.  
\v 2 Tauvene kuaz tauu tana ipoii ilam, ve isaav pani ighe: ‘Yo ugham uraat mindai? Pasaa, nakaria loŋaaŋ saveeŋ tsio wa. Yo ula rekia ve ubood uraat tsio ta ughamghamu na saveeŋa ila rau, ve ughamu ilam naghita. Pa yo aat usov pa uraat tane. Irau uŋgin gabua tsiau muul mako.’   
\p
\v 3 “Uraata tooni ilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve iil ŋgar ighe: ‘Wai, tiina tsiau ighe ipasov ghau pa uraat to ŋginiiŋ gabua tooni. Pale nagham mindai? Tapirig irau to nagham uraat pataŋani imin mbutuuŋ taan ne mako. Ve mayag paam pa suŋuuŋ tamtamon pa leg gabua.’  
\v 4 Tauvene ilepleep le ŋgar ee ivot pani, ve isaav ighe: ‘Aa! Ŋgarig gha matag iŋgal ŋgar ee! Isaav ighe nagham tauvene, ene pale tamtamon lolozi poia payau, ve saawe tau tiina tsiau ipasov ghau pa uraat, tamtamon siriv pale tigham ghau nala ruum toozi, ve naleep ila nimazi.’   
\p
\v 5 “Ra i ipoi yes tau lezi bun igheen ila to tiina tooni na, ve eŋaeŋa tilam tooni. I tau ila ivot tooni imin maata na, uraata tana ighasoni ighe: ‘Ai, usaav: Bun tsio piiz igheen ila to tiina tsiau?’   
\p
\v 6 “Ŋeer tawe iyol aliiŋa ighe: ‘Ŋgoreeŋ tau igheen ila patuzi tintiina irau ndiŋndiŋ ee (100).’  
\p “Uraata tana isaav pani ighe: ‘Yau aat nazuure izi rig. Enes, ugham rau tau bun tsio igheen ila na, mbolem izi, ve rekia mon ubood tamoot ru saŋavul (50) mon. Ve sirivu ileple.’   
\p
\v 7 “Ra ŋeer ite aana ila ivot tooni, ve uraata tana ighasoni ighe: ‘Aiyo, usaav: Bun tsio piiz?’  
\p “I iyol aliiŋa ighe: ‘Bek ndiŋndiŋ ee (100) tau tivoniir pa aniiŋ wit.’  
\p “Uraata tana isaav pani ighe: ‘Enes, ugham rau tau bun tsio igheen ila na, ve ubood bek wit tamoot paaŋ (80) mon.’”   
\p
\v 8 Ra Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Onoon, ŋgar tau uraata tana ighamu na, iduduuŋ mako. Eemon saawe tau tiina tooni ilooŋ vaaru, i ipait uraata tana eeza. Pasaa, i igham ŋgar pa pataŋani tau ighe ivot pani, ve iil eez pa tauu leso murei ileep poia.  
\p “Tamtamon tau titaghon ŋgar to taan na, tiliiv yes tau titaghon ŋgar to ghazooŋa. Pasaa, yes tiwatagh katin saa ŋgar to taan tau yes irau tighamu, leso tileep poia izi taan. Ve titaghon ŋgar tawe. Eemon yes tau tiwatagh ŋgar to ghazooŋa na, titaghoni irao mako. \x * \xo 16:8 \xt Yo 12:36; Ep 5:8; 1Tes 5:5\x*   
\m
\v 9 “Yau nasaav payam: Ail eez pa taumim, leso murei aleep poia. Maet to taan tau imin puughu pa ŋgar sasaghati naol na, yam areii pa tamtamon. Leso lolozi poia payam. Ve murei, saawe tau maet to taan isov, ene pale tigham gham ala aleep poia ila ruum tsiam izi nugh sambam taghon taghon gha ila.   
\s1 Gabua to sambam, ene gabua tauu  
\p
\v 10 “Isaav ighe tamtamon eta iŋgin poghania gabua ŋgiira tau tighuru ila niima, ene pale iŋgin poghania gabua tiina paam. Ve isaav ighe tamtamon eta igham ŋgar tau iduduuŋ mako pa gabua ŋgiira, ene pale igham ŋgar raraate mon pa gabua tiina paam. \x * \xo 16:10 \xt Lu 19:17+\x*   
\m
\v 11 Maet to taan, gabua tauu mako. Ve imin puughu pa ŋgar sasaghati naol. Tauvene isaav ighe yam aŋgin poghania maet itaghon Maaron ŋgar tooni mako, ene pale ighur gabua tauu to sambam ila nimamim mindai? Ene aat mako.   
\m
\v 12 Onoon kat, isaav ighe tighur gabua ila nimamim ve aŋgin poghania mako, ene pale sei igham gabua imin lemim kat? \f + \fr 16:12 \ft Maaron ighur gabua naol ila nimaan ve ighe taŋgin poghania itaghon i tauu ŋgar tooni: Maet, taan toit, tapiriin, ŋgar, saveeŋ tooni, azuwaanŋa, natuunŋa ve gabua siriv paam. Isaav ighe iit taŋgin poghania gabua naol tawe mako, i irau igham leen gabua tauu to nugh sambam mako.\f*   
\m
\v 13 “Besooŋa eta irau ibees poi pa daaba ru mako. Pale ighur loolo pa ee, ve loolo isaghavu kat. Ve ite, ene pale ighur loolo pani geeg mako, ve maata veleghini. Tauvene yam irau abees poi pa Maaron tomania kuaz to taan ne mako.” \x * \xo 16:13 \xt Mt 6:24\x*   
\p
\v 14 Zeran tutuuŋa tighur lolozi kat pa maet. Yes tilooŋ saveeŋ isov tana, ve tisik saveeŋ veleghiiŋ naol pa Yesu.  
\v 15 Tauvene Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Yam aghamgham ŋgar naol ila tamtamon matazi, leso tighit gham tighe yam zeran duduŋamim. Eemon Maaron iwatagh lolomim wa. Ve alooŋ! Gabua tau tamtamon tighita tighe gabua tiina, ene Maaron ighita ighe gabua saghati kat.” \x * \xo 16:15 \xt Mbo 7:9; Mt 23:28, 18:9+\x*   
\s1 Tutuuŋ to Maaron ve pooz tooni  
\p
\v 16 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Tutuuŋ to Mose ve saveeŋ to yes propet itotoi tamtamon pa eez to Maaron le ilam imuul saawe to ŋeer rughuzaaŋa Yoan. Eemon saawe tana ve ilam, tamtamon tivovotia vaaru poia pa pooz to Maaron, ve eval tiina tizuari zi tighe le tiloŋ tila pooz tooni loolo. \f + \fr 16:16 \ft Eez ite to tatoor saveeŋ tane, ene vene: “Eemon saawe tana ve ilam, tamtamon tivovotia vaaru poia pa pooz to Maaron, ve avozi iyaryaaŋ pa tamtamon tisov tighe yes aat tizuari zi leso tiloŋ tila pooz tooni loolo.”\f* \x * \xo 16:16 \xt Mt 11:12+; Ro 10:4\x*   
\p
\v 17 “Sambam ve taan, ene iraurau pa Maaron to ipasov zi. Eemon tutuuŋ tooni ziiri ŋgiira rigta irau ilale ne mako. Mako le mako kat. \x * \xo 16:17 \xt Mbo 119:89; Is 40:8; Mt 5:18; Lu 21:33; 1Pe 1:25\x*   
\s1 Yesu isavia ŋgar to ravuuŋ motin vaiŋ  
\p
\v 18 “Isaav ighe ŋeer eta iziir azaawa ila ve ivai livaa paaghu, ene imalaaŋ pa tutuuŋ to vaiŋ. Ve isaav ighe ŋeer eta ivai livaa eta tau azaawa iziire na, ene i paam imalaaŋ pa tutuuŋ to vaiŋ.” \x * \xo 16:18 \xt Mt 5:32, 19:9; Ro 7:2+; 1Kor 7:10+\x*   
\s1 Kuaz tauu ve Lasarus  
\p
\v 19 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Pai ee, kuaz tauu ee ilepleep. Lepoogh tooni poia kat. Monmon inonogh ghi pa nonoghiiŋa popoiazi mon tau ŋgeretazi imin aindan ve atuyazi tintiina kat. Ve saawe isov, ighanghan aniiŋ popoia mon, ve ilepleep toman tintini.  
\v 20 Mbolaaŋa ee ilepleep igharau kuaz tauu tawe. Eeza Lasarus. I narape, ve tiini isov mbotmboot. Monmon tisursuru ila, ve tighuru izi igharau kuaz tauu tana ataman tooni aavo.  
\v 21 Lasarus pitoola kat. Tauvene ighe le ighan aniiŋ ŋgirŋgiira tau itaptap pa kuaz tauu boor tooni na. Saawe tau ilepleep ta sewe, ŋgavuun tilamlam ve tindadamoz mbotmboota.   
\p
\v 22 “I ilepleep toman pataŋani tauvene le imaat. Ra aŋela tighamu ve tighuru ileep ila nugh poia igharau Abaram ziige. Murei ra, kuaz tauu aana imaat ve titavia.   
\p
\v 23 “I izila nugh saghati to mateegha, ve iyamaan yavyavuuŋ tiina kat. Maata izala le ighita Abaram yesuru Lasarus tilepleep malau kat.  
\v 24 Tauvene iboob ila pa Abaram ighe: ‘Oyai, tamaŋ Abaram, lolom raa, isaghatin ghau ve umbaaŋ Lasarus ilam. Leso izeev niima ŋguruuŋa izila yaa, ve ipaluum yamag rigta. Pasaa, yau naleep ila yav tane loolo, ve yavyavuuŋ tiina kat igham ghau.’ \x * \xo 16:24 \xt Mk 9:48\x*   
\p
\v 25 “Eemon Abaram iyol aliiŋa ighe: ‘Oo natug, matam iŋgal lepoogh tsio tau muuŋ ughamu izi taan na. Saawe tana, yo uleep poia mon, ve Lasarus ileep saghat. Tauta aazne, aate izi ve igham lepoogh poia izi nugh tane, ve yo uyamaan yavyavuuŋ tiina ta sena. \x * \xo 16:25 \xt Lu 6:24\x*   
\m
\v 26 Ve gabua ite. Ughita. Maaron ighur sapsapu tiina tane isap sosoon. Leso tamtamon eta to sene ighe ilat tsiam, ene aat irau ilat mako. Ve yam tauvene paam. Tsiam eta irau ilam iliv ta sene mako.’   
\p
\v 27 “Kuaz tauu ilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve itaŋ rarai Abaram muul ighe: ‘O tamaŋ, ighe tauvene, na umbaaŋ Lasarus imuul ila pa tamaŋ ruum tooni,  
\v 28 ve iveveen tazigŋa liim tau tilepleep we, leso titoor ŋgar toozi. Mako pale yes paam titaghon ghau tilam pa nugh to yavyavuuŋ tane.’   
\p
\v 29 “Abaram iyol aliiŋa ighe: ‘Saveeŋ to Mose ve yes propet, ene tiwataghi wa. Yes irau tilooŋa ve titaghoni.’ \x * \xo 16:29 \xt 2Tim 3:16+\x*   
\p
\v 30 “Kuaz tauu isaav pani muul ighe: ‘Tamaŋ Abaram, ŋgar tsio tana poia. Eemon irau ighur mako. Ve isaav ighe mateegha eta iburig gha ila ivot toozi ve ipaes pazi, ene aat tighur ila saveeŋ tooni, ve titoor ŋgar toozi.’   
\p
\v 31 “Abaram iyol aliiŋa ighe: ‘Mako. Ighe tilooŋ Mose tomania yes propet aliŋazi mako, ene pale tamtamon tau iburig pa mateegh na paam, irau igham zi tighur ila mako.’” \x * \xo 16:31 \xt Yo 11:44, 12:10+\x*   
\c 17  
\s1 Tagham zetaanŋa titap pa ghuruuŋ ila toozi sov  
\r (Mt 18:6-7, 21-22; Mk 9:42)  
\p
\v 1-2 Yesu isaav pa mbiwa tooni ighe: “Tovaaŋ maata maata pale ivot pa tamtamon, ve igham zi titap pa ghuruuŋ ila toozi. Eemon tamtamon tau ighe imin watiiŋ pa marani eta, ve ighamu itap pa ghuruuŋ ila tooni, ene i ikaria tauu wa. Tamtamon tauvene, poia to timbit maet tiina ila luua, ve tipazalia izila te gha ilale. Tauvene matamim imomoos poi pa taumim!   
\p
\v 3 “Isaav ighe toŋvetaz tsio eta igham sosor, na ula tooni ve usaav duduuŋ pani pa sosor tooni. Isaav ighe ilooŋ ghom ve itoor ŋgar tooni, o upul sosor tooni, ve lolom iveegh pani. \x * \xo 17:3 \xt Mt 18:15; Ep 4:32\x*   
\m
\v 4 Isaav ighe i igham sosor payo pai liim ve ru pa aaz eemon, ve ilatlat tsio ve isavsaav payo ighe: ‘Yau naghilaal sosor tsiau, ve natoor ŋgar tsiau wa.’ Na yo paam, upul sosor tooni ve lolom iveegh pani.” \x * \xo 17:4 \xt Mt 18:21-22\x*   
\p
\v 5 Mbaŋooŋa tooni tilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve tisaav pani tighe: “Tiina, ighe tauvene, na ugham ghuruuŋ ila tsiei ivot imin tiina.”   
\p
\v 6 Yesu isaav pazi: “Isaav ighe ghuruuŋ ila tsiam ŋgiira rigmon imin mastet uuve, \f + \fr 17:6 \ft Mastet, ene gabua tau itum izaa imin was ma vene. Ve uuve, ene geegeu kat imin dog paatu, ma mbuas uuve.\f*  
\m na yam pale irau asaav pa ai tiina tane aghe: ‘Ukuul taum uzaa, ve ula upayooz taum ila te loolo.’ Ve ai tane pale itaghon aliŋamim.” \x * \xo 17:6 \xt Mt 17:20; Mk 11:23\x*   
\s1 Isaav ighe tagham uraat to Maaron, taghur mataan pa pakuruuŋ to tamtamon sov  
\p
\v 7 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Isaav ighe tsiam eta isaav pa besooŋa tooni ve ila imbut uum, ma iŋgin sipsip tooni, ve ravrav besooŋa tawe imuul ila pa ruum, ene pale isaav mindai pa besooŋa tana? Pale rekia mon isaav pani ighe: ‘Ulam, mbolem izi, ve ughan?’  
\v 8 Ene aat mako. Pale isaav pani tauvene: ‘Yo ula ugharaat aniiŋ payau le isov, mako ugharaat ghom, ve umuul ulam ubees payau le irau naghan ma naghun isov. O anam mbolem izi, ve ughan ma ughun.’ \x * \xo 17:8 \xt Lu 12:37\x*   
\p
\v 9 “Ve mindai? Isaav ighe besooŋa tooni ilooŋ aliiŋa ve igham uraat tana isov, pale tiina tooni ipakuru? Mako. Pasaa, ene i uraat tooni.  
\v 10 Yam tauvene paam. Isaav ighe agham gabua isov tau Maaron isavia payam to agham zi, na asaav mon aghe: ‘Yei besooŋa to Maaron. Nigham gabua poia eta irau to tipakur ghei pani ne mako. Uraat tau i ighuru ila nimamai, tauta nighamu.’” \x * \xo 17:10 \xt 1Kor 9:16+\x*   
\s1 Yesu igharaat tamtamon saŋavul tau mbotmboot kolekole igham zi  
\p
\v 11 Yesu ilaagh taghon eez tau ila pa Yerusalem, le ila ivot bodbodaaŋ pa Samaria ve Galilaia.  
\v 12-13 I iloŋ ila nugh ee tau igheen sewe, ve izaa to zeran saŋavul tau moroghooŋ kolekole igham zi. Tauvene tiyooz malau, ve tiboob ila pani tighe: “Yesu, tiina tsiei, lolom isaghatin ghei ve uul ghei lak!” \x * \xo 17:12-13 \xt Wkp 13:45+\x*   
\p
\v 14 Yesu ighit zi, ve isaav pazi ighe: “Yam ala atotoi taumim pa yes zeran to watooŋrau.” Tauvene tipuli ve tila. Tilaagh taghon eez tila, ve Maaron tapiri igham zi tinizi poia le tiŋgalaaŋ ila i maata. \x * \xo 17:14 \xt Lu 5:14\x*   
\m
\v 15 Toozi ee ighilaal ighe Maaron iuule ta tiini poia. Tauvene ipapait Maaron eeza toman aliiŋa tiina, ve imuul ila pa Yesu.  
\v 16 Ila ivot tooni, ve itap izi Yesu aaghe puughu, ve ighur naagho izila pa taan, ve ipaiti toman loolo poia. Ŋeer tawe, i Yuda mako. I to Samaria.   
\p
\v 17 Yesu ighita ŋeer tana, ve isaav ighe: “Wai, yau naghe pa nagharaat tamtamon saŋavul tinizi poia. Liim ve paaŋ tileep sindei?  
\v 18 Ŋeer tane, i Yuda mako. Puughu mindai ta i zigani imuul ilam ve ipait Maaron eeza, ve yes siriv mako?”  
\v 19 Ra Yesu isaav pa ŋeer tana ighe: “Uburig ve ula toman lolom poia. Ghuruuŋ ila tsio, tauta igham ghom tinim poia, ve Maaron igham mulin ghom wa.” \x * \xo 17:19 \xt Mt 9:22; Lu 7:50\x*   
\s1 Pooz to Maaron ivot mindai?  
\p
\v 20 Saawe ee, zeran tutuuŋa siriv tighason Yesu tighe: “Pale ŋeez, o pooz to Maaron ivot ighazooŋ?”  
\p Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Pooz to Maaron ivot toman ilaal tiina eta tau tamtamon irau tighita pa matazi ne mako.  
\v 21 Tauvene tamtamon irau tisaav tighe: ‘Aghita. Pooz to Maaron igheen sene,’ o ‘igheen sewe,’ ene mako. Pasaa, pooz to Maaron, ene gabua tau ivot ila lolomim.” \x * \xo 17:21 \xt Yo 3:3; Ro 14:17\x*   
\s1 Saawe tau Tamtamon Naatu pale itotoi pooz tooni ivot ighazooŋ  
\r (Mt 24:23-28, 37-41; Mk 13:14-23)  
\p
\v 22 Ra Yesu isaav pa mbiwa tooni ighe: “Murei, saawe saghati kat pale ivot, ve yam apasul aghe le aghita Tamtamon Naatu itotoi pooz tooni ivot ighazooŋ rigta, o poia. Eemon yam irau aghita rekia mako.  
\v 23 Tauvene matamim imomoos poi pa taumim. Pa zeran siriv pale tisaav payam tighe: ‘Aghita. I tauu ta ewe!’, ma tighe: ‘I tauu ta ene!’ Eemon yam ala ataghon zi sov. \x * \xo 17:23 \xt Lu 21:8; 2Tes 2:1\x*   
\m
\v 24 Pa saawe tau Tamtamon Naatu imuul ilam ve itotoi tapiri ivot ighazooŋ, ene pale tamtamon tisov tighita. I pale izilam imin nugh ighani milia ila sambam saamba ziige ee ve ila ivool ziige ite. \x * \xo 17:24 \xt 1Tes 4:16+\x*   
\m
\v 25 Eemon gabua tana irau ivot rekia soone. Pasaa, imin maata, Tamtamon Naatu aat ibaad pataŋani naol itaghon Maaron ŋgar tooni, ve tamtamon to aazne tizori. \x * \xo 17:25 \xt Mk 8:31; Lu 9:22\x*   
\p
\v 26 “Saawe tau muleeŋ to Tamtamon Naatu ighe ilam igharau, ene pale tamtamon titaghon ŋgar tau muuŋ tighamu ila saawe to Noa na. \x * \xo 17:26 \xt Gnp 6:5–7:1\x*   
\m
\v 27 Saawe tana, tamtamon lolozi iveghai tauzi kat. Tighilaal pataŋani tau ighe ivot na mako. Tighanghan, tighunghun, ve tivavavai zi ila ila le saawe duduuŋ tau Noa iloŋ ila waaŋ loolo. Ra Maaron igham yaa ivot toman tapiri tiina le itav taan, ve iravuur tamtamon tisov tilalez.   
\p
\v 28 “Ve tamtamon pale titaghon ŋgar tau tighamu ila saawe to Lot na. Saawe tana paam, tamtamon tighilaal pataŋani tau ighe ivot pazi na mako. Tighanghan, tighunghun, tiraraukol pa gabua toozi, tivavazogh aniiŋ, tiraurau ruum, ila ila le  
\v 29 saawe tau Lot ipul nugh Sodom ve ighau ila. Ra Maaron igham yav tomania maet salfa tuntunu tau vaazi saghati kat na, titaptap ila sambam saamba tizi, ve iravuur zi tisov tilalez. \x * \xo 17:29 \xt Gnp 19:24+; 2Pe 2:6; Jud 7\x*   
\m
\v 30 Saawe tau Tamtamon Naatu imuul ilam ve itotoi pooz tooni ivot ighazooŋ, ene pale ŋgar raraate mon ivot.   
\p
\v 31 “Saawe tana ighe ivot, ve ŋeer eta ilepleep ila nugh to lepoogh ta ruum paavo we, \f + \fr 17:31 \ft Yes Yuda, ruum toozi pavozi babaaŋa. Tauvene tirourou ta sewe imin iit tarourou ila patar.\f*  
\m ene irau izila muul ruum loolo to igham gabua tooni siriv mako. Izi le ighau malmali ila. Ve isaav ighe ŋeer eta ileep uum tooni ve ighamgham uraat, ene i paam. Irau imuul ila pa ruum tooni mako. Ighau malmali ila. \x * \xo 17:31 \xt Mt 24:17+; Mk 13:15+\x*   
\m
\v 32 Tauvene matamim ila pa gabua tsiam sov. Matamim iŋgal pataŋani tau muuŋ ivot pa Lot azaawa na. \x * \xo 17:32 \xt Gnp 19:26\x*   
\m
\v 33 Isaav ighe tamtamon eta iil eez pa tauu leso ileep poia izi taan, ene pale ilale. Ve isaav ighe tamtamon eta loolo eemon ve ipul tauu payau, ene pale igham lepoogh poia ila to Maaron. \x * \xo 17:33 \xt Mt 10:39; Lu 9:24; Yo 12:25\x*   
\p
\v 34 “Yau nasaav payam. Saawe tana ighe ivot, ve tamtamon ru tilup zi pa ghenooŋ ila niazi eemon, ene pale tigham ee, ve tipul ee ileep. \x * \xo 17:34 \xt Mt 24:40+\x*   
\m
\v 35-36 Ve isaav ighe zilivaa ru tilup zi pa uraat to gharatooŋ aniiŋ, ene pale ŋgar raraate mon ivot pazi. Pale tigham ee, ve tipul ee ileep.” \f + \fr 17:35-36 \ft Zeran ŋgara siriv tighe saveeŋ ziiri ite paam igheen ila ziiri tane loolo. Saveeŋ tauvene: “Ve isaav ighe zitamoot ru tileep uum ve tighamgham uraat, ene pale tigham ee, ve tipul ee ileep.” Ughita Matayu 24:40.\f*   
\p
\v 37 Mbiwa tooni tilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve tighasoni tighe: “Tiina, gabua tau yo usavia na, pale ivot izi sindei?”  
\p Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Nugh tau ighe uri igheen pani, ene irau iyooŋ mako. Pasaa, man kool pale tiroov tila, ve tilup zi ta sewe to tighani.” \f + \fr 17:37 \ft Saveeŋ tane, puughu tauvene: Muleeŋ to Yesu pale ivot ighazooŋ ila tamtamon matazi.\f* \x * \xo 17:37 \xt Mt 24:28\x*   
\c 18  
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to naar tau inoknok ghasoniiŋ pa uleeŋ  
\p
\v 1 Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane pa mbiwa tooni to ipalot zi. Leso tinizi imum pa suŋuuŋ sov, ve tisuŋ pa Maaron irau saawe. \x * \xo 18:1 \xt Ep 6:18; Kol 4:2; 1Tes 5:17\x*   
\m
\v 2 I isaav pazi ighe: “Nugh ee, daaba toozi to gharatooŋ saveeŋ iroi pa Maaron mako, ve igham ŋgar pa tamtamon eta mako.  
\v 3 Nugh tawe, naar ee ilepleep. Monmon i ilala to daaba tana, ve itaŋtaŋ raraini ighe: ‘Ŋgar tau koiag igham payau, ene iduduuŋ mako. Uul ghau ve ugharaat saveeŋ tsiau itaghon ŋgar duduuŋa.’   
\p
\v 4 “Saawe malau, daaba tana imbuzir pa uleeŋ naar tana. Eemon i inoknoki tauvene le murei ra, daaba tana isaav pa tauu ighe: ‘Yau tane naroi pa Maaron mako. Ve tamtamon paam, nagham ŋgar pazi mako.  
\v 5 Eemon naar tane igham pararaiŋ payau ila ila le tinig imum pani kat. Tambaaŋo. Yau aat nauule ve nagharaat saveeŋ tooni. Mako pale inoknok ghau tauvene.’” \x * \xo 18:5 \xt Lu 11:7+\x*   
\p
\v 6 Ra Tiina toit Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Alooŋ saveeŋ to daaba saghati tana wa?  
\v 7 Isaav ighe tamtamon tauvene ilooŋ naar tana aliiŋa ve igharaat pataŋani tooni, ene pale Maaron igham mindai pa yes tau i tauu isiigh zi timin le na? Isaav ighe koiazŋa tigham sosor pazi, ve yes titaŋ raraini pa mboŋ ve mataaz, pale izuar pa uleeŋ zi? Ene aat mako. \x * \xo 18:7 \xt Mbo 88:1; Syg 6:10\x*   
\m
\v 8 Yau nasaav payam: I pale iuul zi pa pataŋani toozi rekia mon, ve igharaat saveeŋ toozi itaghon ŋgar duduuŋa. Eemon saawe tau Tamtamon Naatu imuul ilam, pale ighita yes tau tileep izi taan na tighur ila tooni, ma mako?” \x * \xo 18:8 \xt 2Tim 3:1+\x*   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to ŋeer to tutuuŋ ve ŋeer to yauŋ takes  
\p
\v 9 Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane iŋarui zeran siriv tau tinumeer tauzi tighe yes mon tiduduuŋ ila Maaron maata, ve matazi veleghin zetazŋa siriv. \x * \xo 18:9 \xt Lu 16:15\x*   
\m
\v 10 “Pai ee, zeran ru tila Rumei Tiina tighe tisuŋ. Ee, ene ŋeer tutuuŋa. Ve ite, i ŋeer to yauŋ takes.  
\v 11 Ŋeer to tutuuŋ ila iyooz, ve isuŋ ila loolo ighe: ‘Aa Maaron, yau napakur ghom toman lolog poia. Pasaa, yau tane namin tamtamon siriv mako. Yau naum mako, naghur boog mako, ve ŋgar tau iduduuŋ ila yo matam na yau nasapir pani rigta mako. Ŋeer to yauŋ takes tane paam, yau namin i mako. \x * \xo 18:11 \xt Is 1:15; Syg 3:17\x*   
\m
\v 12 Wik ta naol ne, yau naŋgun taug pa ghaniiŋ aniiŋ pai ru itaghon suŋuuŋ ŋgara. Ve monmon navalagh gabua isov tau nagham zi na timin ŋgun saŋavul, ve naghur ŋgun eŋaeŋa ilat payo.’ \x * \xo 18:12 \xt Mt 23:23\x*   
\p
\v 13 “I isuŋsuŋ, ve ŋeer to yauŋ takes iyooz soghan. Maata izaa mako. Itud, ve iposai gargari toman taŋiiz. Pasaa, loolo ipataŋan pa sosor tooni. Tauvene isaav mon ighe: ‘Oo Maaron, yau tane, ŋeer to ghamuuŋ sosor. Lolom isaghatin ghau, ve ureu sosor tsiau ilale!’” \x * \xo 18:13 \xt Mbo 51:1; Is 57:15\x*   
\p
\v 14 Ra Yesu iseeŋ saveeŋ tooni ighe: “Yau nasaav payam. Saawe tau ŋeer to yauŋ takes tana ivot gha ila pa ruum tooni, Maaron ighita ighe i mon ta ŋeer duduuŋa. Ve iitete tawe, ene mako. Pasaa, tamtamon tisov tau tipait tauzi, ene pale Maaron itatan zi. Ve isaav ighe tamtamon eta itatan tauu eeza, ene pale Maaron ipaiti.” \x * \xo 18:14 \xt Lu 14:11; Yems 4:6; 1Pe 5:5+\x*   
\s1 Yesu ipalot yes geegeu  
\r (Mt 19:13-15; Mk 10:13-16)  
\p
\v 15 Tamtamon tigham natuzŋa geegeu paam tila to Yesu, leso ighur niima izala pavozi ve ipalot zi. Mbiwa tooni tighit zi, ve tiyaon zi.   
\p
\v 16 Eemon Yesu ipoi geegeu tawe timuul tilam, ve isaav pa mbiwa tooni ighe: “Ai, yam apoon eez pa geegeu sov! Apul zi tilam payau. Pa pooz to Maaron tomania nugh tooni, ene to yes tau ŋgar toozi imin geegeu tane.” \x * \xo 18:16 \xt 1Kor 14:20; 1Pe 2:2\x*   
\m
\v 17 Yau nasaav payam kat. Isaav ighe tamtamon eta itaghon pooz to Maaron ŋgara imin geegeu tane mako, i aat irau iloŋ ila nugh tooni ne mako. \f + \fr 18:17 \ft Geegeu tinumeer tamazŋa ve tinazŋa ve tileep ila sambazi. Iit paam irau tanumeer Maaron ve taleep ila i saamba. Leso tataghon pooz tooni, ve murei taloŋ tala nugh sambam.\f* \x * \xo 18:17 \xt Mt 18:3\x*   
\s1 Kuaz tauu ee isavsaav tomania Yesu  
\r (Mt 19:16-30; Mk 10:17-31)  
\p
\v 18 Daaba ee to yes Yuda ighason Yesu ighe: “Mos puughu, yo poiam. Pale nagham mindai, leso naleep matag yaryaare le alok?”   
\p
\v 19 Yesu iyol ghasoniiŋ tooni ighe: “Puughu mindai ta yo ughe yau poiag? Maaron mon ta poia. Ite paam mako.  
\v 20 Tutuuŋ ta naol ne, yo uwatagh zi wa: ‘Ughur boog sov, urav tamtamon imaat sov, uum sov, upariaaŋ saveeŋ karom sov, ve matam loŋloŋai pa tamam gha tinam ve utandagh pazi.’” \x * \xo 18:20 \xt Igham 20:12+\x*   
\p
\v 21 Ŋeer tawe ilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve isaav pa Yesu muul ighe: “Wai mos puughu, saawe tau kukuag ve ilam aazne, yau nataghoniir tutuuŋ tana tisov.”   
\p
\v 22 Yesu ilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve isaav pani muul ighe: “Poia. Ve ŋgar ee ta yo ughamu soone. Ula ugholia gabua tsio tisov, ve urei maeta pa yes mbolaaŋa, leso ugham lem kuaz tauu izi nugh sambam. Le isov, o ulam utaghon ghau.” \x * \xo 18:22 \xt Mt 6:19+; Lu 12:33; Mbaŋ 2:45\x*   
\p
\v 23 Ŋeer tana ilooŋ saveeŋ tane, le loolo ipataŋan kat. Pasaa, i kuaz tauu kat.   
\p
\v 24 Yesu ighita ŋeer tana loolo ipataŋan, ve isaav ighe: “Yes kuaz tauŋa, ipataŋan pazi kat to titaghon pooz to Maaron ve tiloŋ tila nugh tooni. \x * \xo 18:24 \xt Lu 8:14; 1Tim 6:9+\x*   
\m
\v 25 Aghita. Isaav ighe kamel itoova to izeev ghi iloŋ ila sarum puura, pale irao? Ene aat mako. Ve yes kuaz tauŋa tauvene paam. Isaav ighe tauzi titoova to titaghon pooz to Maaron ve tiloŋ tila nugh tooni, ene pale tirao mako kat.”   
\p
\v 26 Yes tilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve tighason Yesu tighe: “Wai, ighe tauvene, sei ta pale Maaron igham mulini ve ileep poi izi nugh tooni?”   
\p
\v 27 Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Gabua tau tamtamon irau tighamu mako, ene irau Maaron ighamu. Pasaa, gabua eta irau ikeek Maaron mako.”   
\s1 Yes tau titaghon Yesu na pale tigham saa atuya?  
\p
\v 28 Tauvene Petrus isaav pa Yesu ighe: “Ughita. Yei tane nipul nugh tsiei tomania gabua tsiei naol isov ileple, ve nilam nitaghon ghom.” \x * \xo 18:28 \xt Mt 4:19+; Lu 5:11\x*   
\p
\v 29 Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Onoon kat, yau nasaav payam. Isaav ighe tamtamon eta igham ŋgar pa pooz to Maaron, ve ipul ruum tooni, azaawa, toŋvetaz tooni, tiina taama, ma natŋa,  
\v 30 ene pale Maaron iyol gabua tau tamtamon tana ipul zi na pai katini. Pasaa, saawe tau i ileep izi taan, poia tiina to Maaron pale izazaa tooni le iliiv kat pa gabua tooni tisov tawe. Ve saawe to Mboŋ Murei ighe ivot, i pale ileep maata yaryaare le alok.”   
\s1 Yesu isaav muul pa mateegh ve burigiiŋ tooni  
\r (Mt 20:17-19; Mk 10:32-34)  
\p
\v 31 Ra Yesu ipet mbiwa tooni saŋavul ve ru tila soghan, ve isaav pazi ighe: “Alooŋ. Iit taghe tala pa Yerusalem tane. Ve saveeŋ isov tau yes propet tiboode izaa to Tamtamon Naatu na, ene pale anooŋa ivot. \x * \xo 18:31 \xt Mbo 22; Is 53:3-7\x*   
\m
\v 32 Pale tighuru ila yes tau Yuda mako na nimazi, ve tipamogheraini, tipamayaŋini, ve tiŋazuvu.  
\v 33 Mako tilosi pa waar tuatua, ve tiravu imaat. Eemon mboŋ imin tol, i pale iburig pa mateegh.”  
\v 34 Mbiwa tooni tilooŋ saveeŋ tana, eemon tighazooŋ pa puughu rigta mako. Pasaa, puughu iyooŋ pazi. Tauta tikankaan pa Yesu saveeŋ tooni.   
\s1 Yesu igharaat ŋeer maata kumkuuma ee igharau Yeriko  
\r (Mt 20:29-34; Mk 10:46-52)  
\p
\v 35 Yesu ilaagh ila le igharau nugh Yeriko, ve izaa to ŋeer maata kumkuuma ee. I mboole izi ila eez ziige, ve isuŋsuŋ tamtamon pa le gabua.  
\v 36 Ŋeer tawe ilooŋ eval tiina tilam le tighe tisal pani. Tauvene ighason zi ighe: “Ou, ene mindai?”   
\p
\v 37 Yes tiyol aliiŋa tighe: “Wai, Yesu to Nasaret ilam gha ila we.”   
\p
\v 38 Tauvene i iboob aliiŋa tiina ighe: “Yesu, David Naatu, lolom isaghatin ghau ve uul ghau lak!”   
\p
\v 39 Yes tau tilaagh timuuŋ na, tiyaon ŋeer tana tighe ineneeŋ. Eemon i itaŋ rarai Yesu muul toman aliiŋa tiina kat ighe: “Aa David Naatu, lolom isaghatin ghau ve uul ghau lak!”   
\p
\v 40 Tauvene Yesu aaghe tuŋia, ve isaav pa tamtamon siriv ighe: “Akis ŋeer tana niima ve aghamu ilam.” Ŋeer tana ilam igharauu, ve Yesu ighasoni ighe:  
\v 41 “Aiyo, ughe nagham mindai payo?”  
\p I iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Aa tiina tsiau, naghe yo ugharaat matag. Leso naghita nugh.”   
\p
\v 42 Tauvene Yesu isaav pani ighe: “Matam poia ve ughita nugh lak! Ghuruuŋ ila tsio, tauta iuul ghom gha matam poia wa.”  
\v 43 Rekia mon, ŋeer tana maata poia gha ighita nugh. Tauvene ipapait Maaron eeza pa tapiri ve poia tooni, ve itaghon Yesu gha yesŋa tila. Ve eval tiina tau tilepleep ve tighita kaut ŋgereeta tana na, tisov tipait Maaron eeza paam. \x * \xo 18:43 \xt Yo 9:1+\x*   
\c 19  
\s1 Sakaius ŋeer to yauŋ takes itoor ŋgar tooni  
\p
\v 1 Yesu iloŋ ila nugh Yeriko, ve ilaagh taghon nugh loolo gha ila.  
\v 2 Nugh tawe, ŋeer ee ilepleep, eeza Sakaius. I zeran to yauŋ takes daaba toozi ee, ve i kuaz tauu kat.  
\v 3 Sakaius izuari ghi ighe le ighita Yesu i saa ŋeer. Eemon irao mako. Pasaa, aaghe tuuku ve eval tiina tipoona.  
\v 4 Eemon ŋgar tooni iyaryaaŋ ighe ighita Yesu. Tauvene ilaan imuuŋ ila, ve ighita ai fik ee tau iyooz igharau eez tau Yesu itaghoni na, ve iip izala, ve isaŋan.   
\p
\v 5 Yesu ilaagh ila le ivot ai tawe puughu. Ra maata izala pa Sakaius, ve isaav pani ighe: “Sakaius, rekia mon ve uzilam! Pa aazne, yau aat naleep tomani ghom ila ruum tsio.”  
\v 6 Sakaius ilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve rekia mon izi, ve igham Yesu toman loolo poia kat, ve yesuru tila pa ruum tooni.   
\p
\v 7 Eemon eval tiina tighita yesuru tila le irau lolozi mako ve tiyau avozi tighe: “Wai, ŋeer tawe, i ŋeer to ghamuuŋ sosor. Yesu ila ileep ruum tooni pasaa?” \x * \xo 19:7 \xt Lu 5:30, 7:34, 15:2\x*   
\p
\v 8 Yesuru tila tivot ruum, ra Sakaius iyooz ila Yesu naagho, ve isaav pani ighe: “Tiina, ulooŋ! Aazne, yau aat navalagh gabua tsiau isov imin ŋgun ru, ve narei ŋgun ee pa yes mbolaaŋa. Ve isaav ighe muuŋ yau natombaan ŋeer eta ve naum gabua tooni, ene aat nayol gabua tawe, ve nagham le tol paam izala paavo.” \x * \xo 19:8 \xt Igham 22:1+; Lu 3:13\x*   
\p
\v 9 I isaav tauvene, ve Yesu isaav ighe: “Aazne, Maaron igham mulin yes to ruum tane wa. Pa ŋeer tane, i Abaram paaghu tooni paam.  
\v 10 Tamtamon Naatu, i ilam pa ilooŋ tamtamon tau tisapir pa Maaron eez tooni, leso igham mulin zi.” \x * \xo 19:10 \xt Ezek 34:11+; Lu 15:1+; 1Tim 1:15\x*   
\s1 Gabua tau Maaron ighuru ila nimaan na, taŋgin poghania ve tagham uratoini  
\r (Mt 25:14-30)  
\p
\v 11 Saawe tana, Yesu ila igharau Yerusalem wa. Tauvene yes tau tiloŋlooŋ saveeŋ tooni na, tighe pai ta Maaron itotoi pooz tooni ivot ighazooŋ. Tauta Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane pazi. \x * \xo 19:11 \xt Mbaŋ 1:6\x*   
\p
\v 12 “Pai ee, ŋeer ee ilepleep. Tomania ziiri waaro tooni ezazi tintiina. I ighe ila nugh malau, leso daaba to nugh tawe tighuru imin kinik pa tauu nugh tooni. Le isov, o imuul ila.  
\v 13 Tauvene ipoi besooŋa tooni saŋavul tilam, ve irei maet mina \f + \fr 19:13 \ft Mina, ene maet ee to yes Yuda. Mina, ene maet tiina. Isaav ighe tamtamon eta igham uraat irau kaiyo tol, ene pale tigham le mina ee imin le atuya.\f*  
\m eŋaeŋa le irau zi. Ra isaav pazi ighe: ‘Alooŋ. Yau naghe nala tane. Maet ta nareii irau gham wa. Tauvene saawe tau naleep soghan payam, yam araukol pani ve agham anooŋa tooni ivot.’ Isavsaav tomani zi le isov, ra iburig ve ila. \x * \xo 19:13 \xt Ro 12:6+; 1Kor 12:7+; Ep 4:7-13\x*   
\p
\v 14 “Eemon ŋeer tawe, tamtamon to nugh tooni tighur koi pani. Tauvene timbaaŋ tamtamon siriv titaghoni tila, leso tigham avozi ve tisavsaav tomania yes daaba to nugh tawe. Tila tivot ta sewe, ve tisaav pazi tighe: ‘Ŋeer tane, yei lolomai pani mako kat. Yam aghuru to iŋgin ghei sov.’ \x * \xo 19:14 \xt Yo 1:11\x*   
\p
\v 15 “Eemon daaba tawe tilooŋ zi mako, ve tighur ŋeer tana imin kinik. Ra i iburig gha imuul ila pa tauu nugh tooni. Ila peria, ve ipoi besooŋa tooni tilam. Leso tivotia uraat toozi ve iwatagh: Maet tau i ireii pazi na, tiraukol pani ve tigham geege piiz izala paavo.   
\p
\v 16 “Besooŋa tau ilam ivot imin maata na, ipaes pani ighe: ‘Tiina tsiau, maet mina ee tau yo upuli ila nimag, ene naraukol pani le ivot irau saŋavul.’   
\p
\v 17 “Tiina tooni ilooŋ saveeŋ tooni, ve ipaiti ighe: ‘Iya, yo uraata poia ee! Pasaa, yo utaghon ŋgar tsiau ve uŋgin poghania uraat ŋgiira tau naghuru ila nimam na. Tauvene yau aat naghur ghom to uŋgin nugh tintiina saŋavul.’ \x * \xo 19:17 \xt Mt 24:45-47; Lu 16:10; 1Kor 4:2\x*   
\p
\v 18 “Ra besooŋa ite imin ru, aana ilam ve ipaes pani ighe: ‘Tiina tsiau, maet tsio mina ee tau yo upuli ila nimag, ene nagham uratoini le ivot irau liim.’   
\p
\v 19 “Tiina tooni isaav pani ighe: ‘Yau aat naghur ghom to uŋgin nugh tintiina liim.’   
\p
\v 20 “Ra besooŋa tooni ite imin tol, aana ila ivot tooni, ve ipaes pani ighe: ‘Tiina, maet tsio mina ee, tauta enes. Yau nazunua pa uuli sirivu, ve naŋgooza ighengheen.  
\v 21 Pasaa, yau naroi payo. Yo ughamgham ariaaŋa pa tamtamon. Irau lolom isaghatin zi rigta mako. Ve ulepleep sorok ve tamtamon tighamgham uratoi ghom. Pasaa, gabua tau tamtamon siriv tighuru igheen na, yo ughamu imin lem. Ve taum uvazogh aniiŋ mako. Eemon saawe to lupuuŋ aniiŋ, yo uyauyau sorokini imin lem.’   
\p
\v 22 “Tiina tooni ilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve isaav ila maata ighe: ‘Yo tane, besooŋa saghati ee! Saveeŋ tau ivot ila taum avom, tauta aat imin puughu payo to naghur atuya iŋarui ghom. Yo ughe yau naghamgham ariaaŋa pa tamtamon, ve irau lolog isaghatin zi rigta mako. Ve ughe yau nalepleep sorok ve tamtamon tighamgham uratoi ghau. Pasaa, gabua tau tamtamon siriv tighuru igheen na, yau naghamu imin leg. Ve taug navazogh aniiŋ mako. Eemon saawe to lupuuŋ aniiŋ, yau nayauyau sorokini imin leg.  
\v 23 Ighe tauvene, puughu mindai ta ughur maet tsiau iloŋ ila ruum to maet mako? Imin ta yo ugham tauvene, kanaŋ saawe tau namuul nalam, nagham maet tsiau anooŋa tomania geege izala paavo.’   
\p
\v 24 “Ra tiina tooni isaav pa zeran siriv tau tiyooz tigharau na ighe: ‘Maet mina ee tau ŋeer tane ikisi ne, awalaava pani ve aghamu ila to iitete tau ikis maet mina saŋavul na.’   
\p
\v 25 “Yes tiyol aliiŋa tighe: ‘Wai tiina, i ikis maet saŋavul wa.’   
\p
\v 26 “Eemon kinik isaav pazi ighe: ‘Mako. Yau nasaav payam: Tamtamon tisov tau lezi gabua ve tigham uratoini, ene pale tigham lezi siriv muul izala paavo. Eemon isaav ighe tamtamon eta le gabua ŋgiira mon, ve igham uratoini mako, ene pale tigham mulin gabua tana, ve i ileep sorok. \x * \xo 19:26 \xt Mt 13:12; Mk 4:25; Lu 8:18\x*   
\m
\v 27 Aiyo, yes tau tighur koi payau ve lolozi pa tileep ila sambag mako na, agham zi tilam, ve arav zi tisov timatmaat ila naghog.’”   
\s1 Yesu izala pa Yerusalem  
\r (Mt 21:1-11; Mk 11:1-11; Yo 12:12-19)  
\p
\v 28 Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ tana le isov, ra ipaburigin laghooŋ tooni muul. I imuuŋ, ve mbiwa tooni titaghoni gha yesŋa tilaagh taghon eez tila tighe tizala pa Yerusalem.  
\v 29 Tila tivot nugh ru, Betpage ve Betania, tau tigheen ila loloz Oliv ziige, ra Yesu imbaaŋ mbiwa tooni ru ighe:  
\v 30 “Yamru amuuŋ azala nugh tawe. Ala avot, pale aghita doŋki paaghu ee tau timbitu iyozyooz. Ŋeer eta mboole izala paavo pai eta soone. Apoola, ve aghamu izilam sene.  
\v 31 Isaav ighe tamtamon eta ighason gham ighe: ‘Puughu mindai ta yamru apool doŋki tana?’ na asaav pani tauvene: ‘Tiina tsiei le uraat pani.’”   
\p
\v 32 Tauvene mbaŋooŋa tooni ru tawe tila ve tighita gabua isov ivot itaghon Yesu aliiŋa.  
\v 33 Saawe tau tighe tipool waar pa doŋki, tauŋa tighason zi tighe: “Yamru apoola pasaa?”   
\p
\v 34 Yesuru tiyol aliŋazi tighe: “Tiina tsiei, i le uraat pani.”   
\p
\v 35 Ra tigham doŋki tawe, ve timuul tila pa Yesu. Tila tivot tooni, ve tizuzuum nonoghiiŋa toozi to ŋgoaaŋ izi, titir zi izala doŋki paavo, ra tiuul Yesu ve izala mboole izi.  
\v 36 Tauvene i ileep izala doŋki paavo, ve itaghon eez ila. Yes tau tilaagh tomani zi na paam, tizavar nonoghiiŋa toozi to ŋgoaaŋ taghon eez to tipakuru.   
\p
\v 37 Tilaagh taghon eez tila le tivot loloz Oliv daaba, ra tindari muul tizila. Saawe tana, Yesu ziŋeera tau tilaghlaagh tomania na, tisov tiburig ve tipait Maaron eeza toman aliŋazi tiina. Pasaa, lolozi poia kat pa gabua ŋgeretazi tintiina naol tau tighit zi na. Tiboob tighe:   
\q1
\v 38 “Ŋeer tane, i kinik tau ilam pa Ŋeer Tiina eeza.  
\q2 Poia to Maaron aat izaa tooni ve ipaloti!  
\q2 Aazne, ŋgar luuma ivot ve koi isap itiŋa Maaron to sambam sosoon muul mako.  
\q2 Tapait Maaron tau ileep saaŋa le saaŋa kat na eeza pa tapiri ve poia tooni.” \x * \xo 19:38 \xt Mbo 118:26; Lu 2:14; Ro 5:1; Ep 2:14\x*   
\p
\v 39 Zeran tutuuŋa siriv tilaagh tomania eval tiina tana paam. Tilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve tisaav pa Yesu tighe: “Mos puughu, usaav pa mbiwa tsio tineneeŋ!”   
\p
\v 40 Eemon Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Yau nasaav payam: Isaav ighe zeran tane tineneeŋ, ene aat maet tiburig ve tipakur Maaron toman aliŋazi tiina.” \x * \xo 19:40 \xt Hab 2:11\x*   
\s1 Yesu itaŋ pa Yerusalem  
\p
\v 41-42 Yesu ilaagh ila le igharau Yerusalem, ra maata izala pa nugh, ve itaŋ pani. Ve isaav ighe: “O nugh Yerusalem, naghe aazne yo ughilaal eez to yamŋa Maaron avalupu gham amin eemon ve luuma tooni izaa tsio, o poi. Eemon eez tane ighazooŋ payo soone. \x * \xo 19:41-42 \xt Ro 11:8\x*   
\m
\v 43 Tauvene saawe eta pale ivot, mako koiamŋa tilam tilivutin ghom, ve tindou taan ila didiiŋ ariaaŋa tau ilivutin nugh tsio ziige imin ndeet pazi. Leso titaghoni, ve tiloŋ tilat nugh tsio loolo. Ve lem eez eta to ughau pazi mako.  
\v 44 Tauvene yes pale tirav ghom tomania natumŋa, ve tireu mbirisai nugh tsio. Irau tipul maet eta igheen izala maet ite paavo mako. Pasaa, saawe tau Maaron ilam pa uleeŋ ghom, yo ughilaalo mako.” \x * \xo 19:44 \xt Mika 3:12; Lu 21:6\x*   
\s1 Yesu iziir tamtamon tighau pa Rumei Tiina  
\r (Mt 21:12-17; Mk 11:15-19; Yo 2:13-22)  
\p
\v 45 Yesu iloŋ ila sirsiir to Rumei Tiina loolo, ve ireu yes tau tiraraukol ta sewe, ve iziir zi tighau tivot tila muuri.  
\v 46 Ve isaav pazi ighe: “Maaron aliiŋa tau tiboode na isaav ighe:  
\q2 ‘Rumei tsiau, ene suŋuuŋ niia.’ \x * \xo 19:46 \xt Is 56:7\x*  
\m Eemon yam aghamu imin nugh tau yes umbuuŋa tiyoŋyooŋ ila!” \f + \fr 19:46 \ft Yes Israela tigholgholia gabua maata maata tau popoiazi pa watooŋrau na ila Rumei Tiina naagho. Yesu iyaon zi pasaa, yes tighur gabua atuyazi izala kat. Ve gabua ite. I ighita ighe Rumei to Maaron, ene nugh to gholiiŋ gabua mako.\f* \x * \xo 19:46 \xt Yer 7:11\x*   
\p
\v 47 Saawe tana ve ila, Yesu imariau mako. Mataaz ta naol ne, i ilepleep izi Rumei Tiina naagho, ve ipapaduduuŋ tamtamon pa Maaron aliiŋa. Tauvene yes daaba to watooŋrau tomania yes ŋgara to tutuuŋ ve yes pooza tiil eez pa ravuuŋni imaat.  
\v 48 Eemon lezi eez mako. Pasaa, monmon eval tiina tilivutini tighe le tiloŋlooŋ saveeŋ tooni.   
\c 20  
\s1 Yes daaba tighason Yesu pa sei ta ighuru pa uraat tooni  
\r (Mt 21:23-27; Mk 11:27-33)  
\p
\v 1 Saawe ee, Yesu ipaghazoŋai tamtamon pa Maaron aliiŋa ila Rumei Tiina naagho, ve ivotia vaaru poia pazi. Tauvene yes daaba to watooŋrau, tomania ŋgara siriv to tutuuŋ ve pooza siriv tilup zi ve tila tivot tooni,  
\v 2 ve tighasoni tighe: “Laak, usaav ghazooŋa payei. Uraat tau yo ughamghamu na, ezam pani mindai? Ve sei kat ta ighur ghom pa uraat tane?” \x * \xo 20:2 \xt Yo 2:18; Mbaŋ 4:7\x*   
\p
\v 3 Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Ghasoniiŋ tsiam poia. Eemon yau leg ghasoniiŋ ee payam paam.  
\v 4 Aiyo, asaav payau. Yoan tau muuŋ irurughuuz tamtamon na, uraat tooni puughu mindai? I itaghon ŋgar to nugh sambam, ma itaghon ŋgar to tamtamon?”   
\p
\v 5 Yes tiyol aliiŋa rekia mako. Tivasavo zi tighe: “Wai, ene pale tasaav mindai? Ighe tasaav taghe: ‘Yoan itaghon ŋgar to nugh sambam,’ i pale isaav pait: ‘Ighe tauvene, puughu mindai ta yam aghur ila saveeŋ tooni mako?’  
\v 6 Ve ighe tasaav taghe: ‘Yoan itaghon ŋgar to tamtamon’, ene pale eval tiina tane tisov tiburig ve tirav ghiit pa maet. Pasaa, yes tighur ila ariaaŋ tighe: Yoan, i propet to Maaron.” \x * \xo 20:6 \xt Mt 14:5; Lu 7:26\x*   
\p
\v 7 Tauvene yes tiyol ghasoniiŋ to Yesu tighe tikankaan pa Yoan uraat tooni puughu.  
\v 8 Tauta Yesu aana isaav pazi: “Ighe tauvene, yau paam, aat irau nayol ghasoniiŋ tsiam, ve navotia puughu tau yau ezag pa uraat tsiau tane ne mako.”   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to uraata sasaghatizi tau tiŋgin uum vaen  
\r (Mt 21:33-46; Mk 12:1-12)  
\p
\v 9 Ra Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane pa eval tiina ighe:  
\p “Pai ee, ŋeer ee igharaat taan tooni, ve ivazogh vaen ila. \f + \fr 20:9 \ft Paesiiŋ to saveeŋ ziiri tane igheen ila Mt 21:33.\f*  
\m Ra ipul uum vaen tooni ila uraata siriv nimazi. Leso tigham uratoini, ve saawe to yauŋ vaen anooŋa, mako tivalaghi gha sirivu imin i le, ve sirivu imin yes lezi. I igharaat saveeŋ tomani zi le isov, ra iburig, ipul nugh tooni, ve ila ileep malau izi nugh ite. \x * \xo 20:9 \xt Mbo 80:8+; Is 5:1+\x*   
\m
\v 10 Ilepleep izi ta sewe le saawe to yauŋ vaen anooŋa ivot, ra imbaaŋ besooŋa tooni ee ila to yes uraata tawe. Leso igig zi, ve igham vaen anooŋa siriv tau tighuru pa uum tauŋa na. Eemon saawe tau besooŋa tana ila peria toozi, yes tiburig gha tiravu, ve tiziire niima ŋginaaŋa, gha imuul ila.  
\v 11 Tauvene uum tauŋa imbaaŋ besooŋa tooni ite ila. Eemon i paam, tiravu, tipamayaŋini, ve tiziire niima ŋginaaŋa, gha imuul ila.  
\v 12 Ra uum tauŋa imbaaŋ besooŋa tooni ite imin tol aana ila. I paam, tirav matini le ighun siŋ, ve tiziire imuul ila.   
\p
\v 13 “Murei ra, uum vaen tauŋa isaav ighe: ‘Wai, ene pale nagham mindai? Yau aat nambaaŋ taug natug tau lolog igheen tooni kat ne ila. Isaav ighe i ila, ene aat tiroron pani, ve tilooŋ aliiŋa.’   
\p
\v 14 “Tauvene imbaaŋ tauu naatu ila. Eemon saawe tau uraata tana tighita naatu ilaghlaagh soghan gha ilam, tivasavo zi tighe: ‘Ou, aghita! Ewe tiina toit naatu tauta ilam we. Murei, i pale ighamuur gabua naol isov to taama. Tala taravu imaat! Leso gabua tau i eeza pani na, taghamu imin leen.’  
\v 15 Tauvene tila gha tikisi, tigherevu ivot ila soghan pa uum vaen, ve tiravu imaat.” \x * \xo 20:15 \xt Hib 13:12\x*  
\p Yesu isavia saveeŋ tane le isov, ra ighason zi ighe: “Yam agham ŋgar mindai? Pale uum vaen tauŋa igham mindai pa yes uraata tawe?  
\v 16 I aat ilam ve irav zi tisov timataar, ve ighur uum vaen tooni ila zeran siriv nimazi, leso tiŋgini.”  
\p Eval tiina tilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve tisaav tighe: “Wai, usaav vene sov!” \x * \xo 20:16 \xt Mbaŋ 13:46, 28:28\x*   
\p
\v 17 Yesu maata ila pazi, ve isaav ighe: “Ene pale mindai pa Maaron aliiŋa ziiri ee tau tiboode na? Isaav ighe:  
\q2 ‘Maet tau yes to raoŋ ruum matazi veleghini ve tisiki ilale na, tauta imin puughu pa ruum iyooz ve ipaloti. Leso ruum iyooz ariaaŋ izala paavo.’ \x * \xo 20:17 \xt Mbo 118:22\x*   
\m
\v 18 Tamtamon tisov tau ighe titap ve tirav tauzi izala maet tawe, ene pale tuazi ipolpol. Ve isaav ighe maet tana itap izala tamtamon eta paavo, ene pale imbiriis le ŋanŋania.” \x * \xo 20:18 \xt Is 8:14+; Dan 2:34+\x*   
\p
\v 19 Ŋgara siriv to tutuuŋ, tomania yes daaba to watooŋrau tighilaal tighe Yesu isavia saveeŋ tane iŋarui zi. Tauvene tighe tikisi pataghaaŋ. Eemon tiroi pa eval tiina, tauta tipuli ileep.   
\s1 Ghasoniiŋ to sikiiŋ takes ila pa kinik tiina to Rom  
\r (Mt 22:15-22; Mk 12:13-17)  
\p
\v 20 Yes daaba to watooŋrau tomania zeran tutuuŋa tana matazi itataghon Yesu. Tauvene timbaaŋ zeran siriv, leso tipadeu pani. Zeran tawe tigham tauzi imin yes zeran to taghoniiŋ ŋgar duduuŋa. Yes tila leso titombaan Yesu pa savsaveeŋ. Ighe isik aliiŋa eta isosor, mako imin puughu pani to tikisi, ve tighuru ila gavana to Rom niima.  
\v 21 Tauvene tila tivot to Yesu, ve tigham saveeŋ ŋgoreeŋ pani tighe: “Mos puughu, yei niwatagh: Saveeŋ tsio tomania ŋgar isov tau yo upaduduuŋ tamtamon pani, ene iduduuŋ mon. Ve isaav ighe tamtamon ezazi tintiina, ma lezi ezazi mako, na yo ugham ŋgar pa gabua tauvene mako. Usasavia ŋgar raraate mon pa tamtamon tisov, ve usavsaav ghazooŋ ila matazi. Ve isaav ighe upaghazoŋai tamtamon pa eez to Maaron, na saveeŋ tsio isov, ene onoon mon.  
\v 22 Tauvene usaav ghazooŋ payei. Isaav ighe iit Yuda tasik takes ila pa kinik tiina to Rom, pale iduduuŋ pa tutuuŋ toit, ma mako?”   
\p
\v 23 Eemon Yesu iwatagh karom toozi wa. Tauvene isaav pazi ighe:  
\v 24 “Maet tau tasiksiki pa takes na, atotoi eta ve naghita. Laak, sei anunu ve eeza tane?”  
\p Yes tiyol ghasoniiŋ tooni tighe: “Ena kinik tiina to Rom.”   
\p
\v 25 Yesu isaav pazi muul ighe: “Tauta ena. Ighe gabua to kinik tiina to Rom, na aghamu imuul ila pa i tauu. Ve gabua to Maaron, o apamuule ila pa Maaron.” \f + \fr 20:25 \ft Paesiiŋ to saveeŋ ziiri tane igheen ila Mt 22:21.\f* \x * \xo 20:25 \xt Gnp 1:27; Ro 13:7; 1Pe 2:17\x*   
\m
\v 26 Tauvene yes titoova to tiwati gha leso isik aliiŋa eta isosor ila eval tiina matazi. Eemon tirao mako. Tilooŋ saveeŋ tooni tane, le tirur pani ve tineneeŋ mon.   
\s1 Ghasoniiŋ pa burigiiŋ to yes mateegha  
\r (Mt 22:23-33; Mk 12:18-27)  
\p
\v 27 Yes Sadusi tisavsaav tighe mateegha irau tiburig mako. Tauvene Sadusi siriv tila to Yesu, ve tighasoni tighe: \x * \xo 20:27 \xt Mbaŋ 23:8\x*   
\p
\v 28 “Mos puughu, muuŋ Mose ibood tutuuŋ pait tauvene: Ighe ŋeer eta ivai, ve yesuru azaawa lezi natuzi eta mako, ve tamoot imaat, ene aat taazi ivai naar tooni. Leso livaa ipoop, ve natuzi tana iyol taama olman tau imaat na, ve iyooz pa gabua tooni. \x * \xo 20:28 \xt Lo 25:5\x*   
\p
\v 29 “Laak, saawe ee, toŋvetaz liim ve ru tilepleep. Ŋeer aidaaba ivai, eemon le naatu mako, ve imaat.  
\v 30 Tauvene taazi tau itaghoni na, igham naar tooni ve ivaii. Eemon taazi tawe paam, le naatu mako ve imaat.  
\v 31 Ra tazizi ite tau imin tol na, aana igham naar tawe ve ivaii. Tighamgham tauvene le yes liim ve ru tivai livaa eemon tana, ve tisov timaat. Ve lezi natuzŋa mako.  
\v 32 Murei ra, naar tana paam, aana imaat.  
\v 33 Laak, saawe to Mboŋ Murei, ve Maaron ighe ipaburigin yes mateegha, ene pale livaa tawe imin sei kat azaawa? Pa yes liim ve ru ta tisov tivaii.”   
\p
\v 34 Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Tamtamon to saawe tane tivaivai.  
\v 35-36 Eemon saawe paaghu tau pale ivot murei, yes tau Maaron ighit zi ighe yes popoiazi irau to tiburig pa mateegh ve tileep tomania, ene yes irau tivai muul mako. Pasaa, irau timaat muul mako. Lepoghazi pale imin yes aŋela. Zeran tauvene, burigiiŋ toozi itotoi zi ighe yes Maaron natŋa. \x * \xo 20:35-36 \xt 1Kor 15:42+\x*   
\m
\v 37 Ve burigiiŋ to yes mateegha, ene Mose paam ivotia saveeŋa alok wa. Pasaa, saawe tau Maaron ivot tooni imin yav tau ighanghan ila ai marani, i iwaat Ŋeer Tiina ighe i Maaron to Abaram, Maaron to Isak, ve Maaron to Yakop. \f + \fr 20:37 \ft Paesiiŋ to saveeŋ ziiri tane igheen ila Mt 22:32.\f* \x * \xo 20:37 \xt Igham 3:6\x*   
\m
\v 38 Maaron, i Maaron to yes mateegha mako. I Maaron to yes tau tileep matazi yaryaare. Ve i tauu ta imin puughu pa lepoogh to tamtamon tisov.” \x * \xo 20:38 \xt Gnp 2:7; Yo 1:3-4; Ro 14:8+; 1Kor 8:6\x*   
\p
\v 39 Zeran ŋgara siriv to tutuuŋ tilooŋ saveeŋ tooni tane, ve tisaav pani tighe: “Mos puughu, saveeŋ tsio tana iduduuŋ mon.”   
\p
\v 40 Tauvene saawe tana ve ila, tamtamon tighason Yesu pa gabua eta muul mako. Pasaa, tiroi pa saveeŋ tooni.   
\s1 Isaav ighe Mesia ivot ila to kinik David, pale eeza irau iliiv David mindai?  
\r (Mt 22:41-46; Mk 12:35-37)  
\p
\v 41 Ra Yesu aana ighason zi ighe: “Puughu mindai ta tighe Mesia pale ivot ila to kinik David siŋ tooni?  
\v 42 Pa muuŋ, David tauu ibood saveeŋ ila rau to Mbouŋ To Suŋuuŋ ighe:  
\q2 ‘Maaron isaav pa Tiina tsiau ighe: “Ulam mbolem izi ila pa nimag tapir,   
\q2
\v 43 le irau natatan koiamŋa, ve tapirizi isov kat, ve uvaghaaz zi ila aghem saamba.” ’ \x * \xo 20:43 \xt Mbo 110:1; Mbaŋ 2:34+; Hib 1:13\x*   
\m
\v 44 Aghita. David tauu iwaat Mesia ighe ‘tiina tooni.’ Eemon Mesia, i siŋ to David. Gabua tane, ŋgara mindai?” \f + \fr 20:44 \ft Paesiiŋ to saveeŋ ziiri tane igheen ila Mt 22:45. \f*   
\s1 Yesu iveveen tamtamon pa ŋgar pakuruuŋ to yes ŋgara to tutuuŋ  
\r (Mt 23:1-36; Mk 12:38-40; Yo 11:37-54)  
\p
\v 45 Eval tiina tilepleep, ve tilooŋ Yesu isaav pa mbiwa tooni ighe:  
\v 46 “Matamim imomoos pa yes zeran ŋgara to tutuuŋ. Yes tighe tinonogh zi pa nonoghiiŋa toozi mamalaua, ve tilaghlaagh taghon maaran aate. Leso tamtamon tighit zi ve tisavia saveeŋ popoia pazi imin pakuruuŋ zi. Ve isaav ighe tiloŋ tila rumei, ma tila pa ghanghaniiŋ, ene tighe le tileep ila paŋ popoiazi tau tighur zi pa yes tau ezazi tintiina na.  
\v 47 Yes titotombaan yes zinaara ve tigham ruum toozi tomania saveeŋ mariŋ toozi imin lezi. Ve tiyotyoot suŋuuŋ toozi le malaua kat. Leso tamtamon tighit zi tighe yes zeran patabuyaaŋa. Tauvene atuya tau pale izaa toozi, ene tiina le tiina kat.”   
\c 21  
\s1 Paitooŋ to naar ee  
\r (Mk 12:41-44)  
\p
\v 1 Yesu ileep izi Rumei Tiina naagho igharau nugh tau tamtamon tighurghur paitooŋ toozi ila na, ve ighita kuaz tauŋa siriv tila ve tighur paitooŋ toozi.  
\v 2 Ra ighita naar mbolaaŋa ee paam, aana ighur maet siŋsiŋai geegeu ru ila.  
\v 3 Yesu ighita gabua tana, ve isaav ighe: “Yau nasaav payam kat. Naar tawe, i livaa mbolaaŋa. Eemon maet tau i ighuru we, ene iliiv maet tau tamtamon tisov tighuru na.  
\v 4 Pasaa, yes tisov lezi maet tiina ighengheen, ve tighur ŋgiira mon. Ve naar tawe, mbolaaŋ ighamu. Eemon maet tooni rig to iŋgini pa lepoogh tooni, tauta ighuru isov ila.” \x * \xo 21:4 \xt 2Kor 8:1, 12\x*   
\s1 Yesu isaav pa rewaaŋ Rumei Tiina to Maaron  
\r (Mt 24:1-2; Mk 13:1-2)  
\p
\v 5 Tamtamon siriv tiyoor Rumei Tiina tighe: “Aighat, rumei poia ee ne! Tipaboode pa maet paghunazi maata maata tomania gabua popoia tau tamtamon tighur zi tila pa Maaron na, le paghuuna kat.”   
\p
\v 6 Eemon Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Alooŋ. Gabua naol isov tau aazne yam aghit zi ne, saawe eta pale ivot, o tireu mbirisai zi tisov tizi. Irau tipul maet eta igheen izala maet ite paavo muul mako.” \x * \xo 21:6 \xt Lu 19:44\x*   
\s1 Pataŋani naol pale tivot imin maata, mako tireu Rumei Tiina izi  
\r (Mt 24:3-14; Mk 13:3-13)  
\p
\v 7 Tauvene tighason Yesu tighe: “Mos puughu, saveeŋ tau yo usavia pa rewaaŋ Rumei Tiina na, ŋeez o gabua tane ivot? Ve saa gabua pale imin ilaal pani?”   
\p
\v 8 Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Matamim imomoos poi pa taumim! Mako pale tamtamon tigherev gham ve apul eez tsiau. Pasaa, murei, tamtamon naol pale tilam ve tiwatwaat sorokin ezag tighe: ‘Ŋeer tau yam asasaŋani, ene yau taug tane.’ Ve yes pale tisaav payam tighe: ‘Taan saawe, ene ilam igharau wa.’ Eemon yam ataghon zi sov. \x * \xo 21:8 \xt 2Tes 2:1+; 1Yo 4:1\x*   
\m
\v 9 Ve isaav ighe yam alooŋ malmal tintiina varuzi, ma alooŋ tighe tamtamon tipaburigin malmal pa tauzi ila nugh loolo, na aroi ve asaŋeeŋ sov. Pa gabua tauvene aat ivot imin maata itaghon Maaron ŋgar tooni. Eemon taan saawe, ene soone.”   
\p
\v 10 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Nugh tintiina pale tigham malmal tomania nugh tintiina siriv, ve kinik siriv pale tigham malmal tomania kinik to nugh siriv. \x * \xo 21:10 \xt Syg 6:3+\x*   
\m
\v 11 Yogyoog tintiina pale titok taan, ve pitool tomania moroghooŋ sasaghati tivot izi nugh siriv ve tivaghamunia tamtamon. Ve ilaal tintiina pale tivot izala sambam saamba ve gabua maata maata ivotvot. Tauvene roiŋ tiina kat pale igham tamtamon. \x * \xo 21:11 \xt Yoel 2:31; Syg 6:12+\x*   
\s1 Tamtamon pale tighur pataŋani pa yes tau titaghon Yesu  
\p
\v 12 “Eemon gabua isov tawe pale tivot soone, ve yes tau tighur koi payau na tikis gham ve tighur pataŋani naol payam. Yes Yuda pale tipayooz gham iloŋ ila rumei toozi, ve tizeev gham aloŋ ala ruum to yavyavuuŋ. \x * \xo 21:12 \xt Mbaŋ 4:1, 5:17, 22:30+\x*  
\m Ve tamtamon pale tipayooz gham ila yes daaba to taan ve kinik naghozi paam. Pasaa, yam ataghon ghau ve avovotia yau ezag. \x * \xo 21:12 \xt Mbaŋ 16:19, 25:23+\x*   
\m
\v 13 Gabua tau ivot payam pa saawe tana, ene pale imin eez payam to avotia varug pazi ve apariaaŋ saveeŋ tsiau. \x * \xo 21:13 \xt Mbaŋ 22:1, 24:10, 26:1+\x*   
\m
\v 14 Tauvene agharaat ŋgar tsiam pataghaaŋ: Isaav ighe tikis gham, na lolomim bubu ve agham ŋgar naol pa ravuuŋ aliŋazi sov. \x * \xo 21:14 \xt Mt 10:19+; Lu 12:11+\x*   
\m
\v 15 Pa yau taug pale nagham lemim ŋgar poia ve napaghazoŋai gham pa saveeŋ to asavia. Tauvene saveeŋ tau ivot ila avomim, ene koiamimŋa pale irau tizoora, ma titatani ne mako. \x * \xo 21:15 \xt Mk 13:11; Mbaŋ 6:10\x*   
\m
\v 16 Saawe tana, tamamimŋa tomania tinamimŋa, toŋvetaz tsiam, ziiri waaro tsiam, ve zeetmimŋa, yes paam pale tighur gham ila koiamimŋa nimazi, ve tirav tamtamon tsiam siriv timatmaat. \x * \xo 21:16 \xt Mbaŋ 7:59, 12:2\x*   
\m
\v 17 Tamtamon tisov pale tighur koi payam. Pasaa, yam avotia yau ezag, ve ataghon ghau. \x * \xo 21:17 \xt Mt 10:22; Yo 15:18+\x*   
\m
\v 18 Eemon aroi sov. Pa Maaron tauu pale maata payam ve iŋgin gham aleep poi. Tauvene dabamim raua eta irau ilale mako. \x * \xo 21:18 \xt Mt 10:30; Lu 12:7\x*   
\m
\v 19 Tauvene ayooz ariaaŋ, ve akis ghuruuŋ ila tsiam tuŋia, leso Maaron igham mulin gham, ve aleep matamim yaryaare le alok.” \x * \xo 21:19 \xt Hib 10:36; Syg 2:7\x*   
\s1 Pataŋani tiina kat pale ivot pa Yerusalem  
\r (Mt 24:15-21; Mk 13:14-19)  
\p
\v 20 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Murei, yam pale aghita zaaba katini tilam tiyooz livutin Yerusalem. Gabua tana ighe ivot, na yam awatagh: Saawe to tireu Yerusalem ve tamtamon tipuli ileple, ene ilam igharau wa.  
\v 21 Isaav ighe gabua tana ivot, tamtamon tau tileep izi taan sirivu to Yudea na, yes aat rekia mon ve tighawaar tizala pa loloz. Ve yes tau tileep Yerusalem loolo na, aat tipuli ve tighau tila. Ve yes tau tileep Yerusalem ziige paam, irau tiloŋ tila Yerusalem muul mako. Tighau mon gha tila.  
\v 22 Pasaa saawe tana, Maaron pale iyat sosor to yes Yuda itaghon aliiŋa isov tau tiboode na. \x * \xo 21:22 \xt Yer 5:29; Dan 9:26+; Hos 9:7\x*   
\m
\v 23 Saawe tana ighe ivot, zilivaa tau apozi, ve yes payamyamŋa, ene tikaria tauzi wa. Pasaa, ipataŋan pazi pa ghaoŋ. Saawe tana, aatyavyav to Maaron pale izaa to taan tane tamtamona, ve pataŋani tiina kat igham zi. \x * \xo 21:23 \xt 1Kor 7:26\x*   
\m
\v 24 Tamtamon siriv, pale timbut zi pa mbuzaagh gha timaat. Ve siriv, ene pale koiazŋa tiyau zi tila tileep irau nugh nugh. Ve nugh nugh tau Yuda mako na, pale tigham Yerusalem imin lezi, ve tileep pani ve tiŋgini le irau saawe tau Maaron ighuru pazi na isov, mako tipuli. \x * \xo 21:24 \xt Mbo 79:1; Lu 20:16; Syg 11:2\x*   
\s1 Muleeŋ to Tamtamon Naatu  
\r (Mt 24:29-31; Mk 13:24-27)  
\p
\v 25 “Murei pale gabua siriv tivot pa aaz, kaiyo, ve pitum timin ilaal pa tamtamon, ve pataŋani tintiina pale tivot izi taan. Te pale isaghat, ve ipei dibom toman luutu tiina kat. Tauvene tamtamon ŋgar toozi pale ivaghamgham ve tisaŋeeŋ. \x * \xo 21:25 \xt 2Pe 3:10+; Syg 6:12+\x*   
\m
\v 26 Ve Maaron pale ivatoki gabua siriv to sambam saamba tau tapirizi tiina na le tirur. Tauvene tamtamon pale lolozi bubu, ve roiŋ tiina igham zi le tapirizi isov. Pasaa, tighilaal tighe malau mako pale pataŋani tiina kat ivot izi taan.  
\v 27 Mako tamtamon matazi izala le tighita Tamtamon Naatu ileep ila taitai loolo, ve izilam toman tapiri ve mbonari tiina kat. \x * \xo 21:27 \xt Dan 7:13; Mt 26:64; 1Tes 4:16+\x*   
\m
\v 28 Isaav ighe yam aghita gabua siriv tana tivotvot, na ayooz tuŋia toman lolomim poia, ve aghur matamim. Pa saawe to Maaron igham mulin gham pa pataŋani tsiam, ene ilam igharau wa.”   
\s1 Saveeŋ palelaaŋ to ai fik  
\r (Mt 24:32-35; Mk 13:28-31)  
\p
\v 29 Ra Yesu isavia saveeŋ palelaaŋ tane pazi ighe: “Matamim ila pa ai fik ve ai siriv paam, ve agham ŋgar pazi.  
\v 30 Isaav ighe aghita mbilazi paghpaaghu tivot, na aghilaal aghe saawe to aaz ighe ilam tane.  
\v 31 Gabua tau nasavi zi ne, ene ŋgara raraate mon. Isaav ighe aghita gabua naol tana tivotvot, mako awatagh aghe: Saawe to Maaron itotoi pooz tooni toman tapiri ivot ighazooŋ, ene ilam igharau wa.   
\p
\v 32 “Onoon kat, yau nasaav payam: Yes to saawe tane pale timaat soone, ve tighita gabua tana tisov tivotiir.  
\v 33 Sambam saamba ve taan pale tilalez. Eemon saveeŋ tsiau ziiri eta irau ilale ne mako.” \x * \xo 21:33 \xt Mbo 119:89; Is 40:8; Mt 5:18; 1Pe 1:25\x*   
\s1 Tamamaat ariaaŋ  
\p
\v 34 Yesu isaav muul ighe: “Matamim imomoos poi pa taumim ve amamaat ariaaŋ. Mako pale apul taumim pa ŋgar soroksorok, imin ghanghaniiŋ ve ghunghunuuŋ, ve agham ŋgar naol pa lepoghamim to taan. Mako itatan ghuruuŋ ila tsiam, ve saawe to Tamtamon Naatu imuul ilam, ene pale ipaperekin gham imin liis ikis gham. \x * \xo 21:34 \xt Ro 13:11+; 1Tes 5:2+; 2Pe 3:10-14; Syg 16:15\x*   
\m
\v 35 Pasaa, saawe tana pale ivot pa tamtamon tisov tau tileep izi taan. Eta irau ighau pani ne mako.  
\v 36 Tauvene amamaat ariaaŋ irau saawe, ve asuŋ Maaron to ipalot gham. Leso ayooz ariaaŋ pa badooŋ pataŋani naol tana, ve saawe tau ayooz ila Tamtamon Naatu naagho, na aroi mako, ve ayooz toman tintinmim.” \x * \xo 21:36 \xt 1Yo 2:28\x*   
\p
\v 37 Mataaz ta naol ne, Yesu ipaghazoŋai tamtamon pa Maaron aliiŋa ila Rumei Tiina naagho. Ve ravrav, imuul izala pa loloz Oliv, ve ileep ta sewe pa mboŋ.  
\v 38 Tauvene mboŋoozo ta naol ne, ndoromroome ve tamtamon tisov tilala Rumei Tiina, leso tilooŋ Yesu saveeŋ tooni.   
\c 22  
\s1 Yes daaba to Yuda tiil eez to tirav Yesu imaat  
\r (Mt 26:1-5; Mk 14:1-2; Yo 11:45-53)  
\p
\v 1 Saawe to lupuuŋ tiina to yes Yuda tau tilup zi pa suŋuuŋ ve tighan mberet tau le yis mako na, ene ilam igharau wa. Saawe tana, tiwaato tighe ‘Pasova.’ \f + \fr 22:1 \ft Pasova, ene lupuuŋ tiina to yes Yuda tau matazi iŋgal imuul ila pa saawe tau timbuzŋa tileep saghat izi Isip, ve Maaron igham mulin zi ila yes Isipa nimazi.\f* \x * \xo 22:1 \xt Igham 12:15+\x*   
\m
\v 2 Yes daaba to watooŋrau tomania yes ŋgara to tutuuŋ tiroi pa eval tiina tau titaghon Yesu na. Tighe pale tipaburigin malmal ma vene. Tauvene tiil eez to tikis Yesu ve tiravu imaat. \x * \xo 22:2 \xt Mbo 2:2; Mbaŋ 4:27\x*   
\s1 Yudas isaav ighe i pale ighur Yesu ila koiŋa nimazi  
\r (Mt 26:14-16; Mk 14:10-11)  
\p
\v 3 Saawe tana, Sadan izeev Yudas Iskariot. Mbiwa to Yesu saŋavul ve ru, i toozi ee. \x * \xo 22:3 \xt Yo 13:2, 27\x*   
\m
\v 4 Tauvene i ila to yes daaba to watooŋrau ve ŋginiiŋa to Rumei Tiina, ve yesŋa tivasavo zi pa eez sindei tau i pale ighur Yesu ila nimazi.  
\v 5 Yes tilooŋ saveeŋ tooni le lolozi poia kat, ve yesŋa timbu saveeŋ tighe pale tigham le maet siriv.  
\v 6 Yudas iyok pa saveeŋ toozi, ve ila isasaŋan. Ighe saawe poia eta ivot, ve eval tiina tileep tomania Yesu mako, o ighuru ila nimazi.   
\s1 Mbiwa to Yesu tila tigharaat aniiŋ to Pasova  
\r (Mt 26:17-19; Mk 14:12-16; Yo 13:21-30)  
\p
\v 7 Tilepleep le saawe to lupuuŋ tiina to ghaniiŋ mberet tau le yis mako na ivot. Mataaz tana, ene saawe to tirav sipsip natŋa pa ghanghaniiŋ to Pasova itaghon tutuuŋ to Maaron. \x * \xo 22:7 \xt Igham 12:18+\x*   
\m
\v 8 Tauvene Yesu imbaaŋ Petrus yesuru Yoan ighe: “Yamru amuuŋ ala ve agharaat leen aniiŋ to Pasova. Leso ravrav na, talup ghiit pa ghanghaniiŋ.”   
\p
\v 9 Yesuru tighasoni tighe: “Yo ughe nila nigharaata izi sindei?”   
\p
\v 10 Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Yamru aloŋ ala nugh tiina Yerusalem, mako aghita ŋeer ee ibaad uur to yaa, ve ilaagh ŋarui gham ilat. Matamim kisini ve ataghoni. Ruum sindei tau ighe i iloŋ ila, yamru ataghoni aloŋ ala.  
\v 11 Ve asaav pa ruum tawe taama aghe: ‘Paduduŋaaŋ toit ighason ghom ighe: Ruum loolo tau yo ughuru pa yes loomba na, igheen sindei? Pa i ighe tomania mbiwa tooni tilup zi ta sene pa ghanghaniiŋ to Pasova.’  
\v 12 Ŋeer tana pale itotoi ruum loolo tiina ee payam. Igheen izala saaŋa. Nugh to lepoogh ve ghanghaniiŋ, ene tigharaata wa. Yamru agharaat leen aniiŋ izi ta sewe.”   
\p
\v 13 Yesu isavsaav pazi le isov, ra yesuru tipuli, ve tiloŋ tila Yerusalem, ve tighita gabua isov ivot itaghon Yesu aliiŋa. Tauvene tigharaat aniiŋ to Pasova izi ta sewe.   
\s1 Yesu tomania mbiwa tooni tighan aniiŋ to Pasova  
\r (Mt 26:20-25; Mk 14:17-21; Yo 13:21-30)  
\p
\v 14 Ravrav izi, ve saawe to Pasova ivot, ra Yesu tomania mbaŋooŋa \f + \fr 22:14 \ft Mbaŋooŋa tane, ene mbiwa saŋavul ve ru to Yesu.\f*  
\m tooni tilup zi, ve mbolezi izi pa ghanghaniiŋ.  
\v 15 I isaav pazi ighe: “Ŋgar tsiau iyaryaaŋ naghe itiŋa talup ghiit pa ghanghaniiŋ to Pasova tane le isov, o nagham yavyavuuŋ.  
\v 16 Ve yau nasaav payam: Irau naghan aniiŋ to Pasova muul mako le Maaron itotoi pooz tooni ivot ighazooŋ ve Pasova anooŋa tooni ivot.” \x * \xo 22:16 \xt Lu 13:29, 14:15\x*   
\s1 Yesu irei mberet ve vaen pa mbiwa tooni  
\r (Mt 26:26-30; Mk 14:22-26; 1Kor 11:23-25)  
\p
\v 17 Ra Yesu igham rubruub vaen, ipait Maaron pani, ve izuzuuna ila pazi. Ve isaav pazi ighe: “Aghamu ve aghun le irau gham.  
\v 18 Yau nasaav payam: Yau aat naghun vaen muul mako le irau Maaron itotoi pooz tooni ivot ighazooŋ.”   
\p
\v 19 Ra igham mberet, ipait Maaron pani, iteeva, ve ireii irau zi. Ve isaav pazi ighe: “Ene yau mizag. Yau aat napul taug ve namaat payam. Ŋgar tau naghamu ne, matamim kisini ve ataghoni. Leso matamim iŋgal ghau.” \x * \xo 22:19 \xt 1Kor 10:16-17\x*   
\p
\v 20 Tighan le isov, ra Yesu itaghon ŋgar raraate pa rubruub vaen. Ighamu ve isaav ighe: “Rubruub tane, ene siŋig tau pale imaliŋ payam ve ipariaaŋ saveeŋ mbuaaŋ to eez paaghu tau pale Maaron ve tamtamon tivalupu zi timin eemon. \x * \xo 22:20 \xt Igham 24:8; Hib 9:12, 10:10\x*   
\m
\v 21 Eemon alooŋ. Tsiam ee tau ilepleep tomani ghiit pa ghanghaniiŋ ne, pale ighur ghau nala koiagŋa nimazi. \x * \xo 22:21 \xt Mbo 41:9; Yo 13:21+\x*   
\m
\v 22 Onoon, Tamtamon Naatu, i aat itaghon eez tau Maaron ighuru pani na. Eemon ŋeer tau pale ighuru ila koiŋa nimazi, ene ikaria tauu wa.” \x * \xo 22:22 \xt Mbaŋ 1:6, 2:23\x*   
\p
\v 23 Mbiwa tooni tilooŋ saveeŋ tane le tigham ŋgar naol ve tivaghasoni zi tighe: “Wai, iit tane, sei pale igham tauvene?”   
\s1 Ŋeer tau ighe imin tiina, i aat itatan tauu  
\r (Mt 20:25-27; Mk 10:42-44)  
\p
\v 24 Ra mbiwa tooni tivazorai zi pa toozi sei ta eeza tiina iliiv zi tisov. \x * \xo 22:24 \xt Mk 9:34+; Lu 9:46\x*   
\p
\v 25 Tauvene Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Ŋgar to nugh nugh tau Yuda mako na, yam awataghi wa. Kinik toozi tipapait tauzi ezazi, ve monmon titotoi tapirizi pa yes tau tileep ila sambazi na, ve titatan zi. Ve daaba siriv tau tiŋginŋgin zi na, tighe tamtamon tipait zi pa uleeŋ tau tighamgham pazi na.  
\v 26 Eemon ŋgar tauvene igheen tsiam sov. Tamtamon tau ighe eeza tiina kat iliiv yam asov na, i aat itatan tauu eeza, ve igham uraat payam imin tazmimŋa geegeu. Ve ŋeer tau ighe imuuŋ payam na, i aat ibees payam. \x * \xo 22:26 \xt 1Pe 5:3\x*   
\m
\v 27 Laak, sei ta eeza tiina? Ŋeer tau mboole izi ve ighanghan, ma ŋeer tau iŋgalŋgal aniiŋ ve ibesbees pani ne? Ene i ta mboole izi ve ighanghan. Ve aghita. Yau naleep tomani gham, ve nabesbees payam.” \x * \xo 22:27 \xt Mt 20:28; Yo 13:12+; Pil 2:7\x*   
\p
\v 28 “Onoon, tovaaŋ naol ivot payau. Eemon yam apul ghau mako. Ayozyooz tomani ghau le ilam aazne.  
\v 29-30 Tauvene yau aat naghur gham pa uraat to ghamuuŋ pooz, imin Tamaŋ ighur ghau to nagham pooz. Leso murei aleep ila niamim to ghamuuŋ pooz izi nugh tsiau, ve aŋgin rumei saŋavul ve ru to yes Israela. Ve itiŋa pale talup ghiit ila boor tsiau, ve taghanghan ve taghunghun.” \x * \xo 22:29-30 \xt Mt 19:28; Lu 14:15; Syg 3:21, 19:9\x*   
\s1 Yesu isaav ighe Petrus pale ipaisamuna  
\r (Mt 26:31-35; Mk 14:27-31; Yo 13:36-38)  
\p
\v 31 Ra Yesu isaav pa Simon Petrus ighe: “Oo Simon Simon, uyamaan ghom wa! Sadan izuari ghi ighe igham gham amin le. Tauvene i pale itoov ghuruuŋ ila tsiam imin ŋeer tau ilos wit tooni ve itiri izaa, leso ivalagh anooŋa ila soghan, ve uuli ila soghan. \x * \xo 22:31 \xt 2Kor 2:11; 1Pe 5:8\x*   
\m
\v 32 Eemon yau naghur ghom ila suŋuuŋ tsiau wa: Leso utap pa ghuruuŋ ila tsio sov. Ve saawe tau yo utoor ŋgar tsio ve umuul, yo aat upalot toŋvetaz tsio.” \x * \xo 22:32 \xt Yo 17:9, 21:15+\x*   
\p
\v 33 Petrus ilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve isaav pa Yesu ighe: “Tiina, yau irau napul ghom mako. Isaav ighe tighur ghom uloŋ ula ruum to yavyavuuŋ, ene aat ituru tala. Ve isaav ighe tirav ghom umaat, ene aat yau paam, tirav ghau namaat tomani ghom!”   
\p
\v 34 Tauvene Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Aa Petrus, nasaav payo kat. Mboŋ aazne, yo aat upaisamun ghau pai tol, o tatareek itaŋ.”   
\s1 Yes mbiwa aat tigham lugluug, pepeel ve mbuzaagh ve tilaagh tomania  
\p
\v 35 Ra Yesu ighason mbiwa tooni ighe: “Laak, muuŋ saawe tau nambaaŋ gham ala pa uraat na, yau nasaav payam naghe: Yam alaagh tomania lugluug, pepeel, ma zuzuuŋa to aghemim sov. Ve mindai? Saawe tana, yam ambool pa gabua eta?”  
\p Yes tiyol aliiŋa tighe: “Mako. Yei nimbool pa gabua eta mako.” \x * \xo 22:35 \xt Mt 10:9; Lu 9:3\x*   
\p
\v 36 Yesu isaav pazi muul ighe: “Aazne, ene saawe ite. Isaav ighe lemim lugluug, na aghamu tomania pepeel, ve alaagh tomania. Ve ighe lemim mbuzaagh mako, na ala agholia nonoghiiŋa tsiam to ŋgoaaŋ, mako agham maeta, ve ala aghol lemim mbuzaagh.  
\v 37 Pasaa, Maaron aliiŋa ziiri ee tau tiboode na isaav ighe:  
\q2 ‘Yes tighita tighe i tamtamon saghati ee tau imalaaŋ pa tutuuŋ.’  
\m Mboŋ aazne, saveeŋ tane aat ighur anooŋa ivot payau itaghon Maaron ŋgar tooni. Pasaa, saveeŋ naol tau tiboode izaa tsiau na, anooŋa ighe ivot tane.” \x * \xo 22:37 \xt Is 53:12; Lu 24:26+\x*   
\p
\v 38 Mbiwa tooni tisaav pani tighe: “Tiina, ughita. Mbuzaagh ru tane.”  
\p Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Ena irau.”   
\s1 Yesu isuŋ izi loloz Oliv  
\r (Mt 26:36-46; Mk 14:32-42)  
\p
\v 39 Ra Yesu ipul nugh tiina Yerusalem, ve izala pa loloz Oliv itaghon ŋgar tau monmon ighamghamu na. Ve mbiwa tooni titaghoni gha yesŋa tizala.  
\v 40 Tila tivot ta sewe, ve i isaav pazi ighe: “Yam aleep ta sene ve asuŋ Maaron. Leso atap pa tovaaŋ sov.” \x * \xo 22:40 \xt Mt 6:13\x*   
\m
\v 41 Ra ipul zi tizi tileep, ve ilaagh ila soghan rig, ve iput aaghe ve isuŋ.  
\v 42 Ighe: “O Tamaŋ, ighe lolom tauvene, na upasalia rubruub tane payau. Eemon utaghon ŋgar tsiau sov. Utaghon taum lolom.” \x * \xo 22:42 \xt Mt 6:10; Yo 6:38\x*   
\p
\v 43 Saawe tau Yesu isuŋsuŋ, aŋela ee to sambam izilam ve ipaloti.  
\v 44 Yesu loolo ipataŋan kat le punita tomania siŋ toŋtoŋia izi taan. Tauvene isuŋ ariaaŋ kat. \x * \xo 22:44 \xt Yo 12:27; Hib 5:7\x*   
\p
\v 45 Isuŋ le isov, ra imuul ila to mbiwa tooni, ve ighit zi tighengheen. Pasaa, lolozi ipataŋan kat.  
\v 46 Tauvene isaav pazi ighe: “Wai, yam agheen pasaa? Aburig ve asuŋ Maaron. Mako pale tovaaŋ ivot payam ve atap.”   
\s1 Tikis Yesu  
\r (Mt 26:47-56; Mk 14:43-50; Yo 18:3-11)  
\p
\v 47 Yesu isavsaav soone, ve Yudas igherev eval tiina gha tila tivot tooni. (Mbiwa saŋavul ve ru, Yudas, i toozi ee.) I iŋarui Yesu ila ighe iyaŋin pani.  
\v 48 Yesu isaav pani ighe: “Yudas, mindai? Yo ughe uyaŋin pa Tamtamon Naatu, gha leso ughuru ila koiŋa nimazi?”   
\m
\v 49 Mbiwa tau tiyozyooz tomania Yesu na, tighilaal gabua tau pale ivot. Tauvene tighasoni tighe: “Tiina, mindai? Pale nipas mbuzaagh ve nirav zi?”   
\p
\v 50 Ra toozi ee, ipas mbuzaagh tooni izaa, ve isiki le isap motin ŋeer ee taliiŋa, ziige ila pa tapir. Ŋeer tawe, i daaba to watooŋrau besooŋa tooni.  
\v 51 Eemon Yesu isaav ighe: “Ai, irao! Apul zi tigham ŋgar tane.” Ra igham besooŋa tana taliiŋa, ve ipaako ila niia le poia muul.   
\p
\v 52 Ra Yesu isaav pa yes zeran to watooŋrau tomania ŋginiiŋa to Rumei Tiina, ve pooza siriv tau tilam pa kisiiŋni na ighe: “Mindai ta alaagh tomania mbuzaagh ma zaab, ve alam pa kisiiŋ ghau? Yau ŋeer to ghamuuŋ malmal?  
\v 53 Saawe naol, itiŋa talepleep izi Rumei Tiina naagho. Puughu mindai ta akis ghau pataghaaŋ ta sewe mako? Poia. Akis ghau lak. Mboŋ aazne, ene saawe tsiam. Pa ŋgar to ndoroom igham uraat toman tapiri.”   
\s1 Petrus ipaisamun Yesu eeza  
\r (Mt 26:69-75; Mk 14:66-72; Yo 18:25-27)  
\p
\v 54 Yesu isavia saveeŋ tane le isov, ra tikisi, ve tighamu tila, ve tighuru iloŋ ila daaba to watooŋrau ruum tooni. Petrus itaghon zi, eemon ilaagh soghan rig gha ila.  
\v 55 Tamtamon siriv tindav yav izi sirsiir to ruum tawe loolo, ve mbolezi izi ila yav ziige. Tauvene Petrus ila ve mboole izi tomani zi.   
\p
\v 56 Malau mako ve besooŋa livaa paaghu ee ila le ighita Petrus mboole izi yav ziige. Tauvene itugh maata pani, ve isaav ighe: “Ou, ŋeer tane ilaghlaagh tomania Yesu paam.”   
\p
\v 57 Eemon Petrus ipaisamun tauu ighe: “Wai livaa, ŋeer tawe, yau nawataghi mako.”   
\p
\v 58 Tileep rig, ve ŋeer ite ilam le aana ighilaal Petrus. Tauvene isaav pani ighe: “Ai, yo tane, toozi ee paam!”  
\p Eemon Petrus iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Ee-e ŋeer tsiau, yau mako.”   
\p
\v 59 Tileep rig, ra ŋeer ite iburig gha aana aavo iyaryaaŋ ighe: “Onoon kat, ŋeer tane, i ilaghlaagh tomania Yesu. Pa i paam to Galilaia.”   
\p
\v 60 Eemon Petrus iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Wai ŋeer tsiau, saveeŋ tau yo usavia na, yau nawataghi rigta mako.” Petrus isavsaav soone, ve tatareek itaŋ.  
\v 61 Saawe duduuŋ tana, Yesu itoor ghi, ve maata imuul ila pa Petrus. Petrus ighita, ve maata iŋgal saveeŋ tau Yesu isavia pani na. Saveeŋ tauvene: “Mboŋ aazne, yo aat upaisamun ghau pai tol le isov, o tatareek itaŋ.”  
\v 62 Tauvene Petrus iburig ivot ila muuri, ve itaŋ tiina toman loolo isaghat kat.   
\s1 Tirav Yesu ve tipamogheraini  
\r (Mt 26:67-68; Mk 14:65)  
\p
\v 63 Yes tau tikiskis Yesu na, tiravravu, ve tipamogheraini.  
\v 64 Tipoos maata pa uuli ve tighasoni tighe: “Yo propet, ne? Poia. Usaav lak! Sei ta irav ghom ne?”  
\v 65 Yes tiveleghi ve tisik saveeŋ sasaghati naol pani.   
\s1 Tipayooz Yesu ila daaba to yes Yuda naghozi  
\r (Mt 26:59-66; Mk 14:55-64; Yo 18:19-24)  
\p
\v 66 Tilepleep le nughizau, ra ŋginiiŋa to yes Yuda tilup zi izi niazi to lupuuŋ. Yes daaba to watooŋrau ve yes ŋgara to tutuuŋ paam tileep ila lupuuŋ tawe loolo. Ra tigham Yesu ila ivot toozi ve tipayooze ila naghozi, ve yes pooza tawe tisaav pani tighe:  
\v 67-68 “Isaav ighe yo Mesia, na usaav ghazooŋa payei!”  
\p Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Isaav ighe yau nasaav tauvene payam, yam irau aghur ila aliŋag mako. Ve isaav ighe naghason gham pa gabua eta, yam irau ayol aliŋag mako.  
\v 69 Eemon aazne ve ila,  
\q2 Tamtamon Naatu pale ileep ila niia to ghamuuŋ pooz tau igheen ila Maaron saksaki niima tapir.” \x * \xo 22:69 \xt Dan 7:13; Mbaŋ 7:56; Hib 1:3, 8:1\x*   
\p
\v 70 Yes tilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve tisov tilup avozi ve tighasoni muul tighe: “Mindai, yo ughe yo Maaron Naatu?”  
\p Yesu iyol aliŋazi ighe: “Saveeŋ tauta taumim asavia na.”   
\p
\v 71 Yes tilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve tisaav tighe: “Isov wa! Tail tamtamon ite paam to ipariaaŋ saveeŋ muul pasaa? Aazne, talooŋ katin saveeŋ ila i tauu aavo wa.”   
\c 23  
\s1 Tipayooz Yesu pa savsaveeŋ ila Piladus naagho  
\r (Mt 27:1-2, 11-14; Mk 15:1-5; Yo 18:28-38)  
\p
\v 1 Tauvene yes daaba tana tisov tiburig gha tigham Yesu tila, ve tipayooze ila Piladus naagho.  
\v 2 Ra tiŋgal saveeŋ pani tighe: “Yei nighita ŋeer tane monmon ikau tamtamon tsiei ŋgar toozi, ve ipapazaagh zi pa ghamuuŋ ŋgar sasaghati naol. I iŋgalsekin zi pa sikiiŋ takes ila pa kinik tiina to Rom paam. Ve ipapakur tauu ighe i Mesia ve kinik. Tauta nighamu ilam.” \x * \xo 23:2 \xt Lu 20:25; Mbaŋ 17:7\x*   
\p
\v 3 Tauvene Piladus ighason Yesu ighe: “Mindai, yo tane, kinik to yes Yuda?”  
\p Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Saveeŋ tauta taum usavia na.” \x * \xo 23:3 \xt Yo 18:36\x*   
\p
\v 4 Tauvene Piladus isaav pa yes daaba to watooŋrau tomania eval tiina ighe: “Yau naghita naghe ŋeer tane, i le sosor eta mako.”   
\p
\v 5 Eemon yes daaba tana avozi iyaryaaŋ tighe: “Ŋeer tana ilaghlaagh irau taan isov to Yudea, ve ikaukau ŋgar to tamtamon pa saveeŋ tooni, ve ipapazaagh zi, leso tizoor gavman to Rom aliiŋa. I ipaburigin uraat tooni izi taan sirivu to Galilaia, ve taghon taghon gha aazne ilam ivot izi sene.”   
\s1 Tighur Yesu ila to Erod  
\p
\v 6 Piladus ilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve ighason zi ighe: “O, ŋeer tane to Galilaia?”  
\p Yes tiyol aliiŋa tighe: “Vee, i to Galilaia.”   
\p
\v 7 Piladus ilooŋ tighe Yesu ilam pa nugh tau Erod iŋgini na, tauta isakia Yesu ila to Erod, leso itiir saveeŋ tooni. Pasaa saawe tana, Erod ilepleep izi Yerusalem paam.  
\v 8-9 Saawe malau, Erod iloŋlooŋ Yesu vaaru, eemon ighita rigta mako. I ighe le ighita Yesu igham gabua ŋgereeta eta. Tauta saawe tau tigham Yesu ila ivot tooni, Erod loolo poia kat, ve igham ghasoniiŋ naol pani. Eemon Yesu iyol aliiŋa rigta mako. Ineneeŋ mon. \x * \xo 23:8-9 \xt Is 53:7; Lu 9:9\x*   
\m
\v 10 Yes daaba to watooŋrau tomania yes ŋgara to tutuuŋ tau tiyozyooz tigharau Yesu na, avozi iyaryaaŋ ve tiŋgal saveeŋ naol pani.  
\v 11 Ve Erod tomania zaaba tooni tiveleghi ve tipamogheraini. Tigham nonoghiiŋa poia ee imin tau kinik tinonogh zi pani na, ve tinonoghi pani. Ra tighamu ve tighuru imuul ila to Piladus.  
\v 12 Muuŋ, koi isap Erod yesuru Piladus sosozi. Eemon saawe tana, yesuru tivalupu zi timin eemon. \x * \xo 23:12 \xt Mbaŋ 4:27\x*   
\s1 Piladus iyok ighe tirav Yesu izala ai pambarooŋ  
\r (Mt 27:15-26; Mk 15:6-15; Yo 18:39–19:16)  
\p
\v 13 Tauvene tigham Yesu imuul ila to Piladus, ve Piladus ipoi yes daaba to watooŋrau ve daaba siriv tomania eval tiina tilam tilup zi,  
\v 14 ve isaav pazi ighe: “Alooŋ. Yam agham ŋeer tane ilam, ve asaav aghe i ikaukau ŋgar to tamtamon tsiam, ve ipapazaagh zi, leso tizoor gavman to Rom aliiŋa. Eemon yau natiir saveeŋ tooni ila yam asov matamim, ve nandeeŋ sosor tooni eta imin tau yam asavia ne mako.  
\v 15 Ve Erod paam indeeŋ sosor tooni eta mako. Tauta tighamu imuul ilam. Tauvene aghita. Ŋeer tane, i igham sosor tiina eta irau to taravu imaat ne mako.  
\v 16-17 Tauvene yau aat nalosi mon, ve napuli ilat.” [Ndaman isov, saawe to lupuuŋ tiina to Pasova ighe ivot, ene gavana to Rom aat ipul yes tau tilepleep ila ruum to yavyavuuŋ loolo na, toozi ee ivot.]   
\p
\v 18 Eemon yes tisov tilup avozi, ve tiboob tighe: “Ŋeer tana ileep sov. Uravu imaat, ve upul Barabas ilam payei.”  
\v 19 Barabas tane, muuŋ ipazaagh tamtamon gha tigham malmal izi Yerusalem to tiziir gavman to Rom. Ve irav tamtamon imaat paam. Tauta tighuru iloŋ ila ruum to yavyavuuŋ.   
\p
\v 20 Piladus ighe ipul Yesu ila. Tauvene itoov saveeŋ pazi muul.  
\v 21 Eemon tinoknok bobaaŋ tighe: “Uravu izala ai pambarooŋ! Uravu izala ai pambarooŋ!”   
\p
\v 22 Tauvene Piladus isaav pazi muul imin pai tol ighe: “Narav sorokin ŋeer tane pasaa? I igham saa sosor? Yau naghita naghe i igham sosor eta irau to imaat pani ne mako. Tauvene yau aat nalosi mon, ve napuli ilat.”   
\p
\v 23 Eemon tiyok pa saveeŋ tooni mako. Azezi katitiiŋ pa bobaaŋ tighe Piladus irav Yesu izala ai pambarooŋ. Piladus itoova to irav atezi. Eemon irao mako. Pasaa, avozi iyaryaaŋ kat.  
\v 24-25 Tauvene i ilooŋ zi, ve ipul ŋeer tau eval tiina lolozi pani na, ivot pa ruum to yavyavuuŋ. I ŋeer tau muuŋ ipazaagh tamtamon gha tigham malmal to tiziir gavman to Rom, ve irav tamtamon imaat. Eemon Yesu, Piladus itaghon eval tiina lolozi, ve ighuru ila zaaba siriv nimazi.   
\s1 Yesu ibaad ai pambarooŋ tooni  
\r (Mt 27:32-44; Mk 15:21-32; Yo 19:17-27)  
\p
\v 26 Tauvene zaaba tigham Yesu gha yesŋa tilaagh tila le tizaa to ŋeer ee to nugh Sairini, eeza Simon. I ileep Yerusalem ziige, ve ighe iloŋ ila pa nugh tiina. Zaaba tighita, ve tikisi ve tighur ai pambarooŋ to Yesu izala avaara, gha aana ibaado, ve itaghon Yesu gha tila.  
\v 27 Eval tiina kat titaghon zi gha yesŋa tila. Zilivaa siriv tau tilaghlaagh tomani zi na, lolozi isaghatin Yesu. Tauvene titaŋtaŋ pani.  
\v 28 Yesu maata imuul pazi, ve isaav ighe: “Yam Yerusalem tinazi, ataŋ payau sov. Ataŋ pa taumim ve natumimŋa.  
\v 29 Pa yau nasaav payam. Murei, saawe saghati kat pale ivot, ve apasawal aghe: ‘Oyai, aazne zilivaa tau upazi, ve yes tau tipoop soone, ve yes tau payamyamŋa mako na, irau lolozi poia.’ \x * \xo 23:29 \xt Mt 24:19; Lu 21:23\x*   
\m
\v 30 Saawe tana ighe ivot, tamtamon pale tisaav ila pa loloz tighe: ‘Apol alam atav ghei lak!’ Ve tisaav pa nugh mbua mbua tighe: ‘Azala pavomai ve alal ghei lak!’ \x * \xo 23:30 \xt Is 2:19; Hos 10:8; Syg 6:16\x*   
\m
\v 31 Aghita. Aazne tigham ŋgar tane pa ai mbitai tau iyozyooz tomania raua. Ighe tauvene, pale saa gabua ivot pa ai gorgori?” \f + \fr 23:31 \ft Saveeŋ to Yesu tane, puughu tauvene. I ŋeer to ghamuuŋ ŋgar poia, eemon tigham pataŋani pani. Ighe tauvene, mindai pa yes Israela tau titaghon ŋgar poia mako ve tizorzoor Maaron ŋgar tooni na? \f*   
\s1 Tirav Yesu izala ai pambarooŋ  
\p
\v 32 Yes zaaba tigham zeran sasaghati ru gha yesŋa tila paam. Leso tirav zi timaat tomania Yesu.  
\v 33 Tila tivot nugh ee tau tiwaat eeza tighe ‘Tamtamon Daaba Rubruuba’, ra tirav Yesu tomania zeran ru tawe tizala ai pambarooŋ toz toz, ve tipayooz zi tizaa. Ee ituuk ila pa Yesu niima tapir, ve ite ituuk ila pa ŋas.   
\p
\v 34 Tituktuuk, ve Yesu isaav ighe: “O Tamaŋ, ureu sosor toozi. Pa ŋgar tau tighamu ne, yes tighilaalo mako.” Ra zaaba tigham nonoghiiŋa to Yesu tomania gabua tooni siriv tighe tireii irau zi. Tauvene tipayooz mbuur, leso itotoi sei tau pale igham saa gabua. \x * \xo 23:34 \xt Mbo 22:18; Mt 5:44; Mbaŋ 3:17, 7:60\x*   
\p
\v 35 Eval tiina tiyozyooz ve timarar gabua tau ivotvot na. Ve yes daaba to Yuda paam tiyozyooz ve tisiksik saveeŋ veleghiiŋ pa Yesu tighe: “I iuluul tamtamon naol. Isaav ighe onoon i Mesia, ve Maaron ighuru pa uraat tooni, na iuul tauu lak!” \x * \xo 23:35 \xt Mbo 22:7\x*   
\p
\v 36 Yes zaaba paam tipaŋiŋizaini. Ve tila tigharauu ve tigham vaen maŋiŋi gha tizuzuuna izala pani to ighunu. \x * \xo 23:36 \xt Mbo 69:21\x*   
\m
\v 37 Ve tisaav pani tighe: “Isaav ighe yo kinik to yes Yuda, na uul taum lak!”  
\v 38 Ve tibood paesiiŋ to mateegh tooni puughu izala ai pambarooŋ tooni daaba. Paesiiŋ tawe isaav tauvene: “Ene kinik to yes Yuda.”  
\v 39 Zeran sasaghati ru tau tituktuuk izala ai pambarooŋ na paam, toozi ee isik saveeŋ veleghiiŋ pa Yesu ighe: “Yo Mesia ne? Ighe tauvene, na uul taum ve yeiru paam!”   
\p
\v 40 Eemon iitete iyaoni ighe: “Ai, yo uroi pa Maaron mako? Tigabiiz ghom tighe yo ugham sosor tiina. Tauta aazne yo aat umaat raraate imin ŋeer tane.  
\v 41 Pataŋani tau igham ghiit ne, ene iduduuŋ. Pasaa, ene sosor toit atuya. Eemon ŋeer tane, i igham sosor eta mako.”   
\p
\v 42 Ra isaav pa Yesu ighe: “O Yesu, saawe tau yo ulam ve utotoi pooz tsio tomania tapirim ivot ighazooŋ, na matam iŋgal ghau!”   
\p
\v 43 Yesu iyol aliiŋa ighe: “Onoon kat, yau nasaav payo: Aazne, ituru aat taleep izi nugh tau paghuuna le paghuuna kat.”   
\s1 Yesu imaat  
\r (Mt 27:45-56; Mk 15:33-41; Yo 19:28-30)  
\p
\v 44-45 Aaz anunu izalam zegmatuugh, ra ndoroom tiina ivot irau taan isov, ve ighengheen tauvene le aaz ivool (3 kilok). Ra uuli tiina tau ituktuuk ila Rumei Tiina loolo ve iponpoon nugh tau patabuyaaŋ kat na, imaraŋgat imin ru. \x * \xo 23:44-45 \xt Igham 26:33; Yoel 2:31; Hib 9:3\x*   
\p
\v 46 Ve Yesu iboob aliiŋa tiina ighe: “Tamaŋ, ene naghur taug ila yo nimam.” Isaav tauvene le isov, ve iyavaghan gha imaat. \x * \xo 23:46 \xt Mbo 31:5; Mbaŋ 7:59; 1Pe 2:23\x*   
\p
\v 47 Daaba to yes zaaba ighita gabua tau ivot na, ve ipait Maaron eeza, ve isaav ighe: “Onoon kat. Ŋeer tane, i ŋeer duduuŋa. I igham sosor eta mako.”  
\v 48 Eval tiina tau tilup zi gha tilam pa marariiŋ gabua tau ivot na, tighita gabua naol tana, le lolozi ipataŋan kat. Tauvene tiposai gargarizi ve titaŋtaŋ, ve timuul tila pa ruum toz toz. \x * \xo 23:48 \xt Amos 8:10\x*   
\p
\v 49 Yesu zeetŋa tisov, tomania yes zilivaa tau titaghoni ve yesŋa tilaagh Galilaia gha tilam na, tiyozyooz soghan, ve timamarar gabua tau ivotvot na. \x * \xo 23:49 \xt Mbo 38:11\x*   
\s1 Tighur Yesu paata ila naal loolo  
\r (Mt 27:57-61; Mk 15:42-47; Yo 19:38-42)  
\p
\v 50-51 Yuda ee ilepleep, eeza Yosep. I to nugh Arimatea tau igheen ila taan sirivu to Yudea na. I ŋeer duduuŋa ee, ve ŋgar tooni poia. I ighurghur maata pa saawe to Maaron itotoi pooz tooni ivot ighazooŋ. Ve i ileep ila lupuuŋ tiina to yes daaba tau tiŋginŋgin yes Yuda na. Eemon ŋgar tau tigham pa Yesu na, i iyok pani mako.  
\v 52 Tauvene ila to Piladus, ve ighasoni ighe iyokia Yesu paata pani.  
\v 53 Piladus iyok pani, tauvene Yosep tomania zeran siriv tila tizugh Yesu paata izi pa ai pambarooŋ, ve tizunua pa uuli pisosooŋa. Ra tighamu tila ve tighuru iloŋ ila maet puura ee tau tigharaata pataghaaŋ imin naal pa mateegha. Puura tawe, tighur mateegh eta iloŋ ila soone.   
\p
\v 54 Saawe tana, ene saawe to titartar pa umbom patabuyaaŋ. Ve ravrav izi wa. Tauvene paita tizaa pa umbom patabuyaaŋ leso timariau.   
\p
\v 55 Zilivaa tau yesŋa Yesu tilaagh Galilaia gha tilam Yerusalem na, titaghon Yosep tila. Yes tighe tighita nugh tau tighur Yesu paata pani na, ve tighita igheen mindai. \x * \xo 23:55 \xt Lu 8:1-3\x*   
\p
\v 56 Tighita le isov, ve timuul tila pa niazi to lepoogh, ve tigharaat naunauŋ ve ŋgoreeŋ tau vaazi popoia na pa Yesu paata. Ra saawe to umbom patabuyaaŋ ivot. Tauvene timariau itaghon tutuuŋ to Maaron.   
\c 24  
\s1 Yesu iburig pa mateegh  
\r (Mt 28:1-10; Mk 16:1-8; Yo 20:1-10)  
\p
\v 1 Umbom patabuyaaŋ isov, ve saawe imin maata to wik tana, mboŋoozo geeg, ve zilivaa tawe tigham naunauŋ ve ŋgoreeŋ tau tigharaat zi na, ve tila pa naal to Yesu.  
\v 2 Tila tivot ta sewe, le tighita maet tiina tau ipoon naal aavo na, igheen ila niia muul mako. Tipatambulia ighau ila ziige wa.  
\v 3 Tauvene tiloŋ tila, eemon tighita Yesu paata mako.  
\v 4 Tauta tigham ŋgar naol. Malau mako ve zeran ru tivot, ve tiyooz ila naghozi. Yesuru nonoghiiŋa toozi milmilia kat. \x * \xo 24:4 \xt Mbaŋ 1:10\x*   
\m
\v 5-6 Yes zilivaa tighit zi le roiŋ tiina igham zi. Tauvene tiput aghezi, ve tighur naghozi ila taan.  
\p Eemon zeran ru tawe tisaav pazi tighe: “Yam alam ail ŋeer tau maata yaryaare ila mateegha niazi pasaa? I ileep ta sene muul mako. I iburig wa! Matamim iŋgal. Saawe tau i ileep tomani gham izi Galilaia na, isaav payam ighe:  
\v 7 ‘Tamtamon Naatu, aat tighuru ila zeran sasaghati nimazi, ve tiravu imaat izala ai pambarooŋ itaghon Maaron ŋgar tooni. Eemon mboŋ imin tol, Maaron pale ipaburigini pa mateegh.’” \x * \xo 24:7 \xt Lu 9:22, 18:31+\x*   
\p
\v 8 Yes zilivaa tilooŋ saveeŋ tane, ve matazi iŋgal Yesu aliiŋa.  
\v 9 Ra tipul naal, ve timuul tila tipaesia gabua isov tana pa mbiwa saŋavul ve ee, tomania zeran siriv paam.  
\v 10-11 Zilivaa tawe, ene Maria to Magdala, Yoana, Maria ite tau Yakobus tiina na, ve zilivaa siriv paam. Yes tane ta tipaesia gabua isov tana pa yes mbaŋooŋa. Eemon yes tighur ila saveeŋ toozi mako. Tighe pa dabazi ikaukau ve tisaav sorok.   
\p
\v 12 Eemon Petrus iburig gha ilaan ila pa naal to Yesu. Ila ivot ta sewe, ra itugh ghi izi, ve igig iloŋ ila pa naal loolo, le ighita uuli siriv siriv tau tikau Yesu paata pani na, gabua tawe mon ta ighengheen. Tauvene ipul naal ve ila, ve ighamgham ŋgar pa gabua tau ivot na.   
\s1 Yesu ivot to ziŋeera ru izi eez tau ila pa Emaus  
\r (Mk 16:12-13)  
\p
\v 13 Aaz eemon tana, Yesu ziŋeera ru tighe tila pa nugh Emaus. Nugh tawe igheen malau rig pa Yerusalem (irau 11 kilomita ma vene).  
\v 14 Yesuru tilaghlaagh, ve tivasavo zi pa gabua naol tau ivot na.  
\v 15 Tisavsaav, ve malau mako na, Yesu tauu ivot toozi, ve yesŋa tilup zi pa laghooŋ gha tila.  
\v 16 Eemon gabua eta ipoon matazi, tauta tighilaalo mako.  
\v 17 Yesu ighason zi ighe: “Ou, yamru alaghlaagh, ve avasavo gham pa saa?”  
\p I isaav tauvene, ve yesuru tiyooz. Matazi izaa mako. Titud mon. Pasaa, lolozi ipataŋan kat.  
\v 18 Ra ee, eeza Kleopas, iyol Yesu aliiŋa ighe: “Wai, gabua tau noor mon ivot na, tamtamon tisov tau tileep Yerusalem we tiwataghi le isov. Yo aat loom eta, tauta ukankaan ne?”   
\p
\v 19 Tauvene i ighason zi muul ighe: “Saa gabua?”  
\p Yesuru tiyol aliiŋa tighe: “Yei nisavsaav pa ŋgar tau tigham pa Yesu to Nasaret na. Eval tiina tighita tighe i propet tiina ee ila Maaron maata. Pa saveeŋ ve uraat tooni, ene toman tapiri. \x * \xo 24:19 \xt Mt 21:11; Yo 6:14; Mbaŋ 2:22\x*   
\m
\v 20-21 Tauvene nighe pa i aat Uleeŋa tau pale igham mulin iit Israela pa pataŋani toit. Eemon mako. Yes daaba to watooŋrau tomania pooza toit tighuru ila Roma nimazi leso tiravu imaat. Tauta tiravu izala ai pambarooŋ gha imaat. Gabua tane ivot pani mboŋ tol ila wa. \x * \xo 24:20-21 \xt Lu 1:68, 19:11; Mbaŋ 1:6\x*   
\p
\v 22-23 “Ve ŋgarig mboŋoozo, ndoroome geeg, ve gabua ite ivot. Zilivaa tsiei siriv tigham ghei nirur tiina le ŋgar tsiei imbool. Pasaa, tila naal tooni, eemon tighita Yesu paata igheen muul mako. Ve tighita aŋela tivot toozi, ve tisaav pazi tighe: ‘Yesu ileep maata yaryaare.’ Tauvene timuul tilam, ve tipaesia gabua tana payei.  
\v 24 Ra zeran tsiei siriv anazi tila tighe tighita naal. Tila tivot, ve tighita Yesu paata mako. Ve gabua isov ighengheen raraate imin zilivaa tisavia.” \x * \xo 24:24 \xt Yo 20:3+\x*   
\p
\v 25 Ra Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Wai, yam lemim ŋgar mako! Maaron aliiŋa isov tau yes propet tivotia na, puughu mindai ta yam aghur ila mako?  
\v 26 Saveeŋ igheen pataghaaŋ wa: Mesia aat iyamaan yavyavuuŋ tiina, ve ibaad pataŋani naol itaghon Maaron ŋgar tooni, o eeza tiina ivot ighazooŋ, ve izala ileep izi nugh sambam toman tapiri ve mbonari tiina.” \x * \xo 24:26 \xt Lu 9:22; Mbaŋ 17:3; Hib 12:2; 1Pe 1:10+\x*   
\m
\v 27 Ra Yesu ipaghazoŋai zi pa Maaron aliiŋa isov tau tiboode izaa tooni na. Ipaburigin saveeŋ tooni pa saveeŋ to Mose, ve itaghon ila ila le ipasovu ila saveeŋ isov to yes propet. \x * \xo 24:27 \xt Gnp 3:15; Lo 18:15; Mbo 22\x*   
\p
\v 28 Tilaghlaagh tila le tigharau nugh tau yesuru tighe tila pani na. Ra Yesu itoom gha ighe malmali ila.  
\v 29 Eemon yesuru tiŋguruuta tighe: “Aiss, ula sov. Mboŋ izi wa. Umuul ulam ve itiŋa taleep.” Tauvene Yesu ila tomani zi, ve yesŋa tileep.   
\p
\v 30 Tilepleep le saawe tau mbolezi izi pa ghanghaniiŋ, ra Yesu igham mberet, ipait Maaron pani, iteeva, ve igham pazi.  
\v 31 Igham tauvene, ra matazi pakia ve tighilaalo. Eemon i iyaŋgovai ghi le tighita muul mako.  
\v 32 Yesuru tivasavo zi tighe: “Onoon kat. Saawe tau talaghlaagh taghon eez talam, i iwakaav ŋgar toit pa Maaron aliiŋa tau tiboode na, le saveeŋ tooni tawe ipazaagh katin ghiit le loloon poia kat.”   
\p
\v 33 Saawe duduuŋ tana, yesuru tiburig, ve rekia mon timuul tila pa Yerusalem. Tila tivot ta sewe, ve tindeeŋ mbiwa saŋavul ve ee tomania zetazŋa siriv tilup zi gha tilepleep.  
\v 34 Yes tau tilup zi na, tisaav pa yesuru tighe: “Onoon kat. Tiina toit iburig pa mateegh, ve ivot to Simon wa!” \x * \xo 24:34 \xt 1Kor 15:4+\x*   
\m
\v 35 Ra yesuru anazi tipaesia gabua tau ivot pazi izi eez livuugha na. Ve tisaav pazi tighe: “Saawe tau Yesu ileep tomani ghei ve iteev mberet na, yeiru nighilaalo.”   
\s1 Yesu ivot to mbiwa tooni  
\r (Mt 28:16-20; Mk 16:14-18; Yo 20:19-23; Mbaŋ 1:6-8)  
\p
\v 36 Yes tisavsaav pa gabua tana, ve malau mako na, Yesu tauu ivot gha iyooz ila sosozi, ve isaav pazi ighe: “Luuma to Maaron igheen tomani gham.”   
\p
\v 37 Yes tighita le tirur, ve roiŋ tiina igham zi. Tighe pa i mariaam.  
\v 38 Eemon Yesu isaav pazi muul ighe: “Wai, puughu mindai ta yam aroi ve lolomim ruru payau, ve ŋgar tsiam imin naol?  
\v 39-40 Aghita nimag ve agheg. Ene yau taug tane. Alam akis ghau ve aghita. Mariaam le miiza ve tuua imin yau? Mako.” I isavsaav pazi, ve itotoi niima ve aaghe pazi. \x * \xo 24:39-40 \xt 1Yo 1:1\x*   
\p
\v 41 Yes tintinizi kat. Eemon lolozi ruru soone. Pasaa, gabua tau tighita na, igham ŋgar toozi imbool. Tauvene Yesu ighason zi ighe: “Mindai, lemim aniiŋ eta to naghani, ma mako?” \x * \xo 24:41 \xt Yo 21:5\x*   
\m
\v 42-43 Tauvene tigham iigh mazooza sirivu pani, ve tisov timarari ve ighan. \x * \xo 24:42-43 \xt Mbaŋ 10:41\x*   
\s1 Yesu ighur uraat pa mbiwa tooni  
\r (Mt 28:18-20; Mk 16:15)  
\p
\v 44 Ra Yesu isaav pazi ighe: “Matamim iŋgal aliŋag tau muuŋ itiŋa talepleep ve nasavia payam na: Saveeŋ isov tau tiboode izaa tsiau na, ene aat ighur anooŋa ivot itaghon Maaron ŋgar tooni. Saveeŋ tau igheen ila Mose tutuuŋ tooni, saveeŋ to yes propet, ve saveeŋ tau igheen ila mbouŋ to iit Israela na paam.” \x * \xo 24:44 \xt Mbo 2, 16, 22, 69, 72, 110, 118\x*   
\p
\v 45 I isaav tauvene, ra iwakaav ŋgar toozi pa Maaron aliiŋa tau tiboode na. Leso tighazooŋ kat pa puughu.  
\v 46 Ve isaav pazi muul ighe: “Maaron aliiŋa tau tiboode na isaav tauvene: Mesia aat iyamaan yavyavuuŋ, ve tiravu imaat itaghon Maaron ŋgar tooni. Ve mboŋ imin tol, i aat iburig pa mateegh. \x * \xo 24:46 \xt Mbaŋ 17:3\x*   
\m
\v 47 Mako tivotia saveeŋ pa tamtamon ila i eeza tighe: Yes aat titoor ŋgar toozi ila pa Maaron, ve tipul ŋgar toozi sasaghati ileple, ve tighur ila to Mesia. Leso i ndaamo pazi, ve Maaron ireu sosor toozi. Uraat tane, yam aat apaburigini izi Yerusalem imin maata, mako aseeŋga ila le irau nughmariŋ. \x * \xo 24:47 \xt Mt 28:19\x*   
\m
\v 48 Yam aghit katin gabua isov tau ivot payau na pa matamim. Tauvene lemim uraat to ala ve avotia varug, leso apariaaŋ saveeŋ tsiau. \x * \xo 24:48 \xt Yo 15:27; Mbaŋ 1:8, 2:32; 1Yo 1:1+\x*   
\m
\v 49 Eemon ala rekia sov. Yau pale nambaaŋ Avuvu Patabuyaaŋ izilam itaghon saveeŋ mbuaaŋ to Tamaŋ Maaron. Tauvene aleep Yerusalem ve asaŋan le tapiri sambam ve izilam izala pavomim, o ala.” \x * \xo 24:49 \xt Is 44:3; Yoel 2:28; Yo 14:16, 15:26, 16:7; Mbaŋ 1:4, 2:4; Ga 3:14\x*   
\s1 Yesu imuul izala pa sambam  
\r (Mk 16:19-20; Mbaŋ 1:9-11)  
\p
\v 50 Ra Yesu igham mbiwa tooni gha tila pa nugh Betania. Tila peria ta sewe, ra iit niima izaa ve ighur poia to Maaron izaa toozi.  
\v 51 Niima izazaa pavozi soone, ve Taama Maaron ighamu ipul zi gha izala pa sambam. \x * \xo 24:51 \xt Yo 20:17\x*   
\m
\v 52 Yes tiput aghezi ve tipakuru le isov, ra timuul tila pa Yerusalem toman lolozi poia kat. \x * \xo 24:52 \xt Yo 16:22\x*   
\m
\v 53 Saawe tana ve ila, tiluplup zi pa suŋuuŋ ila Rumei Tiina naagho, ve tipapait Maaron eeza pa poia tooni.   